Dyos okichi mochiten
Kimani okinpewalti mochiten, Dyos,
okichi takpakIlwikak wan tal.
Wan tal amo kipiyaya tachiwaliste wan amoten kipiyaya,
wan atim wehwekatim kitapachowaya se tatikomat,
wan ni'EspirituDyos moliniya ipa atim,
ipa wehwe'atim pa kishki we.
Wan Dyos kito: “Ma ye tawiliste!”
Wan ye tawiliste.
Wan Dyos okit kina kwal katka tawiliste
Dyos okitokayolti tawiliste “tahka”,
wan tayowaliste, “tayo”.
Wan yok o'as se tyotak, wan yok o'as se watsinko:
ka se tonat.
Wan Dyos kito: “Ma ye se tatsakwaliste
ipanta atim, pa yok mosesemanaske atim ka atim!”
Okichi Dyos tatsakwaliste
wan kiseseman atim yewal katka itsinta,
tatsakwaliste ka atim wan katkaloya ipa tatsakwaliste wan yok omotachi.
Wan Dyos kitokayolti tatsakwaliste “ilwikak”.
ka ome tonatim.
Wan Dyos kito: “In atim inik kat itsinta tatsakwaliste ilwikak
ma monichikok,
ma moneshte tal wak!”
Yok omotachi.
Wan Dyos yok okitokayolti wak “tal”,
wan inik atim monichikok okitokayolti “wehwe'atim”.
Wan yok kina kwal okit Dyos.
Kwakin Dyos kito: “Ma ye mochiten pa tal;
ma motashosholti ka tashosholtik ma kipiyak nishinashte,
yok kina sesen nesil!”
Wan yok omotachi.
Okitakatilti tal tashosholtik:
ka shosholtik ka nishinashte,
inik kwawim ka nitakilme ka nishinashte,
kina takil sesen.
Wan Dyos kina kwal okit.
Wan yok o'as se tyotak, wan yok o'as se watsinko:
ka yey tonatim.
Wan Dyos kito: “Ma yek tawiliste ka tatsakwaliste pa takpakIlwikak
ma ye kina taneshtiliste pa kimatiske kimani tonalko wan shopanta,
pa tonatim wan shiwim,
ma tipitakak pa tatsakwaliste ka takpakIlwikak
pa tawiske pa mochital!”
Kwakin yok omotachi.
Okichi Dyos ome tawiliste:
wehwe tawiliste tatake tahka,
wan amoyok we tawiliste tatake tayo.
Wan niyok okinchi sitalme.
Okintal Dyos pa takpakIlwikak
Okinchi pa tatakewaske pa tahka wan tayo,
yok kinseseman tawiliste ka tayowaliste.
Dyos okit kina kwal katka.
Wan yok o'as se tyotak, wan yok o'as se watsinko:
ka in nawi tonatim.
Wan Dyos kito: “Ma mochiwak pa atim myak yolikilme,
wan totom patanilme ipa tal
pa tatsakwaliste takpakIlwikak!”
Kwakin okinchi Dyos yolikilme wehwe pa atim,
wan moshte inik yolikilme
wan niyok okinchi yehwante kishki kinpiyal ininnastakapalme,
kina sesen.
Wan yok kina kwal okit Dyos,
wan Dyos kinmashti kitowaya:
“Shimomiyaptik;
wan shikintemiltik atim ka wehwe'atim.
Ma momiyaptik totom pa mochital!”
Wan yok o'as se tyotak, wan yok o'as se watsinko:
ka makwil tonatim.
Wan Dyos kito: “Ma takatik pa mochital yolikilme kina sesen nesil:
wan kowam, kina sesen nesil!”
Wan yok omotachi.
Dyos okinchi tekwanim mochantilme pa kwawim,
wan yolikilme kitikipanol takam,
wan yolikilme mowilanal pa tal,
kina sesen nesil.
Wan yok kwal okit Dyos,
wan Dyos kito: “Ma tikchiwak se masewal
kina tehwante.
Ma kipiyas chikawaliste ipa we'at pa michim,
ipa yolikilme kitikipanol takam,
wan tekwanim mochantilme pa kwawim,
wan ipa yolikilme
yehwante mowilanal ipa tal.”
Kwakin okichi se masewal kina nes;
okichi kina Dyos.
Takat wan siwat okinchi,
kinmashti Dyos wan kinmili:
“Shikintakatiltik wan shimomiyaptik;
shiktemiltik mochital wan shitatakewak;
wan mochiten yewal mowilanal ipa tal.”
Wan Dyos kinmili: “Annimishmak yewal onka ipa tal
shosholtik temakal nishinashte
mochi kwawim temakal takilme wan temakal shinashte;
mochiten ina kwal ankikwaske.
Wan mochi tekwanim pa mochital,
wan mochi patanilme pa takpakIlwikak,
wan mochi mowilanalme pa tal,
mochi kishki kipiyal yoliliste,
mochi shosholtik nikinmak pa kipiyaske pa kikwaske.”
Kwah Dyos okit mochiten yewal okichi,
wan kwal katka.
Wan yok o'as se tyotak, wan yok o'as se watsinko:
ka chikwase tonatim.
Otam okichi Dyos takpakIlwikak wan mochital,
wan mochiten onka pa mochital.
Pa chikome tonatim, Dyos mosewiyaya
kampa tamiyaya nitikipanoliste ten kichiptikatkaya.
Wan kimashti Dyos pa tonat chikome, okichi se tonat we,
pa yewal mosewi kwah otam okichi mochi nitikipanoliste.
ka takpakIlwikak wan mochital kimani oyek tachiwalme.
In masewal kaha motashot itok Edén
Kimani Dyos in WeTatsDyos okichi mochital wan takpakIlwikak,
wan mochi tashosholtik pa kwawim kimani ayamo kisaloya shosholtik, kampa Dyos in WeTatsDyos ayamo kiwaltitaniyaya kyawit pa mochital wan amo katka masewal kitikipanoskya tal.
Ma yok, nalkistikatka pa tal nitonalmikiliste at ki'ahwiliyaya mochital.
Kwakin Dyos in WeTatsDyos okichi se masewal ka nipohtiTal, wan okipits pa niyakatsol ka ni'ihyo kimak yoliliste, wan ye se masewal yolke.
Wan Dyos in WeTatsDyos okitok se kwahmil itok Edén kaha kis tonat, ompa okika masewal yewal okichi.
Dyos in WeTatsDyos okichi pa kisaloskya kwawim kwal nesiloya inintaki pa kikwaloskya. Ipanta tashotanilme katkaloya ome kwawim, se tayolti, wan okse kimashti ten kwal wan ten amokwal.
Kistikatka pa Edén se atenko we ki'ahwiliyaya in kwahmil, kipiyaya nawi nimashaltik atenko.
Se itoka Pishón, wan kiyawalowaya tal Hawilá, kampa katka oro.
In okse atenko itok Gihón, in atenko kiyawalo in tal itoka Kush.
In okse atenko itok Tigris, wan totok pa itenko pweblo Asirya kaha walkis tonat. Wan in okse atenko itoka Éprates.
Dyos in WeTatsDyos okika in masewal pa kwahmil Edén pa kitikipanoskya wan kikwitawiskya,
wan WeTatsDyos kili masewal: “Pa mochi inik kwawim takilme kwal tewal tikwas,
ma yok kwawit kinmashti ten kwal wan ten amokwal amo tikwas, kimani yewal tonat tikwas melak timikis.”
Kwakin Dyos in WeTatsDyos kito: “Amokwal isel yes masewal. Nikchiwilis se pa kipaleptiyas se nihni nesis kina yewal.”
Wan Dyos in WeTatsDyos okinchi ka tal mochi inik tekwanim yolil ka takam wan yolil pa kwawim wan mochi totom pa takpakIlwikak, wan okinwikil masewal pa kintokayoltiskya. Yewal takat kintokayolti, yok kina ashka itokal.
Yok kintokayolti mochi inik tekwanim yolil pa kwawim, wan totom pa takpakIlwikak wan inik yolil ka takam. Ma yok, masewal amo okit ak kipalewiskya se nihni nesis kina yewal.
Kwakin Dyos in WeTatsDyos okikochilti masewal chikawak, kwah koshtikatka, kikishtil se ni'omit<sup>a</sup> tanakastekal wan okitsakwa oksep inaka.
Ka ni'omit kostiya masewal, okichi WeTatsDyos se siwat okiwikil masewal,
“Ashka, ina no'omit ka no'omit
wan inaka nonaka.
Itoka siwat
kampa takishtiliste katka pa takat.”
Kampa se takat kikawas nitats wan ninantsi, motakitskilti inak nisiwa, wan yeske se han inakayo.
Kampa takat wan nisiwa amo kipiyaloya shashalme, ma yok amo pinawaloya.
In takat wan siwat amo kineltokak Dyos
In kowat kimatiya tekwamanaya, amoyok moshte kimatiloya oksek yolikilme, tekwanim mochantil pa kwawim wan in tekwanim kintikipanol takam, yewal kinchiwaya Dyos in WeTatsDyos. In kowat kili siwat:
Kampa melak anmichili Dyos pa amo ankikwaske nitaki inik kwawim pa kwahmil?
In siwat kinankili in kowat:
Ma yok otichil Dyos: “Amo tikwaske wan amo tihkitskiske nitaki kwawit, yewal onka ipanta kwahmil, ma yok timikiske.”
Kwakin kowat kili siwat:
―Amo anmikiske!
Kampa Dyos kimat, ta ankikwak nitaki, kwakin melak anmehwante ankimatiske kampa anmo'ilnamikiske anmo'ishtaposke anmoshtololme anyeske kina Dyos, ankimatiske ten kwal wan ten amokwal.
Kwakin siwat okit kwawit nitaki kina kwal nestikatka pa kikwaskya, wan niyok kinekiya kimatiskya tamatiliste, kwakin okonan se nitaki wan okikwa. Niyok okimak nitaka, yewal katka inak wan niyok yewal okikwa.
Kwakin haniman mo'ilnamikik ten okichiwak, wan katkaloya nakatilme. Kwakin kitsomak sek ni'iswam igo' pa motakemiltiloskya.
Kikakiloya Dyos in WeTatsDyos pek nehnemiya pa kwahmil kwah katka ta'istikit pa tyotakit, kwakin kitatilik tsalakwawim pa kwahmil.
Ma yok okinots Dyos in WeTatsDyos takat wan kili:
―Kaha ti'onka?
Wan yewal kinankili:
Kwakin Dyos kitahtanili:
―Ak yok michili kampa tikatka nakatil?
―Otikwa nitaki kwawit yewal nimichili amo tikwaskya?
Wan yewal takat kinankili:
―In siwat yewal otishmak pa yes nonihni onishmak tahko taki, wan newal onikwa.
Kwakin Dyos in WeTatsDyos kili siwat:
―Ten otikchi?
Wan kito siwat:
―In kowat onishkwaman kwakin onikwa taki.
Kwakin kili Dyos in WeTatsDyos in kowat:
nimichilis kampa amokwal mishyaptiyas ika mochi tekwanim,
yolil ka takam, wan mochi tekwanim yolil pa kwawim!
Pa kimani tiyoltiyas timowilanas,
wan tikwas mochi inik tonatim nipohtiTal.
Wan nikchiwas kampa tewal wan siwat,
mokokolitiyaske niyok mokolinchim wan nikolinchim in siwat,
nikolinchim siwat kishakwalo motsontek,
wan tewal tikwas nikshi.”
Kili siwat:
“Nihmiyapti motakokoliste kwah ti'ostitiya,
Ma yok tihnekis motaka yes ka tewal.
Yewal kipiyas chikawaliste ipa tewal.”
Wan takat<sup>a</sup> kili:
“Kina otikchi kina michili mosiwa,
wan otikwa nitaki yewal nimichili amo tikwaskya!
Nimichilis kampa amokwal kiyaptiyas in tal!
Ka takokoliste titakwas
pa hanse tonatim tiyoltiyas.
Wistim wan tsetsekalot mochiwaske,
wan tikwas shosholtik tashotanilme.
yok tiyes pa mochi inik tonatim kimani timikis wan timokwepas pa tal
onimishchi ka nipohtiTal.
Kampa timochiwas nipohtiTal
wan timochiwas pohtital kwah timikis.”
Adán okitokayolti nisiwa Hawa, kampa yewal ininnantsi moshte kishki yoltikat.
Kwakin Dyos in WeTatsDyos okinchiwil takat<sup>b</sup> wan nisiwa shashalme ka nikwero tekwanim wan yok okintakemilti.
Wan kito Dyos in WeTatsDyos: “Ashka takat omochi kina tehwante, kimat ten kwal wan ten amokwal. Ta kitekiskya nitaki kwawit tayolti, wan pa kikwaloskya wan yok yoliske hanse.”
Kampa okikishti Dyos in WeTatsDyos pa kwahmil Edén, pa kitikipanoskya tal kampa okichi ka nipohtiTal.
Kimani okikishti takat pa kiyawak, okital pa itenko kwahmil Edén kaha kis tonat sek yolil itokal kerubine', wan se teposte tatatitikatka wan kati momalintikatkaloya kina tapitaniliste, kikwitaptikatkaloya ot pa amo'ak kalakiskya pa kwahmil kaha katka kwawit tayolti.
Kayin wan Habel
Panok tonatim wan okitakatilti Habel, ninohni Kayin. Habel katka se takwitawil borrego', chibo' wan Kayin tatokaya.
Panok tonatim, wan Kayin okiwikil WeTatsDyos nitapishkaliste kina tatamakal.
Habel niyok okiwikil borrego' tohtomawak, yehwante kintakatiltik ta'ishpa yewal kinpiyaya pa niyolikilme. Dyos in WeTatsDyos kwal okit tatamakal yewal okiwikil Habel,
amoyok kwal okit ten okiwikil Kayin. Kwakin hyero kwalantikatka amokwal nestikatka nishayak.
Kwakin kili Dyos in WeTatsDyos Kayin: “Pates hyero tikwalantik? Pates yok titachishtik?
Ta otikchi kwal, wan newal nikonanas kwal. Ma yok ta amokwal otikchi, katsawiliste yes kina se tekwan yolil pa kwawim, pa michkwas. Amo shimotemak, tewal shikmansot.”
Kayin kili ninohni Habel. Ma tiyak pa kwahmilShosholtik, wan katkaloya pa kwahmilShosholtik ompa Kayin okimikti ninohni Habel.
Kwakin Dyos in WeTatsDyos kili Kayin:
―Kaha onka monohni Habel?
Wan Kayin kinankili:
Kwakin kili Dyos in WeTatsDyos:
―Ten otikchi! NiyEste monohni tahtantik takokoliste pa tal.
Ashka kampa amokwal mishyaptiyas tewal pa in tal, kampa totokatik niyEste monohni tewal tihmikti.
Kwah tiktikipanos tal, amo mishmakatiyas tapishkaliste, tinehnemtiyas wan amo tikpiyas mosewiliste pa tal.
Kayin kinankili Dyos in WeTatsDyos:
―We yes notakokoliste amo nikehwaltis.
Ashka tinishtitantik pa nimochantis kina se amo kipiyas icha, nimotatitinemis pa amo tichitas tewal, wan aki nichitas yok nishmiktis.
Kwakin Dyos in WeTatsDyos, kili:
―Aki kimikti Kayin, kwakin panos takokoliste ka chikome takwepaliste.
Kwakin in Dyos WeTastsDyos okital se taneshtililiste pa Kayin, pa yok amo'ak kimiktiskya aki kitaskya.
Kayin kipi nisiwa wan omotek inak, o'osti ta'apa wan okitakatilti se takatonte okitokayolti Henok. Okichi Kayin se Wepweblo pa inik tonatim, wan okitokayolti Wepweblo kina itoka nikon Henok.
Henok okipi se nikon okitokayolti Irad, wan Irad omochi nitats MehuyaEl, wan MehuyaEl ye nitats MetushaEl wan MetushaEl ye nitats Lamek.
Wan Lamek omonamikti ka ome siwam. Se itoka Ada wan okse Tsilá.
Ada okitakatilti Yabal, wan Yabal yek niwichalme yehwante takwitawilme yolikilme wan mochantiloya pa kalme tachiwalme ka shashalme.
Wan itoka ninohni Yubal, okinpewalti inik yehwante kimatil tatsotsonal gitarra wan flawta.
Niyok kipiyaya Tsilá se nikon yewal itoka Tubal-kayín, yewal kichiwaya mochi inik tachiwalme ka bronse wan yerro. Wan kipi se ninohniSiwat itoka Namá.
Se tonat Lamek kinmili ininsiwam Ada wan Tsilá:
“Shinishkakik ten annimichilis!
Shihkakik notahtolme!
Onihmikti se takat yewal nishkokolti,
Aki kimikti Kayin yewal yes se takwepaliske ka chikome,
wan Lamek kikwepiliske ka 77 aki kimikti.”
Adán omotek oksep inak nisiwa, okitakatilti se nikonTakat okitokayolti Shet, kampa kito: “Kampa WeTatsDyos onishmak okse nokon kampa amo onka Habel yewal Kayin okimikti.”
Shet niyok okipi se nikon wan okitokayolti Enósh. Kwah okipewaltik takam ni'itokaliste Dyos in WeTatsDyos.
Nikolinchim Adán
Nika nitakwihkwiloli nitapowaliste Adán<sup>a</sup> wan nikolinchim.
Dyos okichi masewal kina yewal.
Okinchi takat wan siwat, wan okinmashti. Pa tonat kwah okinchi kintokayolti “masewalme.”
Kwah yoliyaya Adán pa 130 shiwim, okipi se nikon yewal ones kina yewal, okitokayolti Shet.
Kwah takati Shet, Adán yolti 800 shiwim, wan okinpi oksek ininpilwaTakam wan ininpilwaSiwam.
Yolti Shet 105 shiwim okipi se nikon okitokayolti Enósh.
Kwah otakat Enósh, Shet yolti 807 shiwim, wan okinpi oksek ininpilwaTakam wan ininpilwaSiwam.
Mochi inik shiwim kipiyaya Shet 912 shiwim wan omik.
Yolti Enósh 90 shiwim, okipi nikon okitokayolti Kaynán.
Kimani otakat Kaynán, Enósh yolti 815 shiwim, wan okinpi oksek ininpilwaTakam wan ininpilwaSiwam.
Yolti 905 shiwim Enósh wan omik.
Yolti Kaynán 70 shiwim wan okipi nikon MahalalEl.
Kimani otakat MahalalEl, yolti Kaynán 840 shiwim, wan okinpi oksek ininpilwaTakam wan ininpilwaSiwam.
Mochi in shiwim yewal yolti Kaynán 910 shiwim wan omik.
Yolti MahalalEl 65 shiwim kimani okipi nikon Yéred.
Mochi shiwim yoliyaya MahalalEl kipiyaya 895 shiwim wan omik.
Yolti Yéred 162 shiwim kimani okipi nikon Henok.
Kimani otakat Henok, yolti Yéred 800 shiwim, wan okinpi oksek ininpilwaTakam wan ininpilwaSiwam.
Mochi inik shiwim yolti Yéred 962 shiwim wan omik.
Yolti Henok 65 shiwim kwakin okipi nikon Metushala.
Nehnemiyaya Henok niyol inak Dyos, kimani otakat Metushala, yolti 300 shiwim wan okinpi oksek ininpilwaTakam wan ininpilwaSiwam.
Mochi inik shiwim yolti Henok 365 shiwim,
wan nehnemiyaya inak Dyos, kwakin se tonat opoli kampa Dyos okiwik.
Yolti Metushala 187 shiwim otakat nikon Lamek.
Kimani otakat Lamek, yolti Metushala 782 shiwim, wan okinpi oksek ininpilwaTakam wan ininpilwaSiwam.
Lamek yolti 182 shiwim wan okipi se nikon,
okitokayolti No'á, kampa kito: “Ina tishyolsewis ka totikipanoliste yewal titikipanotikat ka tomahwam, yewal Dyos in WeTatsDyos kili kampa amokwal kiyaptiyas in tal.”
Kimani otakat No'á, yolti Lamek 595 shiwim, wan okinpi oksek ininpilwaTakam wan ininpilwaSiwam.
Mochi inik shiwim yolti Lamek 777 shiwim wan omik.
No'á kipiyaya 500 shiwim kwah okinpi ininpilwam Shem, Kam wan Yapet.
Ininta'ihtakoliste takam
Kwah momiyaptik masewalme pa tal wan kintakatiltik ininpilwaSiwam,
kwah nipilwaDyos kinmitak kina kwal nesiloya ininpilwaSiwam kintakatiltik masewalme. Kwakin konanak kishki kinekik pa moshte yeloskya ininsiwam.
Kwakin Dyos in WeTatsDyos kito: “Amo nikinyoli takam<sup>a</sup> ka no'ihyo pa hanse, kampa han kat nakat; amo panoske 120 shiwim.”
Katkaloya takamWehweyak pa in tal pa inik tonatim (wan takwitap), kimani nipilwaDyos omotekak ka ininpilwaSiwam masewalme wan kinpiyak ininpilwam inak yehwante. Yek monotsaliste ka momiktiliste chikawak pa inik tonatim ya wehkA.
wan moyokolti Dyos in WeTatsDyos kampa okinchi takam pa tal, wan okikok niyol.
Wan kito Dyos in WeTatsDyos: “Niyas nikshitinis mochital inik takam yewal onikinchi, inik tekwanim inik mowilanal pa tal wan inik totom pa takpakIlwikak. Nimoyolkokotik kampa onikinchi!”
Ma yok, Dyos in WeTatsDyos kitaya kwal No'á kampa kwal kichiwaya.
No'á kichiwaya arka
Ina nitapowaliste ka No'á.
Hanse kikaktiyas kwal i'ishpa Dyos. Yewal takat han kwal wan kimawishtiliyaya i'ishpa Dyos wan yewal han nehnemiyaya inak Dyos.
Okinpi No'á yey ininpilwaTakam: Shem, Kam wan Yapet.
Dyos kitaya kina yoliloya pa tal mo'ihtakotikatkaloya wan miyak mokokoltitikatkaloya.
Okit Dyos kina mo'ihtakotikatkaloya kampa moshte amo kimatiloya yoliloya kina okital Dyos pa yoltiyaloskya,
kili Dyos No'á: “Niyas nikinshitinis moshte masewalme, kampa mokokoltitikat sek ka oksek pa tal. Melak niyas nikinshitinis inak tal.
Wan yok tikchiwas: 135 metros iweyak, wan 22.5 metros ipatawak wan 13.5 metros itakpak.
Shikchiwil se nita'ishtapol kal pa nitakalchiwal shikpanolti tepante pa itahko metro itakpak, shikchi se tatapoli sela pa kal wan shikchi okse kal pa nipanta wan okse ikpak pa yey.
Newal nihwaltitanis se tapakyawaliste ipa in tal, wan niyok nikshitinis mochiten kipiyal yoliliste itsinta ilwikak. Wan mochiten onka pa tal mikiske.
Ma yok ka tewal niktalis se tahtoliste, tewal tikalakis pa arka wan mopilwam, mosiwa wan mosiwamonwam ankalakiske.
Wan mochiten yolil, moshte kishki kipiyal nakat, ka ohome kina sesen nesil, tikinkalaktis pa yok yoliske siwat wan takat yeske.
In totom kina kat sesen, wan tekwanim yolil ka takam kina sesen nesil, wan kishki mowilanal pa tal kina sesen nesil, ka ohome kalakiske ka tewal pa yok yoliske.
Wan shikonan shiknichik mochiten kikwal shikahkok, pa yok ankipiyaske ten ankikwaske anmehwante wan inik yolikilme.”
Kwakin okichi No'á mochiten kina kili Dyos.
Kwakin kili Dyos in WeTatsDyos No'á: “Shikalakik pa arka tewal wan moshte kishki mochantil pa mokal, kampa nimichit amo tikchiptik takokoliste amoyok nikinmit moshte in oksek yolil ashka.
Shikinwik ka tewal chikome tekwanim ka ohome kina sesen nesil; takat wan siwat, yehwante kinmit Dyos kina tekwanim amo chihchipawak, se siwat wan se takat.
Kimani panoske chikome tonatim, nikchiwas tapakyawaliste pa mochital 40 tonatim wan 40 tayowalme, wan nikshitinis mochital wan mochiten yolilme onikinchi.”
Yok okichi No'á kina kili Dyos in WeTatsDyos.
No'á kipiyaya 600 shiwim kwah wets tapakyawaliste ipa mochital.
Kalakik pa arka No'á wan nisiwa, ininpilwam wan nisiwamonwam, pa yok motsakwililoskya ka in tapakyawaliste.
Wan katkaloya tekwanim chihchipawak wan tekwanim amo chihchipawak, wan ka inik patanilme wan mochiten mowilanal ipa tal,
ka ohome kalakik ka No'á pa arka, se takat se siwat, kina Dyos kili No'á.
Kimani panok chikome tonatim, wets tapakyawaliste pa mochital.
Kimani No'á kipiyaya 600 shiwim, katka tonat 17 pa ome meste, yek ta'ishtapolilme in atim ka tatsakwaliste takpakIlwikak.
Wan ye tapakyawaliste ipa mochital 40 tonatim 40 tayowalme.
Pa in tonat kalakik pa arka No'á, ka ininpilwam Shem, Kam wan Yapet, wan nisiwa wan niyok ininsiwamonwam.
Walak ka No'á pa arka ka ohome mochi kishki kipiyaloya nakat ka ininihyo kipiyaloya yoliliste;
kalakiloya se takat wan se siwat kina sesen nesil, kina Dyos kili No'á. Kwakin Dyos in WeTatsDyos kitsakwa tatapoli.
Pa 40 tonatim tapakyapti ipa tal. Inik atim tehkoti, wan ki'ahkokti arka ipa tal.
Tehkoti inik atim wan mo'apakti ipa mochital, wan mo'ahkok arka ipa wehwe atim.
Inik atim tehko ipa mochital, wan mochi inik talTepet wehwe itsinta ilwikak kintapach.
Kwah kintapacho atim inik talTepet tehkok chikome metros wEhkat.
Wan mikik mochiten yoliloya ipa mochital: totom, tekwanim yolil ka takam wan tekwanim yolil pa kwawim, wan mochiten mowilanaloya ipa tal, wan moshte takam.
Mochiten mihyotiloya kipiyaloya yoliliste ka ininyakatsol wan mochiten katkaloya pa mochital mikik.
Yok ye tashitiniliste mochiten yolikilme pa mochital, ka takam ka tekwanim, inik mowilanalme wan inik totom pa takpakIlwikak. Moshte oye tashitiniliste pa mochital. Han omoka No'á wan inik katkaloya inak yewal pa arka.
Yok tapachoti tal ka atim pa 150 tonatim.
Motsakwak atim wehwehkat niyok atim pa takpakIlwikak, yahmo kyaptikatkaya.
Kwakin waktiyaya yolikit atim pa tal. Pa 150 tonatim temowaya at.
Pa tonat 17 pa meste chikome omokets arka pa in talTepet itoka Ararat,
inik atim waktiyak kwah o'as pa matahti meste onesik inik talTepet.
Kwah opanok 40 tonatim ki'ishtap No'á tatapoli yewal okichi pa arka
wan kimaka se kakalot yawiya walaya, pa kimani inik atim wakik ipa tal.
Niyok kimaka No'á se wilot, pa kitaskya atim ta waktiyaya ipa tal.
Ma yok wilot walmokwep pa arka kampa amo okit kaha motaliskya, kampa atim kitapachotikatka tal. No'á kikishti nimahwa, okonan wilot wan okikalakti pa arka.
Omochi chikome tonatim wan oksep okimaka wilot pa kiyawak.
Walmokwep wilot tamalinti tonat, kiwalikaya se iswatonte pa nipiko ka kwawit itoka olibo, kwakin kimat No'á kampa atim waktiyaya ipa tal.
Pa inik shiwim 601 kipiyaya No'á pa meste se in ta'ishpa tonat ka meste inik atim wakik ipa tal. Wan kikishtili No'á tatsakwili ka kal wan okit kampa tal wak katka.
Wan pa tonat 27 pa ome meste, wak katka mochital.
Kwakin Dyos kili No'á:
“Shikis pa arka tewal wan mosiwa, mopilwam wan mosiwamonwam.
Shikinkishti moshte inik tekwanim kat ka tewal mochi kishki kipiyal yoliliste: totom, tekwanim yolil ka takam wan tekwanim mowilanal ipa tal. Tikinkishtis ka tewal wan yaske pa mochital yok shimomiyaptik ipa tal! Shikinpiyak myak anmopilwam!”
Kwakin okis No'á ka ininpilwam, wan nisiwa wan nisiwamonwam.
Moshte inik tekwanim wan mochi inik mowilanal ipa tal wan mochi totom, wan mochi yewal molinil ipa tal, yok kina nesil sesen kisak pa arka.
Kwakin No'á okikets se tanichikol ka tetelme pa Dyos in WeTatsDyos, wan kinonan sek tekwanim wan totom yewal Dyos okinmit chihchipawak kinchichinok kina tatamakal.
Kwah kinehnekwi Dyos in WeTatsDyos ahwiyaliste kina kwal ahwiyaya, kwakin mo'ili: “Amo'ik nihkwepas ten amokwal kiyaptiyas tal ka inintachiwaliste takam kampa ininyolme amo kwahkwalme pa kimani takatil pa kimani mikil, amo'ik nihwalkwepas pa kinshitinis mochi kishki kipiyal yoliliste kina ashka onikchi.
”Pa kishki tonatim yes tal,
in tonatim wan mestim ka sewaliste wan tonaliste,
tonalko wan sewalko,
wan niyok yeske tahka wan tayoway.”
Dyos okichi tahtoliste ka No'á
Dyos kimashti No'á wan ininpilwam wan kinmili: “Shikinmiyapti anmopilwam, wan shiktemiltik pa mochital.
Wan mochi tekwanim wan totom pa ilwikak wan mochi inik mowilanal ipa tal wan mochi michim pa we'at momaptiske ininishpa takam. Annimishmak pa ankichiwaske ten ka yehwante.
Mochiten yewal yolil wan molinil, annimishmak pa ankikwaske. Niyok annimishmak tatokaliste. Annimishmak mochiten.
Ma yok, amo ankikwaske nakat kipiyas yEste, amo shikwak kampa yEste kipi yoliliste.
Newal niktahtanis tahtolme aki tamiktis, ta se tekwan okimikti se takat, in tekwan kipi pa mikis wan ta se takat tamikti niyok kipi pa mikis.
”Ta ak tamikti,
kampa in masewal ye tachiwal
kina Dyos tachiwal.
“Wan anmehwante annimichilis, shimomiyaptik shikinpiyak anmopilwam pa anyeske myak pa tal.”
Dyos kili No'á wan ininpilwam, wan kinmili:
“Newal niktali notahtoliste ka anmehwante, ka anmokolinchim yehwante antakatiske,
wan ka mochi tekwanim yehwante kat ka anmehwante, mochi kishki kisak pa kal: totom, wan tekwanim yolil ka takam wan tekwanim yolil pa kwawim ka mochi yewal yolil pa mochital.
Niktalis notahtoliste ka anmehwante: amo'ik nikinshitinis inik kinpiyal mochi yoliliste ka se tapakyawaliste; amo'ik oksep yes tapakyawaliste pa yok amo kishitinis tal.”
Wan Dyos kito: “Ina nitaneshtiliste ka tahtoliste yewal newal niktali ka newal wan ka anmehwante wan mochiten yolil ka tehwante:
Ashka oniktal nokosamalot arko pa ayawim, ina yes taneshtiliste ka tahtoliste ka newal wan ka tal.
Kwah nihwalika ayawim pa takpakIlwikak ipa mochital, wan moneshti nokosamalot arko pa ayawim,
Kwah nokosamalot arko yes pa ayawim, newal nikitas wan nikilnamikis notahtoliste inak Dyos wan mochi yolikilme ipa mochital.”
Kili Dyos No'á: “Ina nitaneshtiliste ka tahtoliste oniktal pa mochi inik yolinilme onka ipa mochital.”
Ininpilwam No'á
Ininpilwam No'á okisak pa arka yek Shem, Kam wan Yapet. Kam, oye nitats Kanán.
Inik yek ininpilwam No'á ka yehwante takatik in nikolinchim yehwante mosesemanak pa in tal.
No'á kitikipanoli tal, wan okitok se kwahmilUba.
Wan okon nihugoUbaBino otawan, wan nakatil katka pa nikal tachiwal ka shashal tilawak.
Kam, nitats Kanán, okit nitats kina katka nakatil wan oy okinmil in omente ninohniwan, katkaloya pa kiyawak.
Kwakin Shem wan Yapet okonanak se shashal, kitalilik pa niyahkwal, wan nehnemiloya ka inkwitap, kitakemiltik nitats kaha nakatil. Yok tachiyaloya oksela, pa amo kitaloskya nitats pelado nakatil.
Kwah o'is No'á ka nitawanaliste wan kimat ten okichiwil nikon tipichi,
“Ma ye amokwal Kanán!
Yes tikipanol ka tikipanoliste
ka ninohniwan.”
Niyok kito:
“Ma kimashti in WeTatsDyos, niDyos Shem!
Wan Kanán yes nitikipanol!
Ma kichiwil we Dyos nital Yapet!
Ma mochanti Yapet pa nikalme Shem yewal kat tachiwal ka shashal tilawak,
wan ma ye Kanán nitikipanol!”
Kwah wets tapakyawaliste No'á yolti 350 shiwim,
Nikolinchim ka ininpilwam No'á.
Inik nikolinchim Shem, Kam wan Yapet, ininpilwam No'á, yehwante niyok okinpiyak ininpilwam kwah otam in tapakyawaliste.
Ininpilwam Yapet yek Gómer, Magog, Maday, Yawán, Tubal, Meshek wan Tirás.
Ininpilwam Gómer yek Ashkenas, Ripat wan Togarmá.
Ininpilwam Yawán yek Elishá, Tarshish, Kitem wan Rodanín.
Ka inik takam mochantik pa itehtenko wehwe'atim, kina sesen tanichikolme ka tahtolme pa sesen talme ka inintahwan.
Ininpilwam Kam yek Kush, Misrayim, Put wan Kanán.
Ininpilwam Kush yek Shebá, Hawilá, Sabtá, Rahma wan Sabteká.Inik yek ininpilwam Rahmá: Shebá wan Dedán.
Wan Kush okitakatilti Nimrod, aki omochi takat ka chikawaliste ka momiktiliste pa tal,
Dyos in WeTatsDyos okichi se takat ka chikawaliste pa ta'asiskya yewal kintemowaya yolikilme, kwakin kililoya takam: “Kina Nimrod in takat chikawak yewal kintemowaya yolikilme kinmiktiyaya, yok kinek i'ishpa Dyos in WeTatsDyos.”
Pa in tal okis pa Asirya wan okichi Wepweblo' Níniwe, Rehobot, Kala.
Wan Resen, katka pa Níniwe wan Kala katka nipwebloWe.
Misrayim okitakatilti in ludeteko' wan in anameyo' wan in lehabiteko' wan in napetuteko',
wan in patrusteko' wan in kasluhíta' wan in kaptorteko' kaha kisak peleshteko'.
Wan Kanán okitakatilti Tsidón, oye nikon ta'ishpa wan Het,
wan in yebuseyo' wan in amoreteko' wan in girgasheteko'
wan in heweteko' wan in arakiteko' wan in sinteko'
wan in arwadeyo' wan in semareyo' wan in hamateko'.
Panok tonatim mosesemanak ka inintahwan inik kananeyo'.
Wan in kananeyo' inintal mosesemanak wan asik pa Tsidón han, pa Gerar wan Gasa, wan niyok pa Sodoma, Gomora, Admá, Tseboyím wan niyok pa Lesa.
Niwichalme Shem, Shem katkaloya nitats pa moshte ininpilwam Heber, wan ninohni ta'ishpa Yapet.
Ininpilwam Shem yek Elam, Ashur, Arpashad, Lud wan Aram.
Wan ininpilwam Aram yek Uts, Hul, Géter wan Mash.
Arpashad okitakatilti Shelá.Wan Shelá okitakatilti Heber.
Wan Heber okinpi ome ininpilwam: ta'ishpa se itoka Péleg, kampa pa inik tonatim inik takam motemakak tahtahko tal; ninohni tipichi itoka Yoktán.
Wan Yoktán okitakatilti Almodad, Shélep, Hasar-máwet wan Yéra,
Hadoram, Usal, Diklá,
Obal, AbiMa'el, Shebá,
Ofir, Hawilá wan Yobab. Moshte yek ininpilwam Yoktán,
wan pa tal kaha mochantiloya katka pa Masha pa ni'ot Separ, katka pa talTepet kaha kis tonat.
Inik oyek inintahwan ka ininpilwam No'á, kina takatiloya nikolinchim wan ininpweblo'. Ka inik mosesemanak pa ininpweblo' pa yaloskya mochantiloskya pa mochital kwah otam tapakyawaliste.
Kichiwak kal weyak pa Babel
Moshte takam pa mochital tahtoloya ka se tahtol.
Kwakin opanotiyak kaha kis tonat, wan okitak se tal ishtawak pa Shinar, ompa omokawak mochantitiyak.
Pa se tonat mo'ilik sek ka oksek: “Toyak tikchiwak ladriyo, wan tikinyokshitiske pa teshoshte.” Yok kwakin kiteshmonekik tal tachichinol ladriyo amo kiteshmonekik tetelme, wan niyok kiteshmonekik chapopote-tsakte amo kiteshmonekik tal tashakwalil.
Kwakin mo'ilik sek ka oksek: “Ma tikchiwak se Wepweblo ka se kal takpak asis pa ilwikak. Yok timochiwaske ka monotsaliste yok amo timosesemanaske pa mochital.”
Wan temo Dyos in WeTatsDyos pa kitaskya Wepweblo wan ka se kal takpak kampa takam kalchiptikatkaloya,
kito WeTatsDyos: “Nika pweblo se han wan moshte kipiyal se han tahtol, wan kipewaltik kalchiwaliste wan amoten kintsakwili kina tamatitikat.
Ma tiyak ma titemok pa tikinpololtiske inintahtolme, yok amo kimatiske ten kinekiske kitoske.”
Yok kinsesemanalti WeTatsDyos pa mochital, wan mokawak amo kichiwak Wepweblo.
Nikolinchim Shem
Inik nitapowaliste Shem:
Shem kipiyaya 100 shiwim, okitakatilti Arpashad, kwah panowaya ome shiwim kwah ye tapakyawaliste.
Kwah otakat Arpashad, Shem yolti 500 shiwim, wan okinpi oksek ininpilwaTakam wan ininpilwaSiwam.
Arpashad yolti 35 shiwim, kwah okitakatilti Shelá.
Kwah otakat Shelá, Arpashad yolti 403 shiwim, wan okinpi oksek ininpilwaTakam wan ininpilwaSiwam.
Shelá yolti 30 shiwim, kwah okitakatilti Heber.
Kwah otakat Heber, yolti Shelá 403 shiwim, wan okinpi oksek ininpilwaTakam wan ininpilwaSiwam.
Kwah Heber kipiyaya 34 shiwim, kwah okitakatilti Péleg.
Kwah okitakatilti Péleg, kwakin Heber yolti oksek 430 shiwim, wan okinpi oksek ininpilwaTakam wan ininpilwaSiwam.
Wan Péleg yolti 209 shiwim, kwah okitakatilti Rehu, wan okinpi oksek ininpilwaTakam wan ininpilwaSiwam.
Rehu yolti 32 shiwim, kwah okitakatilti Serug.
Kwah otakat Serug, Rehu kipiyaya 207 shiwim kwah okinpi oksek ininpilwaTakam wan ininpilwaSiwam.
Serug yolti 30 shiwim, kwah okitakatilti Nahor.
Kwah otakat Nahor, Serug kipiyaya 200 shiwim, wan okinpi oksek ininpilwaTakam wan ininpilwaSiwam.
Nahor yolti 29 shiwim, kwah okitakatilti Téra.
Kwah otakat Téra, kipiyaya Nahor 119 shiwim kwah okinpi oksek ininpilwaTakam wan ininpilwaSiwam.
Téra yolti 70 shiwim, kwah okitakatilti AbRam, Nahor wan Harán.
Nikolinchim Téra
Inik nitapowaliste Téra. Téra okintakatilti AbRam, Nahor wan Harán.
wan omik Haran kimani ayamo mikiyaya nitats Téra pa tal kaha takatiyaya pa Ur inintal kaldeyo'.
Wan konanak AbRam wan Nahor ininsiwam AbRam nisiwa itoka Saray, wan Nahor nisiwa itoka Milka, nikonSiwat Harán, nitats Milka wan Yiská.
Ma yok Saray amo kintakatiltiyaya piltontim.
Wan Téra okis pa Ur in pweblo ka Kaldeyo' pa yaloskya pa tal Kanán. Wan okiwik nikon AbRam, wan nikolinche Lot (nisobrin AbRam) wan Saray nisiwamon, nisiwa AbRam nikon Téra. Ma yok, kwah asik pa in tal itoka Harán, ompa mokawak mochantitiyak,
Téra yolti 205 shiwim kwakin omik pa Harán.
Dyos okinots AbRam
Kili WeTatsDyos AbRam: “Shihka motal, wan moparyente wan nikal motahwan, wan shi pa in tal kaha nimishneshtilis.
“Wan nikchiwas pa momiyaptiske wan yeske tanichikol we,
Wan nimishmashti;
Wan nikchiwas pa mo'itok kina itok se we,
nikinmashti ak kwal anmishmashtil
wan amokwal kinyaptiyas yehwante amokwal mishnotsilil;
Wan pa tewal yeske tamashtiliste
moshte inintahwan ka ininpilwam pa mochital!”
Yok okika AbRam tal, kina kili WeTatsDyos, wan inak Lot okis pa Harán. Kipiyaya AbRam 75 shiwim kwah okis pa tal Haran.
Okiwik AbRam nisiwa Saray, wan Lot nikon ninohni, wan mochiten yewal tapiyaloya kwah katkaloya pa Harán, wan moshte kitikipanoliloya. Kwakin konanak ot pa tal Kanán wan asik pa Kanán,
AbRam pano mochital Kanán wan asi pa Sikem, kaha katka tepotskwawit itok MoriYah. Pa inik tonatim, mochantiloya kananeyo' pa in tal.
Ompa ones WeTatsDyos ka AbRam kili: “Mokolinchim nikinmakas in tal.” Wan ompa AbRam kinichiko tetelme kaha kitaliliskya tatamakal WeTatsDyos, kampa omoneshti.
Kwakin AbRam panoti pa talTepet kaha kis tonat, amo wEhka katka Wepweblo' BetEl. Ompa okital nikal tachiwal ka shashal tilawak. Katka in Wepweblo' BetEl kaha kalaki tonat wan Ay in Wepweblo' oy kaha kis in tonat. Kinichiko tetelme kaha kitaliliskya tatamakaliste WeTatsDyos wan okinots.
Kwakin AbRam panoti wan yawiya pa ot Négeb.
Oye mayanaliste pa tal kaha katka AbRam kwakin temok pa Egipto, ompa oy omochanti kampa katka miyak mayanaliste.
Kwah astiyaloya pa Egipto, AbRam kili Saray nisiwa: “Nihmat kina tewal kwal titachi wan kwal tines.
Kwah michitaske egiptiyo', kitoske: ’Yewal nisiwa’; kwakin nishmiktiske wan tewal mishkawaske pa tiyolis.
Kwakin shikinmil kampa tewal tinonohniSiwat, pa yok nishchiwiliske kwal, wan yok ika tewal wan newal amo nimikis, yok niyolis.”
O'as AbRam pa Egipto, kitatikatkaloya inik egiptiyo' kina kwal tachiyaya Saray.
Kwah kitak nitatakewalme para'ó werey, kililoya para'ó yewal kina kwal tachiyaya Saray, wan yok kikalaktik Saray pa nikal para'ó.
Wan para'ó okichiwil kwal AbRam ka yewal, okimakak ka nitanichikolme borrego', baka', burro', burra' wan kameyo' niyok tikipanolmeSiwam wan tikipanolmeTakam.
Ma yok WeTatsDyos kinpanolti takokoliste ka para'ó in we, wan yehwante ompa mochantiloya kampa Saray nisiwa AbRam mochantitikatka pa nikal para'ó.
Kwakin otatake para'ó pa kinotsaloskya AbRam wan kili: “Ten otinishchiwil? Pates amo otinichil kampa yewal mosiwa?
Pates tikito yewal monohniSiwat? Kampa yok onikonan pa yeskya nosiwa! Shikonan wan shihwik!”
Mosesemanak AbRam wan Lot
AbRam okis pa Egipto o'as pa Négeb, inak nisiwa ka mochiten tapiyaya, niyok yawiya Lot.
AbRam tapiyaya miyak, plata, oro wan yolikilme.
Okis pa Négeb, mochantitiyaya yok o'as pa BetEl, kaha ya wehkA kiketsaya nikal tachiwal ka shashal tilawak, yewal katka ipanta pa in BetEl wan Ay.
Ompa kaha AbRam kinichikowaya tetelme kaha tatamakaya ya wehkA, ompa okinots ni'itokaliste WeTatsDyos.
Niyok Lot yawiya inak AbRam niyok tapiyaya myak borrego', baka', wan kalme tachiwalme ka shashal tilawak.
Ma yok, in tal amo we katka pa mochantiloskya, kampa tapiyaloya myak yolikilme in omente.
Oye momiktiliste ika nitakwitawilme borrego' AbRam wan nitakwitawilme borrego' Lot. Niyok ompa mochantiloya kananeyo' wan in peresheyo' pa in tal.
Kwakin AbRam kili Lot: “Amo timokwalaniliske ika tehwante omente, niyok amo mokwalantiske totakwitawilme, kampa tewal wan newal timonohniwan.
Kan onka mochi in tal pa mo'ishpa. Nimishtantani kampa shi oksela ka newal. Newal nimichili ta tewal timowikas ka momahwamapoch, kwakin newal nimowikas ka momahwakwal, wan ta tewal timowikas ka momahwakwal, kwakin newal nimowikas ka momahwamapoch.”
Kwakin Lot okonan mochi ishtawak Yordán, wan panoti kaha waltakis tonat. Wan mosesemanak se ka okse.
AbRam moka mochantiti pa in tal Kanán, wan Lot moka mochantiti ipanta ni'ishtawak, wan in Wepweblo' kinkets nikalme tachiwal ka shashal tilawak amo wEhka pa Sodoma.
Kampa in masewalme mochantiloya Sodoma amokwal tamatiloya wan kichiwaloya miyak katsawiliste ika WeTatsDyos.
Wan WeTatsDyos kili AbRam kwah panoti Lot: “Shitachi kaha ti'onka, shikit nepa takpak wan nepa tatsinta wan kaha kis tonat wan kaha kalaki tonat.
Kampa mochi in tal, yewal tikitatik, nimishmakas tewal wan mokolinchim pa hanse.
Nikchiwas pa yeske mokolinchim kina nipohtiTal. Wan ta se kwal kipowaskya nipohtiTal, kwakin yok kwal kinpowaloskya mokolinchim.
Shimokets wan shinehnem pa mochital pa kishki weyak wan pa kishki patawak, kampa newal nimishmakas!”
Yok AbRam ki'ahkoki ikal tachiwal ka shashal tilawak wan oy omochanti kaha nitepotskwawim in takat itok Mamré, amo wEhka katka in Wepweblo itok Hebrón. Wan ompa kinichiko tetelme pa tatamakaliste WeTatsDyos.
AbRam kikishti Lot
Pa inik tonatim katka Amrapel Rey pa tal Shinar, Aryok Rey pa Elasar, Kedorlagamer Rey pa Elam, wan Tidál Rey pa Goyim
Inik takwitap makwil Reye' monichikok pa ishtawak Sidim, kaha onka we'atTemtik Tapoyawaltil.
Pa 12 shiwim kitekipanoliloya Kedorlagamer, pa in shiwit 13 yahmo kitekipanolik wan momiktik ika yewal.
Pa in shiwit 14 Kedorlagamer wan in reye' katkaloya inak yewal oyak wan kintanilik in repateko' pa tal Ashtarot Karnayim; wan in susiteko' pa Ham, wan in emiteko' pa ShaweKiryatayim,
wan in horeteko' mochantiloya tepetLom pa Se'ir, kintohtokak kaha ni'ishtawak Parán, yewal onka inak pa se tal kaha tawak.
Kwakin mokwepak, wan oyak pa EnMishpat, yewal niyok itoka Kadésh, wan kintashitinilik mochiten in amalekteko', wan niyok in amoreteko' yehwante mochantiloya pa HasesónTamar.
Kwakin kisak in Rey pa Sodoma, Rey pa Gomora, Rey pa Admá, Rey pa Tseboyím wan in Rey pa Bela, yewal in Tso'ar, wan oyak momiktik ika yehwante pa ishtawak Sidim
inak in, Kedorlagamer Rey pa Elam, Tidál Rey pa Goyim, Amrapel Rey pa Shinar, wan Aryok Rey pa Elasar. Katkaloya nawi reye' wan momiktik ika makwil reye'.
Wan in ishtawak Sidim katkaloya myak kohkoyonke ka chapopote, kwah chololoya inik reye' Sodoma wan Gomora, sek wetsik pa in kokoyonke wan oksek motatik tepetLom.
Kwakin inik nawi reye' tawikak mochi takwaliste, wan mochiten tapiyaloya pa Sodoma wan Gomora, wan panotiyak.
Niyok kiwikak Lot, yewal nikon ninohni AbRam, yewal mochantiyaya pa Sodoma, wan mochiten tapiyaya wan panotiyak.
Kwah kimat AbRam kina kikitskik nikon Lot ninohni, okinnots 318 inintikipanolme yehwante takatik icha, wan kintohtokak pa in pweblo Dan.
Kwah tayoway AbRam wan inintikipanolme kinasik in nawi reye' wan momiktik, kwakin yehwante kintohtokak pa Hobá, panoti nepa takpak pa Damasko.
Okonan mochiten yewal ta'ishtikiloya inik nawi reye' wan niyok Lot, yewal nikon ninohni, ka mochiten tapiyaya, niyok kinwalikak siwam wan oksek masewalme.
Kwah walmokwepaya AbRam kwah kitaniliyaya Kedorlagamer ka inik reye' yehwante kipalewiloya, okis in rey pa Sodoma okinamik pa in ishtawak Shawé, yewal ni'ishtawak in rey.
Kwakin Melkisedek, katka Rey pa Shalem wan niTotats ka in Dyos HyeroTakpak, okiwalik pan wan nihugoUbaBino.
Wan kimashti AbRam, kiliyaya:
“Ma ye in Dyos HyeroTakpak,
in yewal okichi ilwikak wan in mochital,
ma kimashti kwal AbRam!
Wan ma ye ka tamawishtiliste in Dyos HyeroTakpak,
Kwakin AbRam okimak Melkisedek in matahti pa sesen mochiten nitapehpenaliste.
Kwakin in Rey pa Sodoma kili AbRam:
―Shinishkwepil in masewalme wan tewal shimotakawil mochiten.
Kinankili AbRam in Rey pa Sodoma:
―Onitemak notahtoliste pa WeTatsDyos, in Dyos HyeroTakpak, yewal okichi ilwikak wan mochital,
pa amo nikonanas amoten ka tewal, se ikpal, se mekatonte pa se warach. Pa yok amo tikitos: “Onikchi AbRam se takat ka miyak tomi.”
Nikonanas yewal han ten kikwak notakam. Wan niyok yehwante konanaske nipanta Aner, Eshkol wan Mamré kampa yaloya yehwante nonak.
Dyos kitiniwili se nikon AbRam
Kimani pano in, WeTatsDyos okinots AbRam tachiyaya kina tatimiktiyaskya kili:
“Amo shimomapti, AbRam.
wan hyero we yes motashtawaliste.”
AbRam kinankili:
―WeTatsDyos wan Dyos, pates tinishmakas ta amo nikinpi nopilwam, wan yewal ak motakawilis pa no'icha kwah nimikis yewal EliÉser otakat pa Damasko?
Wan niyok AbRam kito: Kampa amo otinishmak se nokon, notikipanol pa nokal motakawilis yewal ten nikpi.
Kwakin owal ka yewal nitahtolme WeTatsDyos kili:
―Motakawiliste amo yes in, se mokon tewal, yewal motakawilis.
Kwakin yewal okiwik pa kiyawak wan kili:
―Shitachi pa in ilwikak wan shikinpo in sitalme, ta kwal tikinpowas. Yok yeske mokolinchim!
AbRam okineltok WeTatsDyos, wan in WetatsDyos okit kwal ka nitaneltokaliste.
Wan WeTatsDyos niyok kili:
AbRam kinankili:
―WeTatsDyos wan Dyos, kina nihmatis kampa newal yes notakawaliste?
Wan in WeTatsDyos, kili:
―Shinishwalikil se beserra, se chiba wan se borrego, kinpiyaske sesen yey shiwim, wan se poporishit wan se wilotonte.
AbRam kinkitske mochi inik yolikilme, wan okintek ipanta, wan okintal nitahko pa se nimapochmahwa wan okse pa nimahwakwal, in totom amo okintek ipanta.
Kwakin tsopilom temoloya ipa yolikilme mihmiki, wan AbRam kinmahmaptiyaya.
Tamalinti tonat, okoch chikawak AbRam, wan tamakasiyaya miyak kampa panowaya se tayowaliste ipa yewal.
Kwakin WeTatsDyos kili AbRam:
―Shihmat kampa mokolinchim yaske mochantiske pa se tal yewal amo inintal, pa in tal kintikipanoltiske amo kintashtawiliske wan hyero kinkokoltiske pa 400 shiwim.
Newal niyok nikinchiwilis takokoliste inik masewalme pa in tal yehwante kintikipanoltik, wan kimani panos in, mokolinchim kisaske ompa ka miyak mochiten tapiyaske.
Wan mokwepaske kwah yahmo yoltiyaske ininwichalme, ininkolinchim, inintahwan wan ininpilwam walmokwepaske nika pa in tal ininwichalme, kampa inintakokoliste in amoreteko' ayamo'ok kinasis in tonat yewal newal nikinkishtilis in tal pa nikinmakas mokolinchim.
Wan panowaya in, kwah tamalin tonat wan waltayoway, nesiyaya se komit ka tikol popokatiyaya wan teshoshte ka okot panowaya itsalaYolikilme tahtahko.
Pa in tonat okichi in WeTatsDyos se tahtoliste ka AbRam kili:
―Nikinmakas mokolinchim in tal, pa in atenko Egipto wan pa in we atenko, in Éprates.
Ka inintal in keniteko', in kenisita', in kadmoneyo',
In heteteko', in peresheyo', in repateko',
in amoreteko, in kananeyo', in girgasheteko' wan in yebuseyo'.
Hagar wan Yishma'El
Saray, nisiwa AbRam amokwal kinpiyaskya ininpilwam. Wan kipiyaya se nitikipanolSiwat egiptiya itoka Hagar,
kwakin Saray kili AbRam:
AbRam kichi in yewal ten kili Saray.
Kimani kipiyaya matahti shiwim AbRam kampa mochantitikatkaya pa tal Kanán; Saray nisiwa AbRam, okonan Hagar nitikipanolSiwat wan okimak pa yeskya nisiwa AbRam nitaka.
AbRam omotek inak Hagar, wan in siwat ta'apa ostitikatka. Kimani kimati Hagar kampa kipiyaskya se nikon, amo kimawistiliyaya Saray niWetatakewan.
Kwakin Saray kili AbRam:
―Pa tewal nipanotik in! Kampa Hagar amo nishmawishtilitik, nimishmak pa yeskya mosiwa wan ashka okimat kampa kipiyas se nikon ashka wetamat. Ma yok Dyos ma kit akyewal kipi takokoliste ika tewal wan newal!
AbRam kinankili Saray:
―Shikit Hagar yewal motikipanolSiwat onka ka tewal. Shikchi pa yewal kina tihnekis.
Wan kina Saray hyero kichiwiliyaya pa hanse tonatim, kwakin ochol Hagar.
In Nitanawatilanhel WeTatsDyos kinamik Hagar kaha nalkistikatka at pa se tal kaha tawak, yewal in nalkistik at onka pa in ot Shur,
wan kili:
Wan Hagar kinankili:
―Nicholoti kaha amo yes nowetatakewan Saray.
NitanawatilanhelDyos kili:
―Shimokwep ka mowetatakewan wan shineltok pa mochiten.
Niyok kili nitanawatilanhel: Nikinmiyaptis mokolinchim, kampa amokwal kina kinpowaske.
In nitanawatilanhel in WeTatsDyos kili: “Ashka ti'ostitik tita'apapti, wan tikpiyas se mokonTakat,
tiktokayoltis Yishma'El,
kampa in WeTatsDyos kimat kina timoyolkokotik.
In mokon tewal yes kina se burro yewal amo kipi niwetatakewan.
Momiktis ka moshte, wan moshte momiktiske ika yewal;
yok yewal mochanti i'ishpa ninohniwam.”
Kina WeTatsDyos kiliyaya, yewal yok okitokayolti “Tewal tiDyos yewal titachi”, kampa kito: “Ashka onikit Dyos yewal nichit newal.”
Wan in nalkistik at moka ika Kadésh wan Béred, yewal kitokayolti Beer-Lahay-Roy in kinek kili: “Takoyonaliste Dyos yewal yoltik wan nichit.”
Hagar okitakatilti se nikonTakat, ka AbRam wan yewal okitokayolti Yishma'El.
Wan AbRam kipiyaya 86 shiwim kwah Hagar okitakatilti Yishma'El.
Nitatekiliste ikwerit itenko kaha mashishal, kina taneshtiliste ka se taketsaliste
AbRam kipiya 99 shiwim, kimani omoneshti in WeTatsDyos wan kili:
―Newal ninewal in Dyos chikawaliste. Shiyolti hanse pa no'ishpa newal wan kwal shikchipti.
Newal nikchiwas se taketsaliste pa tewal, wan nikchiwas pa momiyaptiske mokolinchim.
Kwakin motankwakets AbRam wan Dyos otahto inak yewal wan kili:
Yahmo ti'itokas AbRam, ashka timo'itokas AbRaham, kampa onimishchi pa tiyes inintats myak masewalme.
Newal nikchiwas pa timomiyaptis pa tewal yeske myak tanichikolme ka masewalme wan yeske WeReye'.
Ka in taketsaliste yewal nikchi ka tewal wan ka mokolinchim, ina yes se taketsaliste pa amo'ik tamis. Wan newal niyes nimoDyos wan iniDyos mokolinchim.
Wan nimishmakas tewal wan mokolinchim, mochital kampa ashka timochanti in tal Kanán, kina se takawaliste pa hanse, wan newal niyes ininDyos ka yehwante.
Dyos kili AbRaham:
―Tewal, tikchiwas kina in taketsaliste, wan moshte mokolinchim yehwante takatitiwalaske.
Ina yewal notaketsaliste nikchi ka anmehwante, moshte takam pa anmehwante ankipiyaske pa anyeske takotonilme nikwerit kaha mashishal.<sup>a</sup>
Anmehwante takam ankipiyaske pa yeske takotonilme nikwerit kaha mashishal, kina nitaneshtiliste in taketsaliste ika tehwante.
Kwah monamikiske chikweyi tonatim, yeske takotonilme nikwerit kaha mashishal moshte takam yehwante mochantilme ka anmehwante, wan niyok yehwante anmokowilik ka anmotomi wan amo monotsalme.
Yeske takotonilme nikwerit kaha mashishal yehwante takatik pa anmokal, wan yewal ankinkowak ka anmotomi, notaketsaliste yes pa in nakat pa anmehwante yewal amo'ik tamis.
Dyos niyok kili AbRaham:
―Mosiwa Saray, amo tihnotsa Saray, ashka mo'itokas Sara.
Newal nihmashtis, wan niyok nimishmakas se nikon pa yewal. Newal nihmashtis wan yewal yes ininnantsi pa myak tanichikoliste pa Wepweblo', inik WeReye' wan inik pweblo' pa yewal takatiske.
Kwakin omotankwakets AbRaham pa tal, wan okipakti wan omo'il pa niyol: “Ten aso se takat yewal kipi 100 shiwim, okitakatilti se nikon? Wan aso kipiyas Sara se nikon yewal kipi 90 shiwim?”
AbRaham kili Dyos:
―Ta Yishma'El yoliskya pa mo'ishpa tewal!
Kinankili Dyos:
―Yewal ten nikito kampa in Sara mosiwa, mishmakas se nikon, wan tewal tiktokayoltis Itsak! Wan melak niktalis notaketsaliste inak yewal kina se taketsaliste yewal amo'ik tamis pa nikolinchim, yehwante takatitiwalaske.
Pa kishki Yishma'El, niyok onimishkak. Wan newal nihmashti, wan nikchiwas pa momiyaptiske myak nikolinchim. Yewal yes inintats pa 12 wehwetatakewalme. Wan newal nikchiwilis pa mochiwas se Wepweblo.
Ma notaketsaliste niktalis pa Itsak, in piltonte yewal Sara mishmakas kwah monamikiske pa inik tonatim, pa okse shiwit.
Pa in se tonat okonan AbRaham nikon Yishma'El, wan kikotonili nikwerit kaha mashishal, wan moshte yehwante inintikipanolme takatilme pa nikal wan moshte yehwante omokowil ka nitomi; in kinek kito, ankipiyaske nakat takotonilme nikwerit kaha mashishal pa moshte takam yehwante mochantilme pa mokal, yok kina Dyos kiliyaya.
AbRaham kipiyaya 99 shiwim kwah kikotonilik nikwerit kaha mashishal,
Yishma'El, in ikon kipiyaya 13 shiwim kwah kikotonilik nikwerit kaha mashishal.
Ikon in Yishma'El yek takotonilil nikwerit kaha mashishal pa in se tonat
inak yewal yek takotonilme ininkwerit kaha mashishal moshte takam kishki katkaloya pa nikal, yok kina inintikipanolme takatilme pa nikal yewal niyok takowalme katkaloya pa okse tal.
Dyos kitiniwili se nikon AbRaham
Moneshti in WeTatsDyos ka AbRaham amo wEhka katkaloya nitepotskwawim Mamré, kwah moseptikatka pa tatapoli pa nikal tachiwal ka shashal tilawak, kwah hyero tona pa tahka.
Otachi AbRaham, wan yewal okinmit yey takam moketstikatkaloya ka tamawishtiliste. Kwah okinmit, hani mokets pa in tatapoli pa nikal pa kinnamikiskya. Motankwakets pa tal,
wan kito:
―Tats, ta tihnek tikchiwas kwal pa newal, amo shipan hanse pa motikipanol newal.
Ma nihwalik pan pa ankikwaske, pa konanaske chikawaliste kwakin anmowikaske pa anmo'ot. Kampa anasik anmehwante pa no'icha newal anmotikipanol.
Yehwante kinnankilik:
―Kwal onka, shikchi kina tikito!
Yok AbRaham mo'isiwilte okalak pa nikal tachiwal ka shashal tilawak kaha katka Sara, wan kili:
―Shikonan yey tamachiwiliste arina kwahkwal han, wan shikshakwal shikchi pan.
Kwakin motalo AbRaham kaha katkaloya yolikilme, okonan se beserro tipichi, wan okimak se nitikipanol, yewal mo'isiwiltiyaya pa kiyokshitiskya.
Wan okonan AbRaham keso wan lech wan nakat yewal okiyokshit. Wan okintalil pa ininishpa yehwante, wan yewal moka moketstik inak yehwante, itsinta kwawit.
Yehwante kitahtanilik:
―Kaha onka mosiwa Sara?
AbRaham kinankili:
Kwakin se ka yehwante kili AbRaham:
―Melak niwalmokwepas ka tewal, kwah monamikiske inik tonatim pa okse shiwit wan Sara kipiyas se nikon.
Takaktikatka Sara pa kalitik in kal, yewal katka ikwitap AbRaham.
AbRaham wan Sara wehwe katkaloya wan myak shiwim kipiyaloya, wan Sara yahmo ki'asiyaya nimeste.
Kampa okipakti Sara pa'itik yewal mo'ili: “Kwah nika nisiwat we, wan notaka we, niyok nikpiyas newal in pakiliste?”
Kwakin in WeTatsDyos kili AbRaham:
―Pates wetska Sara wan tamat? Melak nikpiyas se nokon ashka kampa niwe, ka myak shiwim?
Ten aso in WeTatsDyos amo kimat kichi? Newal niwalmokwepas ka tewal pa in tonat pa okse shiwit, wan kipiyas Sara se nikon.
Sara, momapti wan yewal otikwaman kampa yok okit:
―Newal amo niwetskatikatka.
―Newal nihmat kampa melak otiwetska.
AbRaham kitahtani Dyos pa amo kishitinis Sodoma
Inik pashalolme mowikak pa ni'ot wan otachiyak pa tatsinta pa Sodoma. AbRaham yawiya inak yehwante.
Kwakin in WeTatsDyos kito: “Aso niktatilis AbRaham in yewal ten nikchiwas?
AbRaham kinpiyas myak nikolinchim wan yehwante kinpiyaske miyak chikawaliste, wan ipa yewal yeske tamashtiliste moshte in tanichikolme pa mochital.
Kampa newal nihmat yok kintakewas ininpilwam wan ininkolinchim, ma konanak ni'ot in WeTatsDyos ma kichiwak kwal wan ka melawak. Pa yok newal nikashiltis pa AbRaham in ten niktiniwil.”
Kwakin in WeTatsDyos kili:
―In teshpawiliste kina kichiwal hanse tonatim yehwante pa Sodoma wan Gomora, wan ininta'ihtakoliste hyero we.
Ashka niyas wan nitemos ompa, pa nihmatis ta kichiptikat kina in tateshpawiliste yewal o'as kaha newal; ta amoyok, nihmatis.
Ome pashalolme konanak ot pa Sodoma, hanwel AbRaham moka moketstik ni'ishpa in WeTatsDyos.
―Aso tewal tikinmiktis in takam kwahkwalme ka yehwante in amokwahkwalme?
Ta kat 50 takam kwahkwalme pa in Wepweblo'. Hanwel yok tikshitinis in pweblo amo tikinihnilis ka inik 50 takam kwahkwalme yewal yoltikat ompa?
Tewal amoyok tikchiwaskya! Amo tihmiktiskya se kwal inak se ta'ihtakol, wan tikchiwaskya kampa nesiskya se kwal kina inak se ta'ihtakol? Amoyok tikchiwaskya! In tatakewan hwes pa mochital, amo kichiwaskya ten kwal?
Kwakin in WeTatsDyos kinankili:
―Ta nikinmit pa Sodoma 50 kwahkwalme, pa yehwante nikinihnili moshte kishki yeske ompa.
Kwakin AbRaham oksep kito:
―Nika ni'onka ashka, amo nimonots pa nitahtos ka WeTatsDyos, han nipohti wan nineshte.
Ta amo yeloskya 50, ta moteshmonekiloskya makwil. Kwakin tikshitiniskya in Wepweblo kampa moteshmonekiloya in makwil?
WeTatsDyos kito:
―Amo nikshitinis, ta nikinmit 45 kwahkwalme.
―Ta hanwel kat 40?
WeTatsDyos kinankili:
―Ta kat 40 takam kwahkwalme, amo nikinshitinis!
Oksep AbRaham kito:
―NoTats amo shikwalan, ta oksep onitahto. Ta han tikinmit 30.
WeTatsDyos kinankili:
―Amo nikshitinis, ta nikinmit 30.
AbRaham kito:
―Nika ni'onka ashka, amo nimonots pa nitahtos ka noTats, ta hanwel tikinmit 20.
Wan WeTatsDyos kinankili:
Kwakin oksep AbRaham kito:
―NoWeTatsDyos amo shikwalan, ta oksep onitahto. Ta hanwel tikinmit matahti, tikshitinis.
WeTatsDyos kinankili:
―Amo nikshitinis, ta kat matahti takam kwahkwalme.
Kwah otam otahto in WeTatsDyos ka AbRaham, panoti ompa, wan AbRaham omokwep pa nikal.
Tashitiniliste pa Sodoma wan Gomora
Pa tyotak asik omente nitanawatilanhelme pa Sodoma. Lot yowatikatka pa in tatapoli Sodoma. Yok kwah okinmit, omokets oy okintenamik omotankwakwets pa talpa.
Wan kito:
―Takam, annimichilis, shiwalak no'icha newal anmotikipanol. Kampa anmopakaske anmoshiwam, wan anpanoske in yowal kwakin yok mosta kwalka ankonanaske anmo'ot.
Yehwante kinankilik:
Lot kintahtani ka miyak chikawaliste pa mokawaloskya, yehwante oyak inak yewal. Kwah kalakik pa nikal. Kinyokshitil se takwaliste kwal ika pan kati amo kipiyaya ka motapotsawalti, wan yehwante otakwak.
Kwah ayamo'ok motekaloya pa kochiloskya, inik takam pa in Wepweblo kiyawalok kal. Ompa monichikok moshte takam pa Sodoma, in yahyankwik wan moshte wehwe.
Kinotsak Lot kilik:
―Kampa kat in takam yewal asik mo'icha pa tyotak? Shikinkishti pa kiyawak! Pa yok timotekaske inak yehwante!
Okis Lot pa kiyawak pa tahtoskya inak yehwante, haniman kitsakwa in tatapoli,
wan kinmili:
―Nonihnihwan nahnewal, newal annimishtahtani amo shikchiwak in ten hyero amokwal.
Newal nikinpi ome nopilwaSiwam yehwante ayamo motekal ka takam; annimishwalikili anmehwante wan shikinchiwilik kina ankinekil, amo shikinkwesok in takam, kampa kat no'icha kampa yehwante nikinkwitaptik pa amoten kinpanos.
Yehwante kinankilik:
―Shime!
―In se owal pa topweblo se yewal amo otakat nika, wan ashka kinek niyok tishahwa. Ashka timishchiwiliske hyero amoyok kina yehwante!
Wan kitopewaloya Lot wan monichikok pa kitopewaloskya in tatapoli.
Kwakin in pashalolme kikishtik ininmahwam, wan kitilanak pa kalitik Lot ka yehwante kitsakwak in nitatapoli.
Wan inik takam yewal katkaloya pa tatapoli pa in kal moshte takam yahyankwik wan moshte wehwe amokwal kina tachiyaloskya, wan yehwante kitemotinemil tatapoli wan osiyawik.
Kwakin in omente takam kilik Lot:
―Tikinpi oksek pa in Wepweblo' anmonohniwan? AnmopilwaSiwam ka inintakam, anmopilwaTakam, mochiten tikpi pa in Wepweblo' shikinkishti wEhka,
kampa tehwante tikshitiniske in tal nahyehwante. Kampa in WeTatsDyos, kikaki kampa onka miyak ta'ihtakoliste. Otishtake pa tikshitiniske.
Yok okis Lot wan okinnots ininimon, inik yehwante monamiktiloskya ka ininpilwaSiwam wan kinmili:
―Shimoketsak! Shikisak pa in Wepweblo, kampa in WeTatsDyos kishitinis!
Wan ininimon tamatiloya kampa hanya han kitotikatka,
―Shimokets, wan shikinwik mosiwa wan in omente mopilwasiwam, yehwante nika kat, pa amo anpoliwiske kwah Dyos kitamiltis in Wepweblo.
Yolikit mochiptikatka Lot pa kisaskya, kwakin inik takam kinkitskik Lot pa nimahwam, nisiwa wan in omente ininpilwaSiwam, wan kinwikak pa wEhka in Wepweblo, kinkishtitikatkaloya pa in polewiliste, kampa in WeTatsDyos ki'ihniliyaya yewal.
Kwah kinkishtik, kilik:
―Shimotal, shimokishtil yoliliste, pa amo anmishasi! Amo shitachi pa takwitap wan amo shimokets pa in ishtawak. Shicholok pa in tepetLom, pa amo anpoliwiske!
Lot kinmili:
―Takam nahnewal, nimishtamachi, amo shinishchiwilik yok.
Newal anmotikipanol onikit kina annishchiwilik kwal, kina annishkishtik pa in polewiliste ka noyoliliste. Ma yok amokwal nicholos pa in talTepet, in tashitiniliste nishasis wan nipolewis.
Shikit in Wepweblo, amo wEhka onka wan tipichi! Niyas ompa yok niyolis! Kampa melak ta tipichi?
Wan yewal kinankili:
―Nimishchiwilis in yewal tinishtahtan. Amo nikshitinis in Wepweblo tipichi yewal otinichil.
Kwakin okitokayolti in Wepweblo Tso'ar.
Kwah waltakis tonat ipa tal Lot o'as pa Tso'ar.
Kwakin in WeTatsDyos kiwaltitan pa in takpakIlwikak teshoshte wan asufre ipa Sodoma wan Gomora.
Wan kinshitin inik Wehwepweblo' wan mochi in ishtawak inak moshte yehwante ompa yoliloya pa in Wehwepweblo', wan mochi kwawim takiloya pa in tal.
Wan nisiwa Lot otachi pa takwitap, wan omoka kina se takopinal ka tet poshak ka istat.
Mostatik AbRaham omokets omokwep kaha takets pa i'ishpa WeTatsDyos.
Kwah otachi pa Sodoma wan Gomora, pa mochital ishtawak, okit kampa in tal popokatikatka, katka kina ipohti se teshoshte hyero we.
Kwah Dyos kinshitini in Wehwepweblo' pa in ishtawak, kaha Lot mochantiyaya ki'ilnamik AbRaham, wan kikishti Lot pa kiyawak pa in tashitinililiste.
Lot wan ininpilwaSiwam
Tamakas Lot pa mokawaskya pa Tso'ar, yok okis wan panoti pa talTepet. Wan ompa omoka mochantiti pa se kweba inak in omente ininpilwaSiwam.
―Totats ya we, wan amo kat takam pa motekaske ka tehwante, kina kichiwal moshte pa mochi kishki tal.
Ma tiktawantik totats ka nihugoUbaBino, timotekaske inak yewal; yok tikinpiyaske topilwam ka totats.
Pa in tayoway kimakak nihugoUbaBino nitats, kitawantik wan nikonSiwat we okalak wan omotek ka nitats, wan amo kimat Lot kwah omotek nikon wesiwat, amo kimat kwah omokets.
Mostatik kili ninohniSiwat tipichi:
―Yalwa tayo onimotek inak notats. Ma tihmakak nihugoUbaBino niyok pa in yowal, pa ashka tewal tiyas timotekas inak yewal; yok tikinpiyaske topilwam pa totats.
Pa in yowal niyok kimakak nihugoUbaBino intats, wan nikonSiwat tipichi oy wan omotek inak yewal wan yewal amo kimat kimani omotek yewal, pa kimani omokets.
Wan yok in omente ininpilwaSiwam ka Lot ta'ostiloya ta'apawak ka nitats.
In we nikonSiwat okipi se nikonTakat, okitokayolti Mo'Ab, yewal oye inintats mo'abteko'.
Niyok ninohniSiwat okitakatilti se nikonTakat, wan okitokayolti Ben-amí, yewal oye inintats Amoniteko'.
AbRaham wan AbiMélek
ompa kinmiliyaya AbRaham moshte kampa Sara, katka ninohniSiwat. Kwakin in werey Gerar yewal itok AbiMélek okintake pa kiwikililoskya Sara pa yeskya nisiwa.
Kwakin Dyos owal pa se tatemikiliste pa AbiMélek pa se yowal kili:
―Tewal timikis kampa otikonan in siwat yewal tasiyawatil.
AbiMélek ayamo kochiyaya inak Sara, kito:
―Tats, tihmikti se takat yewal amo kichi takokoliste?
Amo nichili yewal, yewal nonohniSiwat, wan niyok yewal nichili, yewal nonohniTakat yok newal nikchi kwal pa noyol wan amo nikchi ten amokwal.
Wan Dyos kili pa in tatemikiliste:
―Newal nihmat kampa tewal otikchi in wan amo timotishpawilitikatka moyol nitamatiliste; kampa in nimishtsakwil pa amo tikchiwas takokoliste ka yewal, wan niyok amo tinishchiwiliskya katsawiliste, kwakin amo nimishmakawalti pa tikochiskya inak yewal.
Ashka shihkwipil in takat nisiwa, kampa yewal niTaketsal nitahtolDyos wan yewal tahtanis pa tewal wan yok tiyolis. Ta amo tihkwepil, nihnek pa tihmatis kampa timikis tewal wan moshte ka tewal.
Mostatik kwalka omokets AbiMélek, wan otatake pa walaloskya moshte inintikipanolme wan melak kinmili mochi yewal ten tatemik, wan miyak momaptik.
―Ten yewal otitishchiwil! Pates otinishchiwil se ta'ihtakoliste we, yewal otishwalikil ipa newal wan ipa noreynaroliste? In yewal otikchi ka newal in ten amoyok mochi!
Niyok kili AbiMélek AbRaham:
―Kina titamatiya kwah yok otikchi in?
Wan AbRaham kinankili:
―Kampa nimo'il kampa in takam nika amo kimatil momaptil pa i'ishpa Dyos, wan nishmiktiloskya ika nosiwa.
Melak yewal nonohniSiwat, nikon notats wan amo nikon nonantsi; wan ashka nosiwa.
Kimani Dyos onishchiwil pa nimowikatinem, kwah onikis pa nikal notats, newal nikili nosiwa: “Pa moshte kaha tiyaske wan ti'astiyaske shikinmil kampa newal nimonohni.”
Kwakin AbiMélek okinwikil borrego' baka', wan tikipanolmeTakam wan tikipanolmeSiwam, wan kintemak AbRaham. Wan okikwepil AbRaham nisiwa Sara,
wan AbiMélek kili:
―Shikit nokwahmilme kat pa mota'ishpa; shimochanti kaha tihnekis.
―Nihmakatik monohni AbRaham mil tomiplata, yok timokishtiliske tehwante pa in amokwal yewal tewal timishchiwililoskya; yok moshte yehwante kat ka tewal kimatiske kampa tewal amo tikchi ten amokwal.
Kwakin AbRaham kitahtan Dyos, wan Dyos okinpahti AbiMélek nisiwa wan inintikipanolmeSiwam wan yok kinpiyak ininpilwam,
ika Sara nisiwa AbRaham, in WeTatsDyos kintsakwil kaha ta'apawal moshte in siwam pa nikal AbiMélek.
Takati Itsak
In WeTatsDyos kipashalo Sara, wan okichi pa yewal yok kina kili.
Wan Sara osti ta'apa wan okitakatilti se nikonTakat pa AbRaham katkaya kolinche, panok in tonatim omotachi yok kina Dyos kito.
Okitokayolti AbRaham nikonTakat Itsak, in piltonte yewal okitakatilti Sara.
AbRaham kikotonil nikwerit kaha mashishal nikon Itsak kwah kipiyaya chikweyi tonatim, yok kina Dyos kiliyaya.
Kimani otakat nikon Itsak AbRaham kipiyaya 100 shiwim.
Kwakin Sara kito: “Dyos onishpakilti, wan moshte yehwante kimatiske wetskaske ka newal.
Hagar wan Yishma'El kinkishtik pa nikal AbRaham
Omo'apa Itsak wan yahmo kichichiltiloya. Pa in tonat, kwah Itsak yahmo chichiyaya okichi AbRaham se mitotiliste we.
Wan Sara okit kina nikon Hagar in egiptiya okitakatilti pa AbRaham kiwetskiliyaya Itsak.
Yok Kili AbRaham:
―Shihkishti in tikipanolSiwat wan nikonTakat! Kampa nikonTakat in tikipanolSiwat amo kipiyas amoten ika nitakawaliste nokon Itsak.
Hyero tamat AbRaham kampa Yishma'El niyok katka nikon.
Ma yok Dyos kili AbRaham: “Amo hyero shitamat ka in takatYankwik ka motikipanolSiwat. Shihneltok Sara, pa mochiten kina michilis kampa ika Itsak tikinpiyas myak mokolinchim.
Niyok nikchiwas pa nikon motikipanolSiwat se pweblo, kampa mokon tewal.”
Mostatik, tahtanesti AbRaham, okimak ten pa kikwaloskya wan se kwero temi ka at, okitalil pa niyahkwal. Wan okimak piltonte okintake pa mowikaloskya. Yok panoti Hagar nehnemtinem pa in tal BérSheba pa se tal kaha tawak.
Otam in at pa in kwero, okital in piltonte itsinta se wiste.
Dyos okikak kwah chokaya piltonte, kwakin nitanawatilanhel Dyos okinots Hagar pa ilwikak wan kili: “Ten mishpano, Hagar? Amo shimomapti, kampa Dyos okikak nichokaliste piltonte.
Shimokets shikonan nimahwa mokon, kampa newal nikchiwas pa yewal se Wepweblo.”
Wan Dyos ki'ishtapol nishtololwam Hagar, wan okit se takoyonaliste ka at. Kwakin oy wan okitemilti in kwero wan okikonilti piltonte.
Dyos katka inak piltonte, wan in mo'apa; wan omochanti pa se tal kaha tawak wan oye tamotaliste ka mit;
mochantiti pa se tal kaha tawak Paran kaha ninantsi okisiyawat ka se siwat pa in tal Egipto.
Taketsaliste ika AbRaham wan AbiMélek
Pa inik tonatim AbiMélek, oy inak Pikol, yewal niwetatakewan igwacho', oy otahto ka AbRaham wan kili:
―Dyos onka ka tewal pa mochi yewal ten tikchi.
Ashka shinichil, pa i'ishpa Dyos, pa amo tinishkwamana newal, wan nopilwam wan nokolinchim. Tewal amo otitakat nika kwakin shinishchiwil kwal pa in tal kina newal onimishchiwil.
AbRaham kinankili:
Kwakin AbRaham ki'ahwa AbiMélek nahyewal nitakoyonaliste at yewal inintikipanolme AbiMélek kikishtilik.
AbiMélek kinankili:
―Amo nihmat ak yok okichi in. Amoten otichil wan ashka nihmatitik.
Okinonan AbRaham baka' wan borrego', okinmak AbiMélek wan in omente kichiwak se taketsaliste.
Wan AbRaham okinonan chikome borregito',
wan AbiMélek kitahtanili AbRaham:
―Pates tikinonan in chikome borregito'? Ten kinek kitos?
Kinankili AbRaham:
―In kinek kito kampa nimishmakas in chikome borregito'. Kampa yes kina se taneshtiliste kampa newal nitahtak nika pa nikitaskya at.
Kampa yok kitokayoltik ompa in tal BérSheba, kampa ompa in omente mochiwilik se tahtoliste.
AbRaham okitok se kwawit itok tamarisko' pa BérSheba wan ompa yewal okinots ni'itokaliste WeTatsDyos, in Dyos amo'ik tami.
Wan AbRaham mochantiti myak shiwim ompa pa inintal in peleshteko'.
Dyos kili AbRaham pa kichiwaskya ten yewal kineshtiliskya ta melak kineltokaya
Kwah panok myak tonatim, Dyos kitali ta melak taneltokaya AbRaham, wan okinots:
―AbRaham!
Wan yewal kinankili:
―Nika ni'onka!
Wan Dyos kili:
―Shikonan mokon Itsak, yewal han tikpi yewal tiktasot, wan shihwik pa tal MoriYah. Ompa shitateniwil, kina tamakaliste wan shikchichin pa in se tepetLom yewal nimishneshtilis.
Mostatik AbRaham kwalka omokets, okisiyat niburro wan okinkwik ome inintikipanolme wan nikon Itsak, okwahkwa kwakin okonan in ot kampa Dyos kili.
Kwakin AbRaham kinmili inintikipanolme:
―Shimokawak nika ka in burro. Newal wan nokon tiyaske ompa tiktankwaketsaliske Dyos, kwakin tiwalmokwepaske ka anmehwante.
Okonan AbRaham kwawit ka kichichinoskya tamakaliste wan kimamaltil Itsak, nikon; okonan teshoshte wan wildok wan panotiyak.
Kwakin Itsak kitakichili AbRaham:
―NoTats!
―Ten kwakin, nokon?
―Tikpiyal teshoshte wan in kwawit.
Kili Itsak:
―Kaha onka in borregit pa tamakaliste yewal tikchichinoske?
AbRaham kinankili:
Wan in omente hanse yaloya.
Kwah asik kaha Dyos kitatiniwili, AbRaham kinichiko tetelme kaha kitali in tamakaliste wan okital in kwawit. Wan ki'ilpi nikon Itsak okital ikpak kwawit.
Kwakin kimela nimahwa AbRaham pa kikitskiskya in wildok ka kimiktiskya nikon,
kwakin nitanawatilanhel in WeTatsDyos okinots pa in takpakIlwikak:
―AbRaham! AbRaham!
Wan yewal tanankili:
―Nika ni'onka.
In nitanawatilanhel kito:
―Amo shihmela momahwa ipa in piltonte, amoten shikchiwil. Newal nihmat kampa timomapti pa i'ishpa Dyos, kampa timochika pa tinishmakas mokonTakat in se yewal tikpi.
Kwakin otachi AbRaham, wan okit in kwawitwiste, okit se borregit' tilintikatka pa nikahilon pa in kwawitwiste, oy okiwalik okimikti wan otemak pa tamakaliste yewal okichichin wan yok amoten okichiwil nikon.
Oksep Nitanawatilanhel in WeTatsDyos okinots AbRaham pa in ilwikak,
wan kito:
―Newal in WeTatsDyos, onimo'ili wan nitemak notahtoliste, pa in ten tikchi kampa amo tishtasotil mokon in se tikpi,
newal melak nimishmashti kwal, wan nikinmiyaptis mokolinchim yeske kina sitalme pa in ilwikak wan kina in shal pa itenko in we'at. Mokolinchim mokawiliske mochi ininWepweblo' anmotakokolinilme.
Wan mokolinchim kiwalikaske tamashtiliste, Wehwepweblo pa mochi kishki tal, kampa otishneltok.
Walmokwep AbRaham kaha katkaloya inintikipanolme, wan moshte okonanak ni'ot pa BérSheba, ompa pa BérSheba omoka mochantiti AbRaham.
Ininpilwam Nahor
Kwah panok inik tonatim, kimashtik AbRaham kilik, shikit niyok Milka okimak ininpilwam monohni Nahor.
Wan kati okipewalti in takatiliste ye Uts, takwitap otakat ninohni Bus wan hani KemuEl. Yewal omochi nitats Aram,
Késed, Hasó, Pildásh, Idelap, wan BetuEl,
Niyok kipiyaya okse siwat Nahor, itoka Rehumá, okitakatilti Teba, Gáham, Tahash wan Maká.
Miki wan kitapachol Sara
Yolti Sara 127 shiwim,
omik Sara pa in Wepweblo Kiryat-arbá, yewal itok Hebrón, pa in tal Kanán. AbRaham oy okichokil Sara.
Kwah AbRaham otam okichokil nimihki Sara oy otahto ka heteteto' kinmili:
―Newal amo nika ika anmehwante; shinishnamakiltik tipit anmotal kaha niktapacho nomihki.
Inik heteteko' kinankilik AbRaham:
―Tats, shitishkak; ka tehwante tewal se niwe Dyos, shiktapach momihki pa in se tokweba yewal kwal, nimichilis kampa tihnikil pa tiktapachos momihki Teshkalkoyonke.
AbRaham omokets, omotankwakets pa i'ishpa heteteko' in pweblo pa in tal,
kinmili:
pa nishnamakiltis in kweba Makpela, yewal onka itenko nital. Shiktahtanik pa nishnamakiltis newal nitashtawas pa kishki kineki, pa yok nikpiyas kaha tikintapachoske tomihmiki.
In Eprón katka ompa, tsala in heteteko', ompa yowatikatka pa i'ishpa in heteteko wan moshte inik kalakilo kaha tatapoli pa in Wepweblo kinankili AbRaham wan kili:
―Amo, Tats newal, shinishkak. Nimishmak in kwahmil wan in kweba niyok yewal onka kalitik. Pa moshte ninishpa, inik masewalme nimishmak. Shiktapach momihki.
Kwakin AbRaham motsinkwep ka tamawishtiliste i'ishpa in masewalme pa in tal,
pa ininishpa in masewalme pa in tal kinankili Eprón, kili:
―Shinishkak, newal nitashtawas kishki ka tihnamak in kwahmil. Kwakin niktapachos ompa nomihki.
Eprón kinankili AbRaham wan kili:
―Tats newal, shinishkak. In tal nihnamak ka 400 tomiplata. Kwal onka in ka tewal wan newal? Shiktapach momihki.
Kwakin mokawak ka se tahtoliste AbRaham ka in tomi kili Eprón, wan kitamachiwilik kishki tomiplata kina okital Eprón, wan kikakik ininpilwam het: Katkaloya 400 tomiplata, kati takowaloya wan tanamakaloya pa in tal.
Yok kikowil kwahmil Eprón ompa Makpela, amo wEhka katka nital Mamré, in kinek kito, in kwahmil ka in kweba yewal katka pa yewal wan mochi kwawim yewal katkaloya pa in tal.
Kwah otam in, kwakin okitapach AbRaham nisiwa, Sara, pa in kweba nikwahmil pa Makpela amo wEhka katka nital Mamré, yewal pa in pweblo Hebrón, pa in tal Kanán.
Wan in kwahmil wan in kweba yewal ten takatka motakawil AbRaham, inik okinamakiltik heteteko'.
AbRaham kitemoli siwat Itsak
AbRaham katka kolinche kipiyaya myak shiwim, wan in WeTatsDyos kimashti kwal pa mochiten.
Wan AbRaham kili se nitikipanol yewal kolinche katka pa nikal, wan yewal niwetatakewan katka pa mochi nitomi wan pa kishki tapiyaya icha wan moshte tikipanolme:
―Shiktal momahwa itsinta nopyerna,
melak shinichil pa i'ishpa in WeTatsDyos, in Dyos pa in ilwikak wan in tal amo tikonanilis se siwat kananeyo', ka nokonTakat nika kaha timochantil tehwante
Kampa tiyas pa notal, ka nonohniwan wan ompa tikonanilis se siwat pa nokon Itsak.
NitikipanolTakat kinankili:
―Ten nikchiwas ta in siwat amo kinek walas nonawak pa in tal? Tihnek pa nihwikas mokon pa in tal kaha otikis?
―Amo'ik shihwik nokon ompa.
In WeTatsDyos, in Dyos pa in ilwikak, onishkishti pa nikal notats wan pa nital ka nonohniwan, yewal isel onishtakichil wan ka tahtol melak nichili in tal nikinmakas mokolinchim, yok yewal kiwaltitanis nitanawatilanhel pa ta'ishpa tewal wan ompa tikonanilis se siwat nokon.
Ta amo kinek walas in siwat monak, timokawas tamakawal ka in tahtol yewal otinichil; amo shihwik ompa nokon!
Kwakin nitikipanol okital nimahwa itsinta nipyerna AbRaham, niwetatakewan wan kichiwil tahtol melawak.
Kwakin okinonan matahti ikameyo' niwetatakewan, wan panoti pa ni'ot kiwikaya ka yewal myak tatemakaliste in miyak kostaro yewal kipiyaya niwetatakewan, wan asiloya pa Wepweblo Nahor pa MesoPotamya.
Okichi kampa motankwaketsaloskya kameyo' pa kiyawak in Wepweblo. Kaha temtikatka at katka tyotak, kwah kisaloya in siwam pa ta'onanaloya at.
Kwakin kito: “WeTatsDyos, niDyos nowetatakewan AbRaham, shinishmakawalti pa kisas kwal, in yewal nikchiptik ashka wan shikihnil nowetatakewan AbRaham.
Shichit nika, inak in nalkistik at, ashka ininpilwam in takam pa in Wepweblo kisal pa ta'onanaske.
Shihmakawalti yewal in siwatYankwik yewal newal nikili: “Shinishihnil, shiktemo mokom pa nikonis at”, wan yewal nishnankilis: “Shikon, wan nikinahmakas mokameyo'”, ma ye in siwatYankwik yewal tewal tikonanilis pa motikipanol Itsak. Yok nihmatis kampa tewal tikihnilitik nowetatakewan.”
Kwah ayamo'ok tamiyaya kitahtaniyaya Dyos omoneshti Rebeka, kiwalikaya nikomi pa niyahkwal. Rebeka katka nikonSiwat BetuEl, yewal katka nikonTakat Milka nisiwa Nahor, yewal ninohni AbRaham.
in tikipanol omotal kaha yewal wan kili:
―Shinishmak tipit at pa nikonis pa mokomi?
Kili:
―Shikon tats.
In siwatYankwik hani kitemowi ikomi wan oki'ahmak.
Kwah otam okinahmak, kili:
―Niyok nikinahmakas mokameyo' pa takoniske.
Motaloti okinok in at kaha takoniloya yolikilme, yawiya wan walmokwepaya wan ta'onanaya pa takoniloskya in kameyo'.
In takat omoka kitatik in siwatYankwik, amo nawatiyaya, pa kimatiskya ta in WeTatsDyos okichi pa kisaskya kwal pa ni'ot ka ten owal.
Kwah tamik takonik in kameyo', in takat okimak se aniyo tachiwal ka oro yetik katka ka chikwase gramo', niyok kimak ome yahyawaltik, tachiwal ka oro yehyetik kina 100 gramos.
―Akyewal motats wan kipi motats kaha tikochiske in tayo?
Wan yewal kinankili:
―Newal nikon BetuEl, yewal nikon Milka yewal kipi ka Nahor.
Wan niyok kili:
―Tikpiyal miyak tasol wan sakat, niyok tikpiyal kaha anpanoske in yowal.
Kwakin in takat motankwakets wan kimashti in WeTatsDyos,
wan kito: “Ma ye ka tamawishtiliste WeTatsDyos, yewal niDyos nowetatakewan AbRaham, amo'ik ki'ilka nowetatakewan ki'ihnili, wan melak onishwalik pa ot pa inikal niparyente nowetatakewan.”
Rebeka motalo pa nikal ninantsi, wan kitakichili ten kipan.
Yewal kipiya se ninohniTakat itoka Labán, wan yewal oy okinamik in takat, yewal omoka ompa kaha nalkistikatka at.
Kwah kinmitatikatka in aniyo wan in yahyawaltik pa nimahwa ninohniSiwat, wan takaktikatka kina taketstikatka ninohniSiwat kina kitowaya in takat. Labán oy okit in takat, wan moketstikatka ika kaha ta'onanal, ka nikameyo'.
Tamashti in WeTatsDyos! Pates timoketstik nika kiyawak?
Nikpi in kal kaha anmosewiske wan niyok in kameyo'!
In takat oy pa in kal, wan Labán kintatemowili in kameyo', wan kinmak tasol wan sakat, in takat wan inik yaloya inak kinmak at pa kinpakaloskya nikshiwam.
Kwah kikishtilik takwal pa takwaloskya, yewal kinmili:
―Ayamo'ok nitakwas ta ayamo annimichilis in yewal ten nikitos.
Wan Labán kili:
―Shitahto.
In takat kito:
―Ninewal nitikipanol AbRaham.
In WeTatsDyos kimashti miyak nowetatakewan wan yewal kimak myak borrego', baka', plata wan oro, tikipanolmeSiwam, tikipanolmeTakam, kameyo' wan burro'.
Wan nowetatakewan onishchiwalti melak pa ni'ishpa Dyos, wan nichili: “Amo shiksiyawat nokon ka ininpilwam Kananeyo', nika kaha timochantil.
Tiyas pa nital notats wan nonohniwan, wan ompa tikonanilis siwat nokon.”
Kwakin nowetatakewan nikili: “Wan ta in siwat amo kinek walas nonawak?”
Kwakin yewal nishnankili: “Newal hanse ninehnemtinem ka in WeTatsDyos, yok yewal kiwaltitanis nitanawatilanhel ka tewal, pa kisa kwal pa mo'ot wan tikonanili nokon se nisiwa ka nonohniwan wan pa nikal notats.
Yok titamakawal tiyes ka tahtol melawak, ta oti ka notiyahwan, wan yehwante amo mishmakal in siwatYankwik, kwakin titamakawal timokawas ka notahtol melawak.”
“Ashka kwah ni'as ka ta'onanal, nikito:
‘WeTatsDyos, niDyos nowetatakewan AbRaham, ta tewal tihnek, shikchi pa kisas kwal notikipanoliste yewal newal nikchiwas.’
Nika ni'onka ashka, ika in at kaha ta'onanal. Ta wal se siwatYankwik pa in pweblo pa ta'onanas wan nikilis:
‘Shinishmak tipit at pa mokomi,’
ta yewal nishnankili:
Ayamo'ok nitamiyaya niktahtaniyaya Dyos pa'itik noyol, onikit Rebeka walaya ka nikomi pa niyahkwal. Wan temo kaha ta'onanal, ta'onanaya. Kwakin nikili: “Nimishtahtani, shinishmak tipit at.”
Haniman yewal kitemo nikomi wan nichili: “Shikon, wan niyok nikinahmakas mokameyo'.”
Kwakin niktahtanili: “Akyewal motats?” Yewal nishnankili: “Newal nikon BetuEl, yewal nikon Nahor yewal kipi inak Milka.” Kwakin oniktalil in aniyo pa niyakatsol wan in yahyawaltik pa nimahwam,
hani nimotankwakets wan niktahtolti in WeTatsDyos nowetatakewan AbRaham, kampa yewal melahka nishwalik pa in ot, pa nikonanas nikonSiwat ninohni nikal pa yes nisiwa.
Wan ashka, ta anmehwante ankinekil ki'ihniliske nowetatakewan, shinichilik. Wan ta amoyok shinichilik niyok, pa nihmatis kina nikchiwas.
Labán wan BetuEl kinankilik:
―Mochi okichi in WeTatsDyos, wan amokwal ten tikitoske ta kwal wan amokwal.
Nika onka Rebeka; shikonan wan shihwik ma yes nisiwa nikon mowetatakewan, yok kina kito in WeTatsDyos.
Kwah nitikipanol AbRaham, kikak ten kilik, mopacho pa in tal pa i'ishpa in WeTatsDyos.
Kwakin in tikipanol okinkishti tachiwalme ka oro wan plata wan shashalme kwahkwalme, okinmak Rebeka. Niyok okinmak ninohni Labán wan ninantsi Rebeka.
Mostatik, watsinkit moketsak, wan in tikipanol kinmili:
―Shinishkwepak newal ka nowetatakewan.
Wan ninohni wan ninantsi kinankilik:
―Ma moka in siwatYankwik ka tehwante pa matahti tonatim, kwakin panotiyas.
Wan yewal kinmili:
―Shinishkawak pa niyas. Kampa in WeTatsDyos okichi pa kisaskya kwal in ka ten niwal. Shinishtakewak pa no'ot pa niyas ka nowetatakewan.
Kwakin yehwante kinankilik:
―Ma tihnotsak in siwatYankwik ma tiktahtanilik yewal.
Wan kinotsak Rebeka wan kitahtanilik:
―Tiyas inak in takat?
―Nihnek niyas inak yewal.
Wan yok panoti Rebeka inak in tikipanolSiwat yewal ki'apa wan niyok nitikipanol AbRaham wan inik tikipanolme.
Wan Rebeka kimashtik yok:
“TonohniSiwat ka tehwante:
ma yes ninantsitsi ka myak wan myak masewalme!
wan mokolinchim, ma kintanilik
inik Wehwepweblo' ka anmotakokolilme!”
Kwakin omokets Rebeka, inak nitikipanolmeSiwam wan omotalik pa kameyo' wan okitokak in takat tikipanol, yewal kati okonan Rebeka wan panoti.
Itsak, yewal mochantiyaya pa Négeb, walmokwepaya pa in ta'onanaliste itoka Beer-Lahay-Roy in kinek kili: “Takoyonaliste Dyos yewal yoltik wan nichit.”
Katka tyotak wan Itsak oyaya nehnemiya ka tashosholtik, kwah otachi wan okinmit kameyo' astiwalaloya.
wan kitahtanili in tikipanol:
―Akyewal in takat yewal nehnem pa in tashosholtik. Wan tishnamiktiwal?
In tikipanol kinankili:
―Yewal nowetatakewan.
Okonan Rebeka se tukuru belo wan motsakwili nishayak.
Wan in tikipanol kitakichili Itsak mochiten okichi.
Kwakin Itsak okonan Rebeka wan okiwalik ka nikal ninantsi Sara, in kal tachiwal ka shashal tilawak wan yok omonamikti ka Rebeka wan Itsak kitasot miyak. Wan yok Itsak moyolse kampa moyolkokotikatka kampa mikiya ninantsi.
Nikolinchim AbRaham wan Keturá
AbRaham okipi okse siwat, yewal itoka Keturá.
Yewal okintakatilti Simrán, Yokshán, Medán, Midyán, Yishbak wan Súa.
Nikolinchim Dedán yek in ashurteko', in letusheyo' wan in lehumeyo'.
In ninpilwam Midyán yek Epá, Éper, Henok, Abida wan ElDá, moshte inik yek ininpilwam Keturá.
Wan AbRaham kimak Itsak mochiten nitakawaliste.
Ininpilwam ka oksek ininsiwam, AbRaham okinmak nitemakaliste kwah ayamo'ok mikiyaya wan okintitan wEhka kaha takis in tonat, pa amo yeloskya kaha Itsak.
Mochi in shiwim yoliyaya AbRaham kipiyaya 175 shiwim,
wan AbRaham omik we, kwal katka, ka myak shiwim, wan panoti ka niwichalme yehwante mikik.
In omente ininpilwam Itsak wan Yishma'El kitapachok pa in koyonkekweba Makpela, katka nikwahmil Eprón nikon Tsohar, in heteteko, wan onka kaha waltakis tonat pa Mamré.
In kwahmil omokowil AbRaham ka inik heteteko'. Wan ompa kitapachok AbRaham kaha yewal kitapachowaya Sara nisiwa.
Kwah omik AbRaham, Dyos kimashti nikon Itsak, wan in moka mochantiti ka takoyonak yewal kitokayolti Beer-Lahay-Roy in kinek kili: “Takoyonaliste Dyos yewal yoltik wan nichit.”
Nikolinchim Yishma'El
Ni'itokalme ininpilwam Yishma'El, okintokayoltik kina takatik: Nebayot, yewal oye nikon ta'ishpa Yishma'El, takwitap otakat Kedar, AdBel wan Mibesam,
Mishemá, Dumá, Masá,
Hadad, Temá, Yetur, Napísh wan Kedemá.
Inik ininpilwam Yishma'El, wan ni'itokalme nipweblo wan nikalme tachiwalme ka shashal tilawak: 12 tatakewalme, pa sesen kat ininpweblo'.
Yishma'El yolti 137 shiwim. Kwakin okonan i'ihyo wan omik, wan oy monamik ka niwichalme yehwante mikik.
Wan miki pa ininishpa ka moshte ninohniwan. Wan yishma'elteko' mochantitikatkaloya pa in tal Hawilá wan asik pa Shur, kwah se wal pa Asirya. Moka i'ishpa in tal Egipto.
Nitakatiliste Yakob wan Esa'ú
Inik nikolinchim Itsak, nikon AbRaham: AbRaham okitakatilti Itsak.
Itsak kipiyaya 40 shiwim kwah omonamikti inak Rebeka, nikon BetuEl wan ninohniSiwat Labán inik aramteko' mochantiloya pa Padán-aram.
Itsak kitahtani in WeTatsDyos pa Rebeka, nisiwa, kampa amokwal kinpiyaskya ininpilwam. Wan in WeTatsDyos okikak Itsak in ten kitahtan, wan yewal o'osti ta'apa.
Wan kinankili in WeTatsDyos:
“Ome mopilwam tikinapapti;
ome pweblo' yeske tashelolme pa tewal.
Se pweblo yes ka miyak chikawaliste wan in okse amoyok miyak kipiyas chikawaliste,
wan in yewal takati ta'ishpa kitikipanolis ninohni tipichi.”
O'as in tonat pa takatiskya, wan katkaloya omente pa'itik yewal.
Yewal ta'ishpa okis katka chichiltik, mochi ikwerpit kipiyaya nitohmi okitokayoltik Esa'ú.
Takwitapit otakat ninohni, kikitskitiwalaya nikshi ninohni Esa'ú. Wan okitokayoltik Yakob. Itsak kipiyaya 60 shiwim kimani okintakatilti Rebeka.
Mo'apawak piltontim. Wan Esa'ú oye takat pa in tashosholtik wan ta'asiyaya ka mit, wan Yakob oye takat ka sewiliste momatiya ni'icha.
Itsak kitasotaya Esa'ú, kampa kikwaya nita'asil; wan Rebeka kitasotaya Yakob.
Kili Yakob:
―Nimishtahtani shinishmak tipit motaposonal chichiltik, kampa nimayantiwal wan hyero nisyaptiwal. Kampa yok kitokayoltil Edom.
Yakob kinankili:
―Nimishmakas ta tinishnamakiltis motamawistiliste ka motakatiliste in ta'ishpa.
Esa'ú kito:
―Inik nimikti ka mayanaliste. Ten monots takatiliste ta'ishpa?
Wan Yakob kito:
―Shinichil ka tahtol melawak ashka.
Wan Esa'ú kili ka tahtol melawak Yakob wan kinamakilti nitakatiliste ta'ishpa.
Kwakin Yakob, okimak Esa'ú pan wan nitaposonal ka lenteha'. Wan otakwa, otakon wan opanoti.
Itsak pa Gerar
Pa inik tonatim katka mayanaliste pa in tal, oye okse mayanaliste pa inik tonatim kwah AbRaham yoltikatka. Yok oy omochanti Itsak pa Gerar, inak AbiMélek ininwe in peleshteko'.
In WeTatsDyos omoneshti wan kili: “Amo shitem pa Egipto. Shimochanti pa in tal kaha nimichilis.
Shimochanti pa in tal kina se pashaloliste, wan newal niyes ka tewal wan nimishmashti. Tewal wan mokolinchim nikinmakas mochi in tal, wan yok nikchiwas in ka tahtolme melawak yewal ten nikili pa ni'ishpa motats AbRaham.
Nikinmiyaptis mokolinchim kina sitalme pa in ilwikak, wan mokolinchim nikinmakas mochi in talme. Moshte pweblo' pa in mochital yeske tamashtinilme ika mokolinchim,
kampa AbRaham onishneltok wan okichi ten oniktake, yoliyaya ka notamawishtiliste pa notahtolme wan nishneltok mochi notamashtiliste.”
Wan yok Itsak moka mochantiti pa in tal Gerar.
Inik takam yehwante ompa mochantiloya kitahtanililoya ka nisiwa wan yewal kinankili, in siwat nonohnisiwat. Wan momaptitikatka pa kinmiliskya yewal nosiwa, kampa tamatiya nishmiktiske kampa kinekiske konanaske Rebeka kampa yewal kwal tachiyaya.
Kipiyaya myak tonatim ompa, kimani AbiMélek, ininweRey in peleshteko', tachishtikatka pa se tatapoli, okit kampa Itsak kinapalotikatka nisiwa Rebeka.
Kwakin AbiMélek otatake pa kinotsaloskya Itsak wan kili:
Itsak kinankili:
―Newal nitamat ika yewal nishmiktiloskya.
AbiMélek kili:
―Pates yok otitishchiwil in? Pa tipit hanya motekaskya se takat ka mosiwa, wan titishchiwiliskya se ta'ihtakoliste!
Kwakin AbiMélek otatake pa kimatiloskya pa mochi in pweblo:
―Ta ak amokwal kichiwili in takat wan nisiwa, in takat mikis.
Itsak otatok pa in tal wan WeTatsDyos kimashti, pa in shiwit kipishka 100 pa mochi sesen.
Wan mochi ka miyak tomi, wan ka miyak chikawaliste.
Okinpi myak borrego', baka' wan myak inintikipanolme, inik peleshteko' amokwal kitak kampa kinekiloya tapiyaloskya kina yewal tapiyaya.
Moshte takoyonalme pa inik tonatim ka AbRaham, nitats, kinkoyonaloya inintikipanolme, inik peleshteko' kintapacholoya wan kintemiltililoya ka tal.
―Ya shi oksela kampa tewal titapi miyak mochikawaliste ka tehwante.
Kwakin Itsak panoti, wan okital nikal tachiwali ka shashal tilawak pa in tal ishtawak pa Gerar, wan ompa omoka mochantiti.
Oksep kinishtapok in takoyonalme ka at pa inik tonatim ka AbRaham, nitats kinishtapoloya kwah omik AbRaham inik peleshteko' kintapacholoya, wan oksep okintokayolti kina nitats kintokayoltiya.
Se tonat, inintikipanolme Itsak takoyanak, wan okitak nalkistikatka at.
Kwakin inik takwitawilme borrego' in Gerar mokwalantik ka inintakwitawilme borrego' Itsak, kampa kitoloya. In at ka tehwante kampa Itsak okitokayolti in takoyonaliste “Esek” in kinek kito momiktik, kampa momiktik ika yewal.
Takoyonak oksela, wan niyok kwalanik peleshteko'. Itsak okitokayolti “Sitna”.<sup>a</sup>
Panoti wEhka pa okse tal wan amo'ak okwalan yok kwakin okitokayolti Rehobot, kito: “Ashka in WeTatsDyos tishmakawalti pa titapiyaske mochiten pa in tal.”
Wan ompa Itsak panoti pa BérSheba.
Pa in yowal omonesti WeTatsDyos wan kili:
“Newal niDyos motats AbRaham.
Pa ika notikipanol AbRaham,
newal nimishmashti wan nikinmiyaptis mokolinchim.”
Itsak kinichiko tetelme pa kitaliskya tamakaliste wan okinots ka ni'itokaliste WeTatsDyos, ompa okital nikal tachiwali ka shashal tilawak wan inintikipanolme takoyonak pa kitaloskya at.
Pa inik tonatim AbiMélek walaya pa Gerar, pa tahtoskya inak Itsak. Wan kitokatiwalaya ninihni ka wetamatiliste Ahusat wan niyok Pikol, niwetatakewan nigwacho.
Wan kinmili Itsak:
―Pates anwalak ka newal? Kampa anmehwante annishkwalanilil, wan annishkishtik ika anmehwante.
Yehwante kinankilik:
―Ashka tikitak kampa WeTatsDyos onka ka tewal, kwakin timo'ilik: Ma ye se tahtoliste melawak ika tehwante, ika tewal wan tehwante. Tihnekil tikchiwaske se taketsaliste ka tewal,
kampa tewal amoten titishchiwili, tehwante amoten timishchiwilik, yok kina tehwante amoten timishchiwilil. Tehwante han timishchiwilik kwal, wan timishtakewak pa tiyas ka mosewiliste, wan ashka tewal mishmashtitik in WeTatsDyos!
Kwakin Itsak kichi se mitotiliste, wan yehwante takwak wan takonik.
Pa in tonat walak inintikipanolme Itsak oyak kinawatik ka in takoyonaliste yewal kikoyontikatkaloya, wan kilik:
―Otikitak at!
Itsak okitokayolti in takoyonaliste Shebá, kampa yok itok in Wepweblo' BérSheba wan pa ashka yok kitokayoltil.
Itsak kimashti Yakob
Kwah Esa'ú kipiyaya 40 shiwim, kimani monamikti ka se siwat itok Yehudit nikon Berí in heteteko', wan niyok monamikti ka Bashemat nikon Elón in heteteko'.
Wan yehwante omente ininsiwam kinkokolti miyak Itsak wan Rebeka.
Yakob okonan nitamashtiliste Itsak
Se tonat kwah kolinche katka Itsak yahmo tachiyaya. Okinots pa walaskya Esa'ú nikon we kili:
―Nokon.
Kinankili Esa'ú:
Itsak kili:
―Shichit ya nikolinche wan amo nihmat pa ten tonat nimikis.
Ashka, shikonan momit, wan motawitol shi kaha tashosholtik shi shita'as pa newal.
Shinishyokshitil takwal kwal welik yok kina newal nihmat nikwa, wan shinishwalikil pa nikwas. Yok newal nimishmashtis kampa ayamo'ok nimiki.
Kwah Itsak tahtotikatka inak nikon Esa'ú Rebeka takaktikatka. Wan Esa'ú oy pa tashosholtik pa ta'asiskya wan kiwalikaskya,
kwakin Rebeka oy otahto ka nikon Yakob wan kili:
―Onihkak motats tahtotikatka inak monohni Esa'ú
shita'as wan shinishwalikil shinishyokshitil pa newal nikwas. Wan nimishmashti i'ishpa in WeTatsDyos kampa ayamo'ok nimiki.
Yok ashka, nokon shinishkak kwal, wan shikchi kina nimichilis.
Shi kampa kat in chibo' wan shinishwalikil ome chibito', pa yok nikyokshitilis motats kina yewal kinek.
Yakob kili ninantsi Rebeka:
―Nonohni kipi miyak nitohmi wan newal amo nikpi notohmi.
Ta nishkitski notats, kwakin tamatis kampa nihwetskilitik yewal, kwakin nikchiwas pa amokwal nishyaptiyas wan yok amo nishmashtis.
Wan ninantsi kinankili:
―Nokon newal, ma ye pa newal ten amokwal mishyas. Shikchi kina nimichili. Shinishwalikil in chibito'.
Yakob oy okinwalik chibito' wan okinwikil ninantsi, wan yewal kinyokshit, kina kimat kikwa Itsak.
Kwakin Rebeka okonan nishashalme Esa'ú nikon we, nishashalme kwahkwalme yewal kipiyaya pa in kal, wan ka yewal okitakemilti Yakob nikon tipichi.
Kipepechol nikwero chibito' pa nimahwam wan pa nikich Yakob kaha amo kipiyaya nitohmi.
Wan okimak pa nimahwam Yakob, nikon, in takwal wan in pan yewal okiyokshitil.
Kwakin Yakob oy okit nitats wan kili:
Itsak kinankili:
―Nika ni'onka. Ak tewal, nokon?
Yakob kili nitats:
―Newal ni'Esa'ú, mokon we. Onikchi kina tinichili. Shimokets, shimotal, shitakwa yewal ten nita'as pa yok tishmashtis.
Itsak kili nikon:
―Kina haniman otikit, nokon?
Yakob kinankili:
―Kampa in WeTatsDyos nishpale pa nikitaskya.
Itsak kili Yakob:
―Pa nikek shimochi nokon, pa nimishkitski pa nihmati ta melak tewal nokon Esa'ú wan amo tewal.
―Nitahtoliste in Yakob. Ma nimahwam kat kina Esa'ú.
Wan amo ki'ishmat kampa nimahwam kipiyaya nitohmi kina ninohni Esa'ú. Yok okimashti
kitahtanili:
―Melak tewal nokon Esa'ú?
Yakob kinankili:
―Haha, ninewal.
Kito niyok Itsak:
―Shinishwalikil mota'asil, nokon pa nikwas, pa nimishmashtis.
Wan Yakob okiwalikil wan otakwa nitats wan okiwalikil nihugoUbaBino, wan okon.
Kwakin Itsak kili:
Yakob mo'asilti wan kitenamik. Kimani Itsak kinehnekwi nishashalme, kwakin kimashti:
“Shikit, kina ahwiyak nokon
kina ahwiyak tashosholtik yewal in WeTatsDyos kimashti.
Yewal Dyos ma mishmak in ahwishti pa in ilwikak takpak;
wan miyak tapishkaliste pa in tal wan miyak trigo
wan miyak nihugoUbaBino.
Ma mishtikipanolik masewalme pa in pweblo;
wan ma motankwaketsak moshte pa in mochital pa mo'ishpa.
Shiye wetatakewan pa monohniwan;
wan pa mo'ishpa ma motankwaketsak ininpilwam monantsi.
Wan ma kinmashti yehwante kwal mishmashtil.”
Kimani otam Itsak okimashti Yakob, wan anok kisaya Yakob pa i'ishpa nitats, ninohni Esa'ú walmokwepaya pa in ta'astiliste.
Niyok yewal kiyokshitil kiwikil nitats wan kili:
―Shimotal, tats, wan shikwa in ten mokon ta'as, pa tishmashtis.
Itsak, nitats, kili:
―Ak tewal?
Wan yewal kinankili:
―Ninewal Esa'ú, mokon we.
Wan Itsak amo kimat ten kitoskya wan ka moyoyokaliste, kito:
―Wan akyewal owal nika, wan okiwalik nita'asil? Wan onishmak takwaliste mochi in kwah ayamo'ok ti'asiyaya, wan newal nihmashti, wan kipi tamashtiliste.
―Shinishmashti niyok newal, notats!
Kili Itsak:
―Owal monohni wan omishkwaman okonan motamashtiliste.
Esa'ú kinankili:
―Melak yewal kinek kili kina itok Yakob! Yewal takwaman! Onishkwahkwaman sehpa wan oksep! Onishkishtil in yewal notakatiliste ta'ishpa wan ashka onishkishtil notamashtiliste! Kwakin kitahtanili, kili:
―Amo otinishkawil newal se tamashtiliste?
Itsak kinankili Esa'ú:
―Onikchi pa yewal yes mowetatakewan tewal wan oniktal pa moshte ninohniwan pa yeske inintikipanolme, wan melak kipiyas miyak trigo wan nihugoUbaBino. Ashka ten kwal nikchiwas pa tewal nokon?
Esa'ú kinankili nitats:
―Notats, hanwel tikpi se han tamashtiliste? Shinishmashti niyok newal, notats!
Kwakin nitats yok kinankili:
“Yes mokal kaha takwak amo'ik tiyes pa in tal temak miyak tapishkaliste,
wan wEhka ka in ahwishti pa in ilwikak.
Ka momachet timopalewis,
wan tiktikipanoli monohni.
Kwah tichikawiyas kina se we,
kwakin yok timokishtilis ka yewal.”
Yakob cholowaya pa nikal Labán
Esa'ú hyero kikwalanil Yakob kampa nitats kimashti wan mo'ili pa niyol: “Astiwalal in tonatim kwah tikchokiliske notats. Kwakin nihmiktis nonohni Yakob.”
Wan Rebeka otakak kina Esa'ú kitowaya pa kichiwaskya, kwakin otatitan pa kinotsaloskya Yakob nikon tipichi kili:
Yok ashka shinishkak, nokon, shichol pa nikal nonohni Labán yewal mochanti pa Harán.
Shimochanti ompa sek tonatim, pa kimani as moyolsewis monohni.
Kwah yahmo kwalantiyas monohni ka tewal, kwah ki'ilkawas ten tikchiwil, kwakin tiwalmokwepas. Kampa amo nihnek annimishpolos anmehwante omente nopilwam pa se tonat?
Kwakin Rebeka kili Itsak:
―Amo niyoltik ka pakiliste, kampa in siwam heteteko' yehwante mochantil nika pa in tal. Ta Yakob omonamikti ka se siwat heteteko', amo nihnek pa niyoltiyas!
Kwakin Itsak okinots Yakob, kimashti wan niyok in okitake:
―Amo shimonamikti ka inik siwam pa in tal Kanán.
Shi pa Padán-aram pa nikal BetuEl nitats monantsi, wan shikonan mosiwa ompa ka nikonSiwat Labán ninohni monantsi.
Yewal Dyos ka nichikawaliste ma mishmashti, wan ma kichi pa takatiske wan pa momiyaptiske, pa yok mochiwaske myak Wehwepweblo'.
Yewal Dyos ma mishmak nitamashtiliste in AbRaham, tewal wan mokolinchim, pa timokawilis in tal kaha ashka timochantitik, wan yewal okimak AbRaham.
Esa'ú okit kampa Itsak kimashtiyaya Yakob wan okititan pa Padán-aram kampa ompa monamiktiskya. Niyok okit kwah kimashtiyaya kili, amo shimonamikti ka inik siwam pa Kanán.
Wan Yakob okineltok nitats wan ninantsi wan oy pa Padán-aram.
Esa'ú kimatiya kina kinihyaya nitats in siwam kananteko'.
Yok oy okit Yishma'El nikon AbRaham wan omonamikti inak Mahalat yewal ninohniSiwat Nebayot nikon Yishma'El, kampa kinpiyaya oksek ininsiwam.
Yakob tatemikiyaya pa BetuEl
Yakob okis pa BérSheba wan oy pa Harán.
Wan pek o'as, ompa okoch in yowal kampa tamalinaya tonat. Okonan se tet omotetsonte wan ompa omotek okoch.
Wan okipi se tatemikiliste, kampa kitaya se eskaler moketstikatka pa in tal wan astikatka pa ilwikak wan kinmitaya kampa nitanawatilanhelmeDyos tehkoloya wan temoloya.
Pa takpak in eskaler, kitaya in WeTatsDyos yewal kiliyaya: “Newal ninewal, WeTatsDyos, niDyos mokolinche AbRaham wan moTats Itsak. Tewal wan mokolinchim annimishmakas in tal kaha ashka tikoshtik.
Mokolinchim yeske kina nipohtiTal. Wan mosesemanaske kampa kalaki in tonat wan kampa walkis in tonat wan nepa takpak wan nepa tatsinta, moshte masewalme yeske tamashtinilme pa tewal wan pa mokolinchim.
Kwah Yakob o'is ka nitatemikiliste kito: “Melak in WeTatsDyos nika onka, wan newal amo nihmatiya.”
Tamakas wan kito: “Tatatsot in tal! Nika onka nikal WeTatsDyos; wan nitatapoli ilwikak!”
Mostatik tahtanesti okonan Yakob in tet yewal motetsonte, wan okikitski wan okikets in tet, kina se ta'ilnamikiliste wan kishawil aseyte ikpak yewal.
Ompa pa in Wepweblo ta'itokaya Luts wan Yakob okitokayolti BetuEl.
Kwakin Yakob okichi ka tahtol melawak: “Ta Dyos nishtokati newal wan nishkwitapti pa ot kaha niyapti, wan ta nishmak ten nikwas wan shashalme ka nimotakemilti,
wan nishwalkwepas ka sewiliste pa nikal notats, kwakin in WeTatsDyos yes noDyos.
Wan in tet yewal nihkets kina se ta'ilnamikiliste, yes nikal Dyos. Wan mochiten tishmakas, newal nimishmakas matahti pa sesen mochiten nikpiyas.”
Yakob o'as pa Padán-aram
Yakob okonan ni'ot, wan o'as pa tal kaha waltakis tonat.
Otachi wan okit takoyonaliste, amo wEhka katkaloya yey tanichikolme borrego', kampa pa in takoyonaliste takoniloya yolikilme. Se tet we kitsakwaya in takoyonaliste.
Yakob kinmili:
―Nonihniwan, kaha anmochantil anmehwante?
Wan yehwante kinankilik:
―Tehwante timochantil pa Harán.
Kwakin kinmili:
―Anki'ishmatil anmehwante Labán, in nikon Nahor?
Wan yehwante kitok:
―Haha, tikishmatil.
Yakob kinmili:
―Kina onka?
―Yewal kwal onka. Shikit tewal nepa wal nikonSiwat Rakel ka borrego'.
Kwakin yewal kito:
―Shikitak, ayamo tyotak, ayamo kwal tikintsakwaske in borrego'. Shikinahmakak wan shikinwikak ma takwak.
Yehwante kinankilik:
―Amokwal yok tikchiwaske, monek pa monichikoske moshte tanichikolme borrego'. Kwakin mokishti in tet we pa takoyonaliste wan tikinahmakaske in borrego'.
Taketstikatka inak yehwante, kwah o'as Rakel ka ininborrego' nitats yewal kinkwitawiyaya.
Rakel katka nikon Labán, ninohni ninantsi Yakob, wan in borrego' katka ka Labán. Kimani Yakob okit Rakel, o'as wan kikishti in tet we ka ta'ahmakaliste wan kinahmakak in borrego'.
Kwakin Yakob kitahpalo ka tenamikiliste Rakel, wan kipewalti chokaliste.
Kwakin Yakob kili Rakel yewal katka nikon ninohni nitats, wan katka nikon Rebeka. Kwakin yewal motalo pa kinawatiskya nitats.
Kwah okikak Labán in taketsaliste ka Yakob, nikon ninohniSiwat, motaloti oy okinamik, wan kinapalo wan kitenamiki, wan okiwik icha, ompa Yakob kitakichili Labán mochi inik ten.
Yakob monamikti inak Le'a wan Rakel
Kwakin Labán kili Yakob:
―Amoyok han tinishtikipanoli, kampa tewal nikon nonohni, shinichil kishki tihnek pa nimishtashtawilis.
Labán kinpiyaya ome ininpilwaSiwam. In we itoka Le'a wan in tipichi itoka Rakel.
Le'a kwal nesiloya nishtololme, Rakel kwal nesiya.
Yakob kinekiya Rakel, wan kili:
―Nimishtikipanolis chikome shiwim pa nimonamiktis ka mokon tipichi, Rakel.
Wan Labán tanankili:
―Kwal onka, pa nimishmakas tewal, pa amo monamiktis inak okse takat. Shimoka ka newal.
Yok ye kina Yakob otikipan chikome shiwim ka Rakel, kitamashti kina sek tonatim, kampa hyero kinekiya.
―Ashka onitam onimishtikipanol mochi in shiwim. Shinishmak nosiwa pa nimonamiktis inak yewal.
Kwakin kinnichiko Labán moshte masewalme wan okichi se mitotiliste.
Kwah tayoway, Labán konan nikon Le'a, wan okiwikil Yakob, wan yewal omotek inak yewal.
Niyok Labán okimak nikon Le'a, se tikipanolSiwat itok Silpa.
Mostatik kwah tanes, Yakob okit kampa katka inak Le'a, kampa yok kili Labán:
―Ten yewal otinishchiwil? Nimishtikipanol pa nikonanas Rakel? Pates otishkwaman?
Labán kinankili:
―Inik, tehwante amo titemakal pa monamiktis se nikon tipichi ta ayamo'ok monamikti nikon we.
Shitakis in chikome tonatim, kwakin nimishmakas in nokse, ta tinishtikipanoli oksek chikome shiwim pa newal.
Yok okichi Yakob, mo'ashilti in chikweyi tonatim, kwakin Labán okimak nikonSiwat Rakel pa yeskya nisiwa.
Wan Yakob omotek niyok ka Rakel, wan okinek miyak Rakel, amoyok okinek Le'a, wan kitikipanoli Labán oksek chikome shiwim.
Ininpilwam Yakob
In WeTatsDyos kitaya kina Yakob amo kinekiya Le'a. Okichi pa kinpiyaskya ininpilwam, wan Rakel amokwal kinpiyaskya ininpilwam.
Le'a o'osti ta'apa wan okitakatilti se nikonTakat wan okitokayolti Rubén<sup>a</sup>, kampa kito: “In WeTatsDyos okit kina nimoyolkokotikatka. Yok ashka nishtasota notaka.”
Oksep osti ta'apa wan okitakatilti okse nikonTakat, kwakin kito: “In WeTatsDyos takak kampa amo nishnek notaka, kampa onishmak in okse nokon.” Kampa yok kitokayolti Shime'ón.
Oksep o'osti ta'apa wan okitakatilti se nikonTakat, wan kito: “Kampa ashka notaka mokawas nonak, kampa nikintakatilti yey ininpilwam takam.” Wan okitokayolti Lewí.
Osti ta'apa oksep, wan okitakatilti okse nikonTakat, wan kito: “Ashka nikilis tahtolme wehwe pa in WeTatsDyos.” Kampa yok okitokayolti Yehudá. Kwakin yahmo okinpi ininpilwam.
Rakel okit kina amo kintakatiltiyaya ininpilwam ka Yakob kwakin kikwalaniliyaya ninohni Le'a. Kwakin kiliyaya Yakob:
―Shinishtakatilti nopilwam, ma yok nimikis!
Yakob okwalan inak Rakel wan kili:
Kwakin Rakel kito:
―Nika onka Bilha notikipanol. Shimotek inak yewal pa yok yewal nishtakatiltis nopilwam kampa pa yewal, newal yok nikinpiyas nopilwam.
Wan Rakel okimak Yakob nitikipanolSiwat Bilha pa yeskya nisiwa wan omotek inak yewal.
Bilha o'osti ta'apa wan okitakatilti se nikon Yakob.
Kwakin Rakel kito: “Dyos onishmak notamawishtiliste wan onishkak kwah niktahtan se nokon takat.” Kwakin okitokayolti Dan.
Rakel nitikipanolSiwat Bilha o'osti ta'apa oksep, wan okitakatilti okse nikonTakat ka Yakob.
Kwakin Rakel kito: “Kina miyak nimomikti ka nonohni Le'a wan ashka niktanil.” Wan okitokayolti nikon Neptalí.
Kwah Le'a okimat kwah ayahmo kintakatiltiyaya ininpilwam, kwakin okonan nitikipanolSiwat Silpa wan okimak Yakob pa yeskya nisiwa.
Wan Silpa nitikipanolSiwat Le'a okitakatilti se nikonTakat pa Yakob.
Wan Le'a kito: “Dyos onishchiwil okse tachiwaliste kwal!” Ashka nikpi okse!, kwakin okitokayolti Gad.
Wan Le'a kito: “Nikpi miyak pakiliste ka newal! In siwam nichiliske newal nimo'itok Pakiliste.” Wan okitokayolti Asher.
Se tonat kwah kipishkaloya trigo, oy Rubén pa in kwahmil. Okit mandragora' yewal kiwikil Le'a ninantsi. Wan Rakel kili Le'a:
―Shinishmak sek mandragora' yewal kiwalik mokon.
Wan Le'a kili Rakel:
―Tewal otinishkishtil notaka, wan ashka tihnek tinishkishtilis nimandragora' nokon?
Rakel kito:
―Ma tikchiwak se tahtoliste kampa ashka yewal pa in yowal kochi monak, ta tinishmak sek mandragora'.
Katka pa kwahmil Yakob wan pa tyotak kwah walmokwep, okinamik Le'a, kili:
―Pa in yowal tikochi nonak, kampa onitashta ka nimandragora' nokon yewal okiwalik.
Wan Yakob okoch ka Le'a.
Kwakin Le'a kito: “Dyos onishchiwil kwal ka in tashtawaliste kampa onihmak notikipanol pa yeskya nisiwa.” Kwakin okitokayolti Isakar.
Le'a o'osti ta'apa oksep, okitakatilti okse nikonTakat ka in katkaloya chikwase ininpilwam Yakob.
Kwakin Le'a kito: “Dyos onishmak se temakaliste yewal kostaro. Ka in nopilwam, notaka nishmawishtilis kampa nikintakatilti chikwase ininpilwaTakam.” Kwakin okitokayolti Sabulón.
Kwakin okitakatilti okse nikonSiwat wan okitokayolti Dína.
Kwakin Dyos ki'ilnamik Rakel, okikak nitahtolme wan okimak pa kinpiyas ininpilwam.
Osti ta'apa wan okitakatilti se nikonTakat pa Yakob, kito: “Dyos onishkishtil nopinawiliste.”
Okitokayolti Yosé, kitowaya: “Nishmakaskya in WeTatsDyos okse nokonTakat.”
Niyashka Yakob momiyaptiloya
Panok tonatim kwah Rakel okitakatilti Yosé, wan Yakob kili Laban:
―Shinishtake pa no'ot pa nimokwepas pa notal.
Ma yok Labán kili:
―Nimishtahtani ka tamawishtiliste shimoka ka newal, kampa nihmat ipa se taneshtiliste, kampa in WeTatsDyos nishmashtitik ipa tewal.
Wan kili:
―Shinichil kishki tihnek nimishtashtawilis wan yok nimishmakas.
Yakob kinankili:
―Wan tihmat kina nitikipanowaya ka moyolikilme kina newal nikinkwitawiyaya.
Amoyok miyak titapiyaya kwah newal ayamo ni'asiyaya, motachi miyak kwah ni'as, wan in WeTatsDyos mishmashti. Kimani ten nikchiwas pa nokal.
Wan Laban kitahtanili:
―Ten tihnek pa nimishmakas?
Yakob kinankili:
Ashka nipanos pa mochi moyolikilme, wan nikinonana moshte in borrego' tamahwilme wan ta'ahwicholme, wan mochi borrego' tihtiltik, wan in chiba' ta'ahwicholme, moshte yehwante yeske notashtawaliste.
Kwah tihnekis tihmatis in notashtawaliste, yok ta onka sek chibo' pa notanichikoliste yewal amo tamahwilme wan sek borrego' yewal amo tihtiltik, kwakin yok tihmatis. Kampa yok nimishta'ishtikilitik.
Kwakin Labán kito:
―Kwal onka yok kina tinichili.
Pa in tonat Labán kinonan mochi in chibo' tamahwilme wan tapahwilme wan in chiba' tamahwilme wan ta'ahwicholme', wan kishki kipiyaloya tipit ihistak wan moshte in borrego' tihtiltik, wan okinmak ininpilwam pa kinkwitawiloskya.
Kwakin kinwikak wEhka, kaha amo yeskya Yakob. Kinwikak kina pa yey tonatim pa ot, wan Yakob omoka kinkwitapti in oksek niborrego' Labán.
Okonan Yakob kwawit pihpitsawak ka kapul wan wachalala wan amakwawit wan kinkishtil ininkashkar pa nesiskya ni'istak in kwawim.
Kwakin okintal in kwawitito ni'ishpa kaha walaloya takoniloya in yolikilme. Wan yehwante motohtokaloya ni'ishpa kwawitito,
yok ta'apawaloya in borrego' i'ishpa in kwawim wan kinmishiwiltiloya borrego' tamahwilme wan tapahwilme wan ta'ahwicholme ka myak tapahwilme.
Kwakin Yakob okinonan wan kinkawaya i'ishpa yolikilme niktihtiltik wan tapahwilme pa nitanichikolme Laban. Yok Yakob mokawiliti pa kipiyaskya isel nitanichikol amo kinnelowaya inak niborrego' Labán.
Kwah walaloya in yolikilme amokwal nesiloya, amo kintaliyaya ma yok, in amo kwahkwalme mokawiliyaya Labán wan in kwahkwalme mokawiliyaya Yakob.
Yok oye in takat kina omochi ka myak mochiten. Wan okinpi myak borrego' wan tikipanolmeSiwam, tikipanolmeTakam, kameyo' wan burro'.
Cholowaya Yakob kampa yahmo yeskya ka Labán
Kwah Yakob kimat kina Labán ininpilwam kililoya: “Yakob ki'ishtikili totats mochi yewal ten tapiyaya, wan mochi in yewal ashka tapi mokawili yewal niyashka totats.”
Kitaya Yakob, kina amokwal kitaya Labán kina kwah o'as.
Kwakin in WeTatsDyos kili Yakob: “Shimokwep pa nital mowichalme wan monohniwan, wan newal nimishpalewis wan niyes ka tewal.”
Kwakin tatake Yakob pa kinnotsaloskya Rakel wan Le'a pa in kwahmil kaha katkaloya in yolikilme,
kinmili:
―Nikit kina anmotats amokwal nichit ashka, kina kwah nichitaya kwah oni'as. Ma yok niDyos notats onka ka newal.
Anmehwante ankimatil kina niktikipanoli anmotats ka mochi nochikawaliste.
Ta yewal kitowaya: “In yolikilme tamahwilme yes motashtawaliste”, kwakin mochi in yolikilme kintakatiltiloya tamahwilme; wan ta yok kitowaya: “Nimishtashtawilis ka in yolikilme tsehtsepestik yes motashtawaliste”, kwakin mochi inik yolikilme kintakatiltiloya tsehtsepestik.
Yok Dyos kikishtil yolikilme anmotats wan onishmak newal.
“Pa se tonat kwah tatohtokaloya in yolikilme, nikpi se tatemikiliste kampa nikinmitaya in toro' kintohtokatikatkaloya in chiba' katkaloya tapahwilme, tamahwilme wan ta'ahwicholme.
Kwakin nitanawatilanhelDyos nishtakichil pa tatemikiliste, nichili: “Yakob!” Newal nihnankili: “Nika ni'onka.”
Wan kito: “Shitachi wan shikit kampa mochi toro kintohtokal ka in tanichikolme tamahwilme wan tsehtsepestek. Onikit kina mishchiwili Labán.
Newal niDyos yewal omoneshte ompa BetuEl, kaha tikshawil moyEste in tet weyak yewal tihkets, ompa otichil newal, ashka shihka in tal shimokwep pa motal kaha otitakat.”
Kwakin Rakel wan Le'a kinankilik:
―Ayamo tikpiyal ka yewal nitakawaliste pa mochiten ka totats.
Yewal tichit kina amo otitakatik nika. Otishnamak tehwante, niyok okitam in yewal totashtawaliste.
Melak kampa mochi in Dyos okikishtil totats ka toyashka wan niyashka topilwam. Ashka shikchi kina Dyos michili.
wan okinpewalti mochi yolikilme tanichikolme. Niyok okinwik mochi inik yewal okinonan ompa pa Padán-aram, yok omokwep pa tal Kanán, kaha katka nitats Itsak.
Kwah oy Labán okinshim niborrego', Rakel kinishtek imono tachiwal ka tal ka nitats yewal katkaloya pa nikal.
Yakob kikwaman Labán in aramteko, amo kinawat kwah panoti.
Kwakin panoti ka mochiten yewal tapiyaya wan panok in atenko Éprates. Kwakin okonan ot pa talTepet Gile'ad.
Labán kitohtok Yakob
Panok yey tonatim, oyak kilik Labán kaha yok cholowaya Yakob.
Kwakin Labán okinwik ka yewal ninihniwan pa oksek kalme wan kitohtokaya Yakob pa chikome tonatim wan oki'as pa tepetLom pa Gile'ad.
Kwakin moneshte Dyos ka Labán in aramteko pa tatemikiliste kili: “Amoten shikil Yakob, amo shihkwalanti!”
Yakob okital nikal tachiwali ka shashal tilawak pa tepetLom pa Gile'ad kwah ki'as Yakob, wan Labán inak ninihniwan ompa niyok mokawak.
Kwakin Labán kili Yakob:
Pates tichol kampa amo'ak kimatiskya wan tishkwahkwaman? Pates amoten otichil? Yok nimishtitaneskya pa mo'ot ka pakiliste wan ka tatsotsonaliste ka arpas?
Wan amo otinishmakawalti pa nikintenamikiskya nopilwam. Otikchi kina se yewal amo mo'ilnamik kwal.
Newal nikpi chikawaliste pa nimishchiwilis takokoliste kampa nichili niDyos motats: “Shimo'it pa amo'ik tikilis amoten Yakob!”
Ashka otimowik kampa hyero tihnek timokwepas pa nikal motats. Ma yok, pates otinishishtikil nomono'?
Yakob kinankili Labán:
―Nimomapti, ompa nimo'il kampa tinishkishtiliskya mopilwam ka chikawaliste.
Ma yok, tatikit se ka tehwante yewal kinpi modyose', ma mik. Ininishpa tonohniwan, shitatem tewal ta tikit ten moyashka nika ka newal, wan shikonan.
Yakob amo kimatiya kampa Rakel kinishtek in mono tachiwal ka tal.
Yok okalak Labán pa nikal Yakob niyok pa nikal Le'a wan okalak pa ininkal in ome tikipanolmeSiwam. Amoten okit, kwakin kwah okis pa nikal Le'a, okalak pa nikal Rakel.
Kwah ayamo'ok asiyaya Labán pa nikal Rakel, kintat pa nisiya ikameyo wan omotal ipa. Labán tatemowaya pa in kal tachiwal ka shashal tilawak, amoten okit.
―Amo shikwalan tats, amokwal nimoketsa mo'ishpa. Nishastik nomeste.
Tatemo Labán wan amo okinmit in mono tachiwal ka tal.
Okwalan Yakob wan oki'ahwa Labán, kitahtanili:
―Ten yewal amokwal onikchi? Ten onimishchiwil pa yok tinishtohtokatiwal kaha niwal?
Ashka otitam otitatem pa mochi yewal noyashka. Ten otikit yewal ka tewal pa mokal? Shiktal nika ininishpa nonohniwan wan ma motishpawilik ka tewal wan newal.
Pa inik 20 shiwim ka tewal. Amo ni se tamaya moborrego' wan mochiba' wan newal amo nikwa ni se moborrego' yewal katkaloya pa motanichikolme.
Amo'ik nimishwalikil moyolikilme yewal kati tekwanim pa kwawim kinmiktiyaya, kampa nimishtashtawiliyaya yewal kati poliwiloya. Wan nimishtashtawiliyaya newal ta nishishtikililoya pa tahka wan pa tayo.
Wan newal yok niyoliyaya kimani nimishtikipanoliyaya. Pa tahka nitolnamikiyaya hyero tona katka, wan pa inik yowalme hyero nisekwalowaya amo nikochiyaya.
Ma yok oniye pa in 20 shiwim kwah nikatka ka anmehwante pa mokal. Onimishtikipanol 14 shiwim pa tinishmakaskya in omente mopilwam pa yeloskya nosiwam onimishtikipanoli chikwase shiwim pa motanichikolme ka yolikilme. Wan tishkistil notashtawaliste ka matahti tashtawaliste.
Tats niDyos notats, niDyos AbRaham, wan notats Itsak, ta yewal amo yeskya ka newal, melak tewal tinishtakewaskya pa kiyawak mokal amo nikpiyaskya amoten. Ma yok, Dyos okit kina nimoyolkokotitikatka kina onitikipan miyak, pa yowal omishahwa.
―In siwam yehwante nopilwam, inik ininpilwam kat nopilwam wan in yolikilme. Mochi yewal tikit ka noyashka. Ma yok, ten wel nikchiwas ashka yehwante inik nopilwaSiwam wan nahyehwante in ininpilwam yewal kintakatiltik?
Aska shiwal, ma timochiwilik se taketsaliste tewal wan newal, wan ma ye kina se tachiwaliste ka taneshtiliste ka tehwante omente.
Kwakin okonan Yakob se tet wan kiketsak,
kinmili Yakob ninihniwan:
―Shikinnichikok tetelme!
Wan kinnichikok tetelme ompa takwak ipa in tetelme.
Labán okitokayolti Yegar Sahaduta wan Yakob okitokayolti Gile'ad.
Labán kito:
―Inik tanichikolme tetelme ka totahtol melawak ka tewal wan newal ashka.
Kwakin kitokayoltil Gile'ad,
―Ma kit in WeTatsDyos pa tewal wan newal kwah temosesemanaske se ka okse.
Ta amokwal tikinchiwil nopilwaSiwam ta tikinonan oksek siwam pa niyok yeske mosiwam, kwakin amo'ak yes ka tehwante, ma yok shikilnamik kampa Dyos okit mochi yewal ka tewal wan newal.
Niyok Labán kili Yakob:
―Shikit in tanichikolme nika ka in tetelme yewal nihkets, pa tewal wan newal.
In tanichikol ka in tetelme, wan in taneshtiliste pa yok tihmatiske in: Newal amo nipanos in tanichikolme ka tetelme pa niyas ka tewal, pa nimishchiwilis ten amokwal wan tewal amo tiyas kaha newal pa tinishchiwilis ten amokwal.
NiDyos AbRaham wan niDyos Nahor, ininDyos inintahwan ma motishpawilik ka tehwante ta amo tikchiwak kina tikitok.
Yok kili melak Yakob pa i'ishpa Dyos, kinotstikatka niDyos yewal nitats Itsak wan kimakasiyaya.
Yakob okital ompa se tatemakal pa in lom wan okinnots ninohniwan pa takwaloskya. Kwakin kwah takwak, panok ompa in yowal.
Mostatik kwalka kintenamiki Labán nikolinchim wan ininpilwaSiwam, kinmashti. Kwakin omokwek pa nikal.
Monamikil Yakob wan Esa'ú
Kwah okinmit Yakob kito: “In kaha mosewil iningwacho' Dyos!” Yok yewal kaha okitokayolti Mahanayim.
Yakob okintake sek tanawatilme, yehwante yaloskya ka ninohni Esa'ú pa tal Se'ir, pa in nikwahmil Edom.
Wan kinmili: “Shikilik notats Esa'ú, yok kito motikipanol Yakob wan pa ashka nimochantitik inak Labán,
nikinpi baka', borrego', tikipanolmeTakam wan tikipanolmeSiwan. Onikintitan in notanawatilme, pa kiliske notats pa niktahtanis pa nishnamikis ka ta'ihniliste.”
Kwah walmokwepak in tanawatilme kilik Yakob: “Tiyak ka monohni Esa'ú wan ashka wal pa mishnamikis ka yewal walal 400 takam.”
Yakob hyero momapti, moka moyokoltiti, kwakin kinshel pa ome tanichikolme ka masewalme yehwante katkaloya inak yewal, wan niyok inik tanichikolme borrego', baka' wan inik kameyo',
wan kito: “Ta wal Esa'ú wan momikti ka in se tanichikol, kwakin in okse tanichikol kwal choloske.”
Niyok kito Yakob: “Tats, niDyos nokolinche AbRaham wan niDyos notats Itsak, tewal yok tinichil shimokwep pa motal wan ka motahwan wan newal nimishchiwilis kwal:
newal amo nimonots pa nikpiyas ta'ihniliste wan ka melak kina tihkwitawi in motikipanol tewal, newal nimopanolti ka no'ota in atenko Yordán. Wan ashka nikpi ome wehwe tanichikolme.
Nimishtahtani, shinishpale ka nonohni Esa'ú, kampa nihmakasi pa walas nishmiktis, wan kinmiktis nosiwam ka ininpilwam!
Pano pa in yowal, wan ka inik yolikilme yewal kinpiyaya, kinkitske tahko pa kimakas ninohni Esa'ú.
Kinkishtili 200 chiba' wan 20 chibo', 200 borrega' wan 20 borrego',
30 kameyo' siwam ka ininpilwam, 40 baka' wan matahti toro' wan 20 burra' ka matahti burro'.
Pa sesen inintikipanolme okintake pa kinmitatiyaloskya se tanichikol, wan kinmili: “Shinimik ta'ishpa wan ma yaptiyak wehwehkito pa mochi sesen ka in tanichikolme.”
Okititan se ta'ishpa, kiliyaya:
―Ta nonohni Esa'ú mishnamiki wan mishtahtanili: “Akyewal mowetatakewan? Kampa ti?, akyewal niyolikilme yewal tikinwik?
Kwakin tikilis: “Niyashka motikipanol Yakob yewal otishtake pa nimishmakas tewal, notats Esa'ú, Yakob wal takwitap ka tehwante.”
Niyok okintake in oksek inintikipanolme wan moshte in oksek yewal kintitan takwitap ka inik tanichikolme, kinmili: “Anmehwante ankiliske yok in tahtolme Esa'ú, kwah ankinamikiske,
wan niyok ankiliske: ’Wal takwitap motikipanol Yakob.’ Wan yewal tamat: ’Nikyolsewis ka inik yolikilme yewal nikintitanilitik ta'ishpa, kimani timonamikiske yok yewal nishnamikis kwal.’”
Yok in yolikilme kintitaniliyaya ta'ishpa Yakob, ma yok Yakob pano in yowal, kaha kikets nikal pa mosewiskya.
Pa in yowal omokets Yakob, okinonan in ome siwam wan in ome nitikipanolmeSiwam wan in 11 ininpilwam, okinpanolti pa in atenko, Yakob.
Kwakin okinpanolti in atenko we, otatake pa kinpanoltiloskya mochi yewal niyashka.
Yok omoka Yakob isel wan omo'onan ka yewal se takat, pa mochi yowal kwah takistiwalaya tonat.
Kwah okit in takat kina amokwal kitaniliskya, okite pa niseltik kaha takitskitik nipyerna, kwah momiktitikatkaloya nipyerna Yakob okopin niweso.
Kwakin in takat kili:
―Shinishmaka, kampa oksep waltakistiwal tonat!
Yakob kinankili:
―Amo nimishmakawas ta amo tinichil motahtoliste kwal pa newal!
In takat kitahtanili:
―Kina ti'itok?
―Ni'itok Yakob.
Wan in masewal kili:
―Yahmo ti'itokas Yakob. Ashka ti'itokas Isra'El, kampa otimo'onan ka Dyos wan ka masewalme tikintanil.
Yakob kili:
―Tihnek tinichilis kina ti'itok tewal.
Wan in takat kinankili:
―Pates tinishtahtanilitik kina ni'itok?
Kwakin in takat kili Yakob nitahtoliste kwal pa yewal.
Yakob okitokayolti PenuEl ompa kaha katkaloya: “Kampa inak Dyos timo'itak, ma yok amo onishkishtil noyoliliste.”
Kwah waltakis in tonat, kwah Yakob panowaya PenuEl, wan kikokowaya nipyerna<sup>a</sup> amokwal kina nehnemiskya.
Kimani Yakob kinamik Esa'ú
Yakob otachi wan astiwalaya Esa'ú wan in 400 takam. Yakob kinmak ininpilwam se ka okse Le'a, Rakel wan in ome inintikipanolmeSiwam.
Ta'ishpa okinkets inintikipanolmeSiwam wan ininpilwam, takwitapit okikets Le'a ka ininpilwam, kampa takwitap okikets Rakel wan Yosé.
Yakob, okinpana moshte wan omotankwaketsaya ka chikome han pa tal kwah astiyaya ninohni.
Ma yok Esa'ú omotal okinamik Yakob wan okinapal wan okitenamik. Wan chokaloya in omente.
Kwakin otachi Esa'ú wan okinmit in siwam wan ininpilwam, kitahtanili:
―Akyehwante inik yewal kat monak?
Yakob kinankili:
―Yehwante nopilwam, yewal Dyos onishmak newal, motikipanol tewal.
Kwakin walaloya inintikipanolmeSiwam ka ininpilwam wan omotankwaketsak pa i'ishpa yewal.
Esa'ú kitahtanili:
―Ten tihnek tikitos ka mochi inik tanichikolme yewal onikinnamiktiwal pa ot?
Yakob kili:
―Nihnekiya niktaniskya tikipanoliste kwal pa notats.
Kwakin Esa'ú kito:
―Miyak nitapi nonohni. Shimokawil in yewal tikpi pa tewal.
Yakob kinankili:
―Nimishtahtani, ta melak kwal tishnamiktik shikonan in temakaliste, kwah onikit moshayak, onikit kina nishayak Dyos. Tewal otishnamik kwal.
Shikinonan in yewal nimishwalikilitiwal, kampa Dyos kwal nishchiwili newal, wan nikpi mochiten moteshmonek.
Kampa Yakob hyero kimakatikatkaya pa kinonanaskya, yok Esa'ú okinonan.
―Ma tiyaptiyak pa ot. Newal nimishtokas.
Yakob kinankili:
―Notats kimat kina piltontim kat sehseltik wan monek pa nikinmitatiyas in borrega' yewal tachichiltil. Ta tikinwikal kongana pa se tonat mikiske mochi in yohyolkilme.
Nimishtahtani, notats, shiyapti ta'ishpa ka motikipanol, wan newal yolikit niyaptiyas kina tatiliktsatiyal yolikilme wan kina tatiliktsatiyal piltontim newal ompa nikasis notats pa Se'ir.
Kwakin Esa'ú kili:
―Nimishkawilis tahko nomasewalme yewal walal ka newal pa mishpalewiske.
Yakob kinankili:
―Amo nishteshmonikil? Kampa melak kwal tishnamik notats.
Yok, pa in tonat Esa'ú omokwep pa ni'ot pa Se'ir.
Wan Yakob, yawiya pa in ot pa Sukot, ompa okichi nikal wan okinchi tasoway ka inik nimahmashaltik kwawim pa yolikilme ompa okitokayolti Sokot (kinek kito ramada').
Mokowili tal kaha kikets nikal, okinkowil ininpilwam Hamor, nitats Sikem, otashta 100 tomi tachiwali ka plata.
Ompa okinnichik tetelme kaha kitaliskya tamakaliste wan okitokayolti, El Elohe Isra'El.<sup>a</sup>
Sikem kikatsawilti Dína
Dína, nikonSiwat Le'a yewal kipi inak Yakob, Dína yawiya kinpashalowaya inik siwam pa in pweblo.
Sikem nikon Hamor in heweteko yewal katka kapitan pa in pweblo okit Dína, wan okonan omotek inak yewal.
Kwakin in takat okitasot miyak Dína, kili tahtolme sehseltek ka in siwatPiltonte.
Kwakin Sikem kili nitats Hamor: “Shitahtan in siwatPiltonte kampa yewal yes nosiwa.”
Kwah Yakob kimat kina in takat kikatsawilti nikon Dína, ininpilwaTakam katkaloya pa in tashosholtik ka in yohyolkilme. Yok amo nawat Yakob, omochi pa walmokwepaloskya ininpilwam.
Kwakin Hamor nitats Sikem oy okit pa tahtoskya ka Yakob.
Kwah walmokwepak ininpilwam Yakob, walaloya pa in kwahmilme kaha katkaloya, kwah okimatik in yewal ten okipan Dína, okinkok miyak ininyolme wan hyero kwalanik. Pates Sikem okichi yewal ten amokwal ka siwatPiltonte Isra'El kampa omotek ka nikonSiwat Yakob. Katka ten pa amo'ik panoskya ten, kina in.
―Nokon Sikem kinek monamiktis ka mokonSiwat. Shihmakak pa monamiktis inak yewal.
Ma timonamiktik tehwante ka anmehwante. Shitishmakak anmopilwaSiwam wan shikinonanak topilwaSiwam pa anmehwante.
Shimokawak wan shimochantik nika ka tehwante, in tal onka pa mota'ishpa. Shiyolik nika, shitakowak wan shitanamakak pa in tal shimokowilik kwahmilme pa in tal.
Kwakin Sikem kili Dína nitats wan ninohniwan:
―Ma nikpi tekipanoliste kwal ka anmehwante, wan annimishmakas ten annishtahtaniske.
Shiktalik in tashtawaliste pa in siwat, shinichilik kishki monek pa annimishwalikili, ma ye we kina ankinekil, wan annimishtashtawilis ten annishtahtaniske. Shinishmakak in siwatPiltonte pa yok yes nosiwa.
Yakob ininpilwam kwah tahtok ka Sikem wan nitats Hamor kikwahkwamanak kampa ninohni Dína ye takatsawaltil.
Kilik:
―Amokwal yok tikchiwaske, pa antimishmakaske tonohniSiwat se takat yewal amo kipi takotonili nikwerit kaha mashishal. In yewal tepinawaliste pa tehwante.
Antimishmakaske pa timonamiktis ka yewal, anmehwante ta ankichiwak kina tehwante: shimokotonilik anmokwerit kaha anmashishal moshte takam ka anmehwante.
Wan ta amo ankinekil ankichiwaske se tahtoliste pa ankipiyaske takotonili nikwerit kaha mashishal, kwakin tikonanaske tonohniSiwat wan tihwikaske.
Yok kikakik kwal Hamor wan nikon Sikem in tahtol;
in takatYankwik Sikem kimawishtililoya yehwante in takam pa in pweblo, wan amo owehkA pa kichiwaskya in yewal kilik ininpilwam Yakob.
Kampa yok miyak kinekiya nikonSiwat Yakob.
Yok Hamor wan nikon Sikem kampa kalakik pa in pweblo pa tahtoloskya ka in takam pa ininpweblo, ompa kaha kalakil moshte.
Kinmilik:
―Mochantil ka sewiliste ka tehwante in takam israelita'. Mochantiske nika pa takowaske wan tanamakaske. Kampa we tal pa yehwante, kampa timonamiktiske ka ininpilwaSiwam, wan yehwante monamiktiske ka topilwam.
Ma yok, in takam mokawaske mochantitiyaske yok ka tehwante tikpiyaske takotonili nikwerit kaha mashishal tehwante, kina yehwante kipiyal.
Yeske toyashka inintanichikolme ka borrego', chibo' wan ininkwahmilme wan in oksek anmoyolikilme, kwakin ma tikinmilik yehwante kampa yeske ka se tahtoliste pa mochantiske ka tehwante.
Kwakin moshte in takam yewal kisaloya ompa kaha kalakil pa in Wepweblo mokawak ka se tahtoliste ka Hamor wan nikon Sikem, wan moshte pa in Wepweblo mochiwilik takotonili.
Tamiktik Hamor wan Sikem wan kikishtik Dína ompa kaha katka pa nikal Sikem wan kiwikak.
Kwakin walak ininpilwam Yakob kaha katkaloya mochi in mihmihke, kalakik wan ta'ishtikik mochi pa in pweblo.
Kinishtikik mochi borrego' wan chibo' wan mochi inik oksek yewal katkaloya ininyashka yehwante pa in Wepweblo, wan yewal katka pa kiyawak pa ininkwahmilme.
Kinsasakak mochiten wan moshte siwam wan ininpilwam. Konanak mochiten yewal katka pa kalitik pa in kalme.
Kwakin Yakob kinmili Shime'ón wan Lewí:
―Annishtalik pa polewiliste annishchiwilik pa annishkokoliske yehwante inik mochantilme pa in tal in kananeyo' wan in pereseyo'. Tehwante amo timiyak takam wan ta yehwante monichikok pa mo'onanaske ka newal, kwakin newal wan moshte pa nokal tiyeske tamiktilme.
Ma yok, in omente ininpilwam kinankilik:
―Kitoloya kampa amokwal katka pa kichiwiliskya tonohni kina se siwat yewal motek ka moshte takam?
Yakob mokwep pa BetEl
Kwakin Dyos kili Yakob: “Shimokets, shi shimochanti pa BetEl ompa shimoka. Ompa tikchiwas tanichikoliste tetelme pa Dyos yewal omoneshti kwah ticholotiyaya ka monohni Esa'ú.”
Ma timoketsak ma tiyak pa BetEl. Ompa nihnichikos tetelme pa niktalis tamakaliste pa Dyos yewal nishpale pa in tonat kwah nikatka pa in polewiliste, yewal hanse tonatim katka ka newal kaha niyaptiyas.”
Kwakin kimakak Yakob mochi in oksek dyose' yewal kinpiyaloya, wan temakak mochi inik sarsiya' yewal kiwikaloya pa ninnaka, wan Yakob kintapach itsinta tepotskwawit yewal amowEhka katka pa Sikem.
Kwakin panotiyak, wan Dyos kintitanil tamaptiliste pa mochi inik Wehwepweblo' yewal katkaloya itehtenko, yok amo'ak kintohtok ininpilwam Yakob.
Yakob wan moshte yehwante yaloya asik pa Luts,<sup>a</sup> yewal niyok kitokayoltil BetEl, pa in tal Kanán.
Wan Yakob kinichiko tetelme ka tatamakal pa Dyos in tal okitokayolti In-BetEl, yewal kinek kili in Dyos pa BetEl kampa ompa omoneshti Dyos kwah yewal cholowaya ka ninohni.
Wan Débora omik, yewal ki'apa Rebeka, wan kitapachok itsinta tepotskwawit amo wEhka katka BetEl. Kwakin kitokayoltik kaha kitapachok Alon-bakut yewal kinek kito in tepotskwawit kaha chokaloya.
Kwah walmokwep Yakob pa Padán-aram, oksep omoneshti Dyos wan kimashti
Dyos kili: “Ti'itok Yakob, ma yok yahmo ti'itokas Yakob. Ti'itokas Isra'El.” Kwakin Dyos okitokayolti Isra'El.
Wan Dyos kili: “Newal niDyos kipi chikawaliste. Shikinpi mopilwam wan shimomiyaptik. Pa tewal kisas se pweblo ka masewalme, wan takwitap yeske myak tanichikolme ka masewalme wan ika mokolinchim yeske reye'.
In tal yewal onihmak AbRaham wan Itsak, nimishmak tewal niyok, wan nikinmakas in tal mokolinchim yewal takatiske kwah timiki.”
Kikets Yakob se tet kina se taneshtiliste. Ompa kaha Dyos tahtowaya inak yewal. Wan kitekili nihugoUbaBino wan kishawili aseyte ipa tet,
ompa kaha Dyos okitakichil yewal, Yakob okitokayolti BetEl.
Miki Rakel
Panotiyak pa BetEl. Kwah amo wehkA katkaloya pa asiloskya pa Eprata, kwah Rakel okitakatilti nikonTakat, wan hyero kitakokolti.
Kwah kipanowaya takokoliste pa kitakatiltiskya, in siwat tapahti kili: “Amo shimomapti; kampa tikpiya okse mokonTakat!”
Kwah Rakel miktiyaya, wan tamtiyaya ni'ihyo okitokayolti Ben-oní, ma yok nitats Yakob, okitokayolti BenYamín.
Yok miki Rakel, wan kitapachok pa ot yewal ya pa Eprata, wan niyok itok BetLéhem.
Pa in tal kaha kitapachok kikets Yakob se tet weyak, wan pa ashka nestik nitaneshtiliste kaha kitapachok Rakel.
Isra'El okonan ni'ot wan kikets nikal tachiwal ka shashal tilawak ompa Migdal-Éder.
Kwah mochantiyaya Isra'El ompa pa tal, okalak Rubén nikon we kaha katka Bilha, wan Rubén omotek inak kwah panok myak tonatim kimat Isra'El.
Ininpilwam Le'a ye Rubén, yewal otakat ta'ishpa in oksek yek Shime'ón, Lewí, Yehudá, Isakar wan Sabulón.
Ininpilwam Rakel yek Yosé wan BenYamín.
Ininpilwam Bilha, nitikipanol siwat Rakel, yek Dan wan Neptalí.
Ininpilwam Silpa, nitikipanol siwat Le'a, yek Gad wan Asher.
Inik yek ininpilwam Yakob yewal kitakatiltik ompa Padán-aram.
Omokwep Yakob pa nikal nitats Itsak yewal katka pa Mamré, amo wEhka kaha katka Arba, yewal niyok itok, Hebrón, katka kaha mochantiyaya Itsak wan AbRaham.
Oyolti Itsak 180 shiwim
kwakin omihyot wan omik, kimani omonichik ka niwichalme yewal mikik. Omochi awel Itsak ompa oyol myak tonatim, kitapachok ininpilwam Esa'ú wan Yakob.
Nikolinchim Esa'ú
Inik yewal nikolinchim Esa'ú, yewal niyok itoka Edom.
niyok omonamikti ka Bashemat, nikon Yishma'El katka ninohniSiwat Nebayot.
Esa'ú ina yek ininpilwam: inak Ada okintakatilti EliPas; Bashemat, okitakatilti RehuEl;
wan Oholibamá, okintakatilti Yehúsh, Yálam wan Kora. Inik yek ininpilwam Esa'ú yewal okintakatilti pa Kanán.
Okinwik Esa'ú ininsiwam, ininpilwaTakam, ininpilwaSiwam, wan moshte yehwante mochantiloya pa nikal, wan niyolikilme wan mochi tekwanim kintikipanol takam wan mochi pa kishki tapiyaya pa in tal Kanán, wan panoti pa okse tal yok moseseman ka ninohni Yakob.
Yehwante in omente tapiyaloya miyak wan amokwal pa mochantiloskya se ka okse; kampa yok amo kipiyaloya ten kikwaloskya in yolikilme.
Yok Esa'ú, oy omochanti talTepet pa Se'ir, yewal niyok itoka Edom.
Ina yewal nikolinchim Esa'ú, in edomteko', yehwante mochantik talTepet pa Se'ir.
Ni'itokalme ininpilwam Esa'ú:EliPas nikon Ada, yewal ye nisiwa Esa'ú; RehuEl nikon Bashemat, wan nisiwa Esa'ú.
Ininpilwam EliPas yek Temán, Omar, Tsepó, Gatam, wan Kenas.
EliPas nikon Esa'ú niyok kipiyaya okse nikon, nisiwa itoka Timená, yewal okitakatilti Amalek.Moshte inik yek nikolinchim Ada, nisiwa Esa'ú.
Inik ininpilwam Oholibamá nisiwa Esa'ú, nikon Haná yewal katka nikon Sibeón, wan okintakatilti Esa'ú ininpilwam Yehúsh, Yálam wan Kora.
Inik yek wehwe nikolinchim Esa'ú:EliPas, ye nikon we Esa'ú, wan ininpilwam EliPas mochiwak tatakewalme Temán, Omar, Tsepó wan Kenas,
wan Kora, Gatam wan Amalek. Inik yek tatakewalme ka EliPas pa in tal Edom, ina yek nikolinchim Ada.
Okse nikon RehuEl, nikon in Esa'ú, wan ka ininpilwam RehuEl mochiwak tatakewalme Náhat, Séra, Shamá wan Misa.
Inik yek inintatakewalme ka ininpilwam RehuEl pa in tal Edom, wan inik nikolinchim Bashemat wan nisiwa Esa'ú.
Esaú wan nisiwa Oholibama, ininpilwam mochiwak tatakewalme Yehúsh, Yálam wan Kora. Ina yek tatakewalme nisiwa Esa'ú, Oholibamá ye nikon Haná.
Ina yewal nikolinchim Esa'ú, wan inintatakewalme yewal niyok itoka Edom.
Inik yek ininpilwam Se'ir in horeteko, yewal mochantiloya pa in tal:Lotán, Shobal, Sibeón wan Haná,
Dishón, Éser wan Dishán. Ina yewal yek tatakewalme ka horeteko' ininpilwam Se'ir ompa pa tal Edom.
Ininpilwam Lotán yek: Horí wan Hemam. Timená ye ninohniSiwat Lotán.
Ininpilwam Sibeón yek: Ayá wan Haná. In Haná yewal okit in nishtolol at ompa kaha amo'ak mochantiyaya, kaha okinwik niburro' nitats pa kikwaloskya sakat.
Ininpilwam Haná: Dishón wan Oholibamá, nikonSiwat Haná.
Ininpilwam Dishón yek: Hemdán, Eshbán, Itrán wan Kerán.
Ininpilwam Éser yek: Bilhán, Sawán wan Akán.
Ininpilwam Dishán yek: Uts wan Arán.
In wetatakewalme takam horeteko' yek: in Lotán, Sobal, Sibeón, Haná,
wan Dishón, Éser wan Dishán. Inik yek tatakewalme in takam horeteko' kina tatakewal pa in tal Se'ir.
In nireye' Edom
Inik yek reye' yewal reynarok pa mochital Edom kwah ayamo'ok katkaloya reye', ininpilwam Isra'El:
Bela nikon Be'or, reynar pa Edom. Nipweblo we kaha reynarowaya itoka Dinhaba.
Kimani omik Yobab, moka reynaroti Husham, yewal nital in pweblo Temán.
Kimani omik Husham, moka reynaroti Hadad nikon Bedad. In Hadad kintanili Midyán pa in tal Mo'Ab. Kwah mo'onanaloya Hadad Wepweblo kaha reynarowaya itok Awit.
Kimani omik Hadad, moka reynaroti Samlá, yewal nital in Wepweblo Masreká.
Kimani omik Samlá, moka reynaroti Sha'úl yewal nital in pweblo Rehobot katka pa itenko atenko Eprates.
Kimani omik Sha'úl, moka reynaroti Bál-hanán nikon Akbor.
Kimani omik Bál-hanán nikon Akbor, moka reynaroti Hadad. Wan nipweblo itoka Pahú. Nisiwa itoka MehetabEl, nikonSiwat Matred yewal ye nikonSiwat MeSaháb.
Ina ni'itokalme ka wetatakewalme Esa'ú, ka nikolinchim, wan niyok itokanilme kaha mochantiloya: Timená, Alwá, Yeter,
Oholibamá, Elá, Pinón,
Kenas, Temán, Mibetsár,
MagdiEl wan Iram. Esa'ú niyok itokaya Edom, wan inik yek niwetatakewalme Edom, kaha mochantiloya wan inintalme katkaloya.
Yakob wan ininpilwam
Yakob omochanti pa tal kaha mochantiyaya nitats, pa tal Kanán.
In tapowaliste ika Yakob wan ininpilwam.
Yosé kipiyaya 17 shiwim, kinkwitawiyaya borrego' wan chibo' ka ninohniwan, ininpilwam Bilha wan Silpa, in oksek ininsiwam nitats. Wan Yosé kinawatiyaya nitats Yakob ten amokwal yehwante kichiwaloya.
Isra'El kitasotaya miyak Yosé amoyok miyak kintasotaya in oksek ininpilwam, kampa okitakatilti kwah Isra'El katka kolinche. Wan Isra'El kichiwil Yosé se tilma kwal nesiya.
Kwah kitaloya ninohniwan itats kishki miyak kitasotaya Yosé wan yehwante amoyok kintasotaya, kwakin kikokoliloya amo kitakichililoya Yosé.
Se yowal Yosé tatemiki, kwah kinmili ninohniwan in tatemikiliste, kikwalanilik miyak,
kampa kinmiliyaya:
―Shinishkakik, annimishtakichilis in tatemikiliste yewal nikpi.
Tikatkaloya pa se tashosholtik tikinihilpitikatkaloya trigo ka manoho. Haniman nomanoho walmokets wan moka moketstik melahka, kampa anmomanoho' anmehwante kiyawaloloya ka ninewal wan mokwalpacholoya pa ni'ishpa yewal.
―Tihnek tikito tewal timochiwas towe, wan titichili mochi yewal tikpiyaske pa tikchiwaske?
Wan kikokoliloya miyak kina taketsaya ka nitatemikiliste ten kitemikiyaya.
Kwakin oksep tatemik, wan kinmili ninohniwan in yewal ten kitemiki:
―Shitakakik oksep nitatemik, yewal pa in tatemikiliste nikitaya in tonat, in meste wan 11 sitalme mokwalpacholoya no'ishpa newal.
Wan kitakichil nitats in tatemikiliste wan ninohniwan, nitats ki'ahwa kili:
―Ten tatemikiliste yewal ten tiktemik? Melak timotankwaketsaske mo'ishpa tewal monantsi wan newal wan niyok monohniwan?
Wan ninohniwan ki'ihyaloya, kampa kinekiloya yeloskya kina Yosé, ma yok nitats ki'ilnamikiyaya miyak in tatemikiliste.
Ninohniwan kinamakal Yosé
Se tonat, ninohniwan oyak takwitawik niborrego' nitats kaha tashosholtik pa Sikem.
Wan Isra'El kili Yosé:
Kinankili Yosé:
―Kwal onka.
―Shi shikinmit ta kwal kat monohniwan wan in borrego' wan hani shiwalmokwep pa tinishnawatis.
Wan okitetan Isra'El pa in ishtawak Hebron, wan Yosé asi pa Sikem. O'as Yosé pa Sikem,
wan se takat okit nehnemtikatka pa in ishtawak ompa wan kitahtinili:
―Ten tiktemotik?
Yosé kinankili:
―Nikintemotik nonohniwan. Shinichil kaha takwitaptikat borrego'?
Kinankili in takat:
―Panotiyak. Ompa onikinkak mo'ililoya ma tiyak pa Dotán.
Kwah yehwante kitak walaya wEhka Yosé, kwah ayamo'ok asiyaya yehwante motakichililoya kina kwal kimiktiloskya.
Mo'ilik sek ka oksek:
―Pa wal in tatemikiliste.
Ma tihmiktik wan ma tiktasak pa se takoyonke, wan tikinmiliske moshte kikwa se tekwan yolil pa kwawim. Kwakin tikitaske kina tamis nitatemikiliste!
Kwah kikak Ruben in, kinek kipale ka ninohniwam, kinmili:
―Amo tihmiktiske.
Anmehwante amo ankimiktiske. Shiktasak pa in takoyonke pa se tal kaha tawak, wan amoten shikchiwilik.
Kinmili Rubén kampa yewal kinek kipalewiskya Yosé pa yok kiwikaskya ka nitats.
Kwah o'as Yosé ka ninohniwan, kikishtilik nitilma kwal nesiya yewal nitats kichiwiliya yewal kikimtiyaya,
kikitskik wan kitasak pa in koyonke katka wak wan amo kipiyaya at.
Wan Yehudá kinmili ninohniwan:
―Ten tihtaniske ta tihmiktik tonohni wan kina tiktatiske, ta tihmiktik?
Ma tikinnamakiltik in takam yishma'elteko'; amoten tikchiwiliske. Shikilnamikik yewal tonohni.
Mokawak ka se tahtoliste ninohniwan,
kwakin kwah panotiyaloya in takam midyanteko', kikishtik Yosé ninohniwan pa in koyonke wan kinnamakiltik pa 20 tomiplata. In yishma'elteko' wan yehwante kiwikak pa Egipto.
Mokwep Rubén pa in koyonke wan tachi ompa amoten katka Yosé, kwakin kitsayani nishashalme.<sup>a</sup>
Mokwep kaha katkaloya ninohniwan, kinmili:
―In takatYankwik yahmo ten onka! Ashka ten nikchiwas?
Kwakin konanak itakemtel Yosé, kimiktik se chibo, wan kishashawilik yEste tilma.
Mokwepak ka itats kineshtilik tilma: “Tikitak in. Shikit ta nitilma mokon.”
Wan kitsayani nishashalme<sup>b</sup> Yakob wan motakemilti ka shashalme tiltik, yok ki'ahkok pa myak tonatim kikokowaya niyol.
Moshte ininpilwaTakam wan ininpilwaSiwam walaloya kiyolsewiloya, ma yok yewal amo kinekiya moyolsewiskya yok kitowaya: “Nikchokilis nokon hanse tonatim, kimani nimikis nitemos pa She'ol<sup>c</sup> kaha kat mimihke kaha onka nokon.” Wan nitats kichokiliyaya.
Asik pa Egipto, in takam madyanteko' wan kinamakiltik Potipar, Potipar in wetatakewan katka nitikipanol para'ó katka niwetatakewan gwacho'.
Yehudá wan Tamár
Pa inik tonatim, Yehudá kinka ninohniwan wan oy omochanti inak se adulamteko, itoka Hirá.
Ompa Yehudá ki'ishmat se siwat, nikonSiwat se takat kananeyo itoka Sú'a, omonamikti Yehudá inak yewal,
o'osti ta'apa nisiwa wan okitakatilti se nikonTakat, yewal kitokayolti Er.
Oksep o'osti ta'apa wan okitakatilti okse nikonTakat, yewal okitokayolti Onán.
Wan okipi okse nikon, yewal kitokayolti Selá, Yehudá katka pa in pweblo Kesib kwah takati Sela.
Kikonanil Yehudá se siwat itoka Tamár, pa monamiktiskya nikon we Er.
Kwakin Yehudá kili Onán: “Shimonamikti ka nisiwa monohni, kina kimatil kichiwal kwah miki se ninohni pa yok kinpiyas nikolinchim mopa tewal.”
Ma yok kimatiya Onán kampa amo yesloskya nikolinchim yewal. Kampa yok kwah motekaya inak yewal, tanokiyaya talpa pa amo kipiyaskya nikon, wan yok amo kipiyaskya nikolinchim ninohni mihke.
Wan in WeTatsDyos, amokwal okit kina okichi Onán, wan niyok kikishtil niyoliliste.
Kwakin Yehudá kili nisiwamon Tamar: “Shimoka pa nikal motats, pa kimani mo'apawa nokon Selá.” Kampa yewal tamat: Aso niyok miki kina ninohniwan. Yok Tamár panoti wan oy omochanti ka nitats.
Panok myak tonatim, wan omik nisiwa Yehudá, yewal nikonSiwat Sú'a. Kwah otam okichokil, Yehudá panoti pa in pweblo Timenat kaha katkaloya in takam kinshimtikatkaloya niborrego'. Wan ninihni Hirá, in adulamteko kitokatiya.
Kinawatik Tamár kampa nimontats panoti pa Timenat pa kinshimaskya niborrego',
kwakin mokishtil nishashalme wan kati motakemiltiloya siwam yewal kwah mikiloya inintaka inintawikal, kitapach itsontek ka se rebos pa yok amo'ak ki'ishmatiskya, kwakin omotal pa in ot kaha kalakil pa in pweblo itoka Enayim, yewal onka pa in ot Timenat. Tamar okit kina omo'apawaya Selá, ma yok Yehudá amo kimak Selá pa yok yeskya nitaka.
Wan Yehudá okit kwah panotiyaya wan mo'il pa niyol yewal siwat motek ka moshte, kampa tapachotikatka nishayak.
Kwakin sela mochi pa ot pa ki'asiskya yewal wan kili:
―Shimotemak pa nimotekas ka tewal. Kampa amo kimatiya kampa yewal katka nisiwamon.
―Wan ten tinishmakas ta nimotemak pa timotekas ka newal?
Yewal kinakili:
―Nimishtitanilis se chibo yewal nikinpi pa noyolikilme.
Wan yewal kinankili:
―Shinishkawil pek ten ka tewal kampa nihmatis ta melak tishwaltitanilis.
Wan Yehudá kili:
―Ten tihnek pa nimishmakas?
Wan Tamár kinankili:
―Moseyo kipi ikpal, wan mobara yewal tihwik.
Wan Yehudá okinmak, wan omotek inak yewal, wan pa yewal ta'apa.
O'as Yehudá kaha nitanichikolme, konan se chibo wan kititanili in siwat inak in ninihni in adulamteko, pa yok kiwalkwepaskya oksep inik yewal kikawil in siwat; ma yok amo kit in siwat.
Kintahtanili inik takam yehwante ompa katkaloya:
―Kaha onka in siwat yewal motek ka moshte takam nika pa Enayim, yewal katka pa sela in ot?
Yehwante kinankilik:
―Nika amo onka siwat yewal motek ka moshte takam.
Ninihni mokwep kaha katka Yehudá kili:
―Amo nikit yewal. Nichilik in takam yewal mochantil ompa amo katka se siwat kina yewal.
Wan Yehudá kito:
―Ma motakawil ka yewal ten nihkawil. Pa amo'ak wetskas pa tehwante. Kampa melak newal niktitanil in chibo, wan tewal amo tikit.
Panok yey mestim, wan kinawatik Yehudá, kilik:
Kwakin Yehudá kinmili:
―Shihkishtik shikchichinok ma mik!
Kwah kikishtitiyaloya yewal tatitan pa kinawatiloskya nimontats: “Nimishtahtani, shikit akyewal niseyo kipi ikpal, wan in bara, yewal nishta'apawilti.”
Kimani Yehudá kinishmat wan kito: “Yewal okichi kwal wan newal amokwal onikchi, kampa amo nihnamikti inak nokon Selá.” Wan amo'ik oksep omotek inak yewal.
O'as in tonat yewal takatiloskya, wan katkaloya omente piltontim pa'itik yewal.
Kwah takatitiyaloya se kikishti nimahwa; kwakin in siwatTapahti ki'ilpil se ikpal chichiltik pa nimahwa wan kito: “In okis ta'ishpa.”
Oksep kikalakti nimahwa in piltonte, kwakin okis ninohni. Wan in siwatTapahti kito: “Kina otikchi pa tikisaskya!” Wan kitokayolti Perets.<sup>a</sup>
Kwakin kis ninohni, yewal kipiyaya ta'ilpil pa nimahwa in ikpal chichiltik, wan kitokayoltik Séra.
Yosé wan nisiwa Potipar
Asik pa Egipto in takam, yishma'elteko' wan kinamakiltik Potipar, Potipar in wetatakewan katka nitikipanol para'ó katka niwetatakewan gwacho'.
kwah okit niwetatakewan kina katka in WeTatsDyos wan kina kipalewiyaya Yosé pa mochiten kichiwaya kisaya kwal.
Kwakin Potipar kitaya Yosé kina kwal kichiwaya, kitokayolti pa nikal kampa okitake pa takwitaptiyaskya mochi kishki tapiyaya.
Pa in tonat kimani Potipar kitakawili pa kikwitaptiyaskya nikal wan pa mochi kishki tapiyaya. Wan in WeTatsDyos kimashtiyaya Potipar, yok kina pa nikal wan yok kina pa nitashosholtik.
Yok Potipar in egiptiyo okitakawil pa takwitaptiyaskya Yosé pa mochi kishki tapiyaya, yahmo kimatiya pa kishki tapiyaya hanwel ten kikwaskya.
Yosé katka se takat kwal tachiyaya.
Kwah panok myak tonatim, nisiwa niwetatakewan kwal okit Yosé wan kili:
―Shimotek nonak.
Yosé amo kinek wan kili:
―Ka newal onka mochi yewal niyashka nowetatakewan pa nikal, wan yewal amoten ki'ilnamik pa nikal mochi yewal nishtake niyashka pa nikitatiyas.
Amo onka okse yok wetatakewan kina newal. Wan amoten nishtatsotili pa kishki tapi, kampa hanwel tewal, kampa tewal ti'isiwa. Kina kwal nikchiwaskya ten amokwal wan nimokatsawiliskya inak Dyos?
Pa se tonat, Yosé kalak kalitik pa kal pa kichiwaskya nitikipanoliste, amo'ak katka pa kalitik.
Wan in siwat kikitski Yosé pa nishashal kili: “Shiwal shimotek nonak!” Ma yok Yosé, kikawil nishashal pa nimahwam in siwat, motal pa kiyawak in kal.
Kimani yewal okit kina okikawil nishashal pa nimahwam wan motaloti okis pa in kal,
in siwat okinnots yehwante tikipanolme pa in kal wan kinmili: “Shikitak!, in hebreteko yewal notaka otishwalikil kinekiya tishpenawaltiskya tehwante. Okalak nika kinek motekaskya nonawak, wan wehwe nitsats.
Kwah nishkak nitsats, kika nishashal ka newal wan motaloti pa kiyawak.”
Wan yewal okital nishashalme Yosé sela pa kimani nitaka walmokwepaskya icha.
Kwakin kinawati kili: “In tikipanol hebreteko yewal titishwalikil owal ka newal kinek omotek nonawak.
Kwah nitsats pa nishpalewiloskya, okika itakemtel nahnewal wan omotal pa kiyawak.”
Kwah niwetatakewan kikak kina kitakichili nisiwa, yok onishchiwil motikipanol, yewal hyero kwalan
kikitskik Yosé kitsakwak pa in kalitik kaha kintsakwaloya yehwante nitakam in we para'ó.
katka WeTatsDyos inak Yosé kaha tatsakwal wan ki'ihniliyaya. Okichi kampa kwal kiwetsiskya in wetatakewan pa in tatsakwal,
niwe nitatsakwalme kimak Yosé pa kinkwitawiskya moshte yehwante ompa katkaloya, kitaliyaya Yosé pa kinkwitawiskya mochi in tikipanoliste yewal mochiwaya ompa kalitik.
In wetatakewan kaha tatsakwal amo monekiya pa takwitawiskya, amoten pa kishki takwitaptikatkaya Yosé kampa katka in WeTatsDyos inak yewal, wan kiyawiya kwal pa mochiten yewal kichiwaya.
Nitatemikiliste in kopero wan in panadero
Panok tonatim, ka in wetatakewan in kopero wan ka in wetatakewan panadero pa in werey Egipto kichiwak ten amokwal ika in tats.
Wan in okwalan ka in omente tatakewalme, inak in wetatakewan kopero wan in wetatakewan panadero,
wan tatake pa kintsakwaloskya kaha tatsawal katka Yosé, pa nikal niwetatakewan gwacho'.
In wetatakewan gwacho okitake Yosé pa kinkwitaptiyaskya yehwante wan yewal kintikipanoliyaya wan yehwante oyek miyak tonatim tatsakwalme.
Wan yehwante miyak tonatim tsaktiyak,
ompa pa in tatsakwaliste, pa se yowal in kopero wan in panadero ka in werey pa Egipto, kipiyak pa sesen se tatemikiliste pa se yowal wan pa sesen kipiyaloya ten kinek kitoskya.
kwakin kintahtanili inik wetatakewalme para'ó yewal katkaloya tatsakwalme kina yewal pa nikal in Tats:
―Pates anmoshayak amokwal nesil?
Yehwante kinankilik:
―Moshte omente titatemikik wan amo'ak onka ak tishnawati ten kinek kito totatemikiliste.
Kwakin Yosé kinmili:
―Han Dyos yewal kipi chikawaliste pa tishmashtis ten kinek kili se tatemikiliste. Shichilik ten ankitemikik?
Kwakin in wetatakewan ka in kopero kitakichili Yosé ten kitemiki:
―Pa notatemikiliste nikit se kwahmil ka uba' pa no'ishpa,
pa in uba' katkaya yey tsimolinke uba'. Kikisaya nishoch; wan hani nitaki yoksiyaya.
Nikpiyaya pa nomahwa nitapalkatonte para'ó. Nihkitske in uba', nikpatska nihugoUba pa in tapalkatonte, wan niktal pa nimahwam para'ó.
―In kinek kili: in yey tsimolinke kat yey tonatim.
Ma yok kwah panoske yey tonatim mishkishti para'ó wan mishtali oksep pa tiktikipanoli. Wan tiktali nitapalkatonte pa nimahwa para'ó, han kina tikchiwiliyaya, kwah tikatka nikopero.
Kwah yok motachiwas in newal nimishtahtani kampa shinishihnil. Wan shikilnamikiltil nahnewal in para'ó pa yok nishkishti pa in tatsakwal.
Kampa newal nishishtikik, pa in tal hebreteko'. Wan amoten onikchi pa nishtsakwaloskya!
Kwakin in panadero in wetatakewan kikak kina kili Yosé in kopero kina kwal katka tatemikiliste yewal kitakichiliya Yosé kili:
―Newal niyok nitatemik. Nikinmit yey chikiwim pa notsontek ka pan.
Pa in chikiwit katka takpak, katka ka miyak kwal nesiloya pane' ka in para'ó, wan inik totom walaloya kikwaloya inik pane' pa in chikiwit yewal katka ipa notsontek.
Kito Yosé:
In kinek kito:
―In yey chikiwim kat yey tonatim.
Kwakin pa yey tonatim katka in tonat yewal nitakatiliste para'ó, wan temak miyak takwaliste pa mitotiliste pa moshte inik inintikipanolme wetatakewalme. Tatake kinkishtik in wetatakewan kopero wan in wetatakewan panadero yehwante katkaloya tatsakwalme kinwalikak ininishpa inik inintikipanolme wetatakewalme.
Kikwipil in we kopero pa kitikipanoli wan yok oksep kital nitapalkatonte pa nimahwam para'ó pa koniskya nihugoubaBino.
Ma yok kisal pa se kwawit in we panadero han kina kili Yosé, kwah kinawat ten kinek kitoskya nitatemikiliste.
Ma yok, in we kopero amo ki'ilnamik Yosé, ki'ilka.
Itatemikiliste para'ó
Yok panok ome shiwim, wan se yowal tatemiki para'ó: Omo'it moketstikatka itenko atenko Nilo
okit kampa, kisaloya pa atenko chikome baka' wan tohtomawak kikwatikatkaloya sakat.
Haniman takwitap yehwante kisak oksek chikome baka', pa atenko Nilo pihpitsawak wan hyero nesiloya, moketsak itenko atenko Nilo, nahyehwante baka' kwal nesiloya.
Wan in baka' pihpitsawak wan hyero nesiloya kinkwaloya in chikome baka' kwahkwalme wan tohtomawak!
Haniman para'ó wal o'is.
Wan haniman kisaloya oksek chikome trigo, pihpitsawak kwihkwitanki kampa walyehyekaya kaha walkis tonat.
Wan in chikome trigo pihpitsawak kinkwaloya in chikome trigo kwal nesiloya!
Temtikatkaloya ka trigo wan o'is para'ó amo kimatiya ten kinek kitoskya nitatemikiliste.
Watsinko, amokwal nesiya hyero tamatiya yok kina tatemikiyaya, kwakin tatake pa walaloskya moshte in tashoshanilme wan in takam kimatiloya ten panoskya pa in Egipto, kintakichili nitatemikiliste. Ma yok amo'ak kinawatiyaya ten kinek kitoskya.
Kwakin in wetatakewan kopero wan kili para'ó: “Ashka nikilnamik ten yewal amokwal nikchi.
Se tonat kwah kwalan para'ó ka inintikipanolme, wan otishtsakwa newal wan niyok in wetatakewan panadero', pa nikal in wetatakewan gwacho'.
Pa se yowal, titatemikik moshte omente, ka sesen tehwante tikpiyaloya se ka okse tatemikiliste.
Katka ompa se takatYankwik se hebreteko, katka ka tehwante, nitikipanol in wetatakewan gwacho'. Tiktakichilik totatemikiliste, wan yewal tichili ten kinek kitoskya.
Wan yok motachi yok kina otichil! Newal nishtalik oksep kaha notikipanol, wan in okse kisalok.”
Kwakin tatake para'ó pa kiwalikaloskya Yosé, hanimam kikishtik kampa tsaktikatka. Kwakin moshim wan malti yok motakemilti okse nishashal, wan yok oy ka para'ó,
―Nikpi se tatemikiliste amo onka amo'ak nishnawatis. Kampa nitakak kwah tewal tihkak se tatemikiliste, tihmat ten kinek kitos.
Yosé kinankili para'ó:
―Ma yok amo pa newal onka, Dyos kimakas para'ó se tanankiliste kwal.
Kwakin para'ó kili Yosé:
―Pa notatemikiliste, onimo'it nimoketstikatka pa itenko in atenko Nilo.
Pa in atenko walkisaloya chikome baka' hyero tohtomawak wan kwal nesiloya, takwatikatkaloya sakat pa itenko in atenko.
Haniman takwitapit ka yehwante kisaloya oksek chikome baka' pihpitsawak hyero nesiloya. Yok amo'ik nikinmitaya baka' hyero nesiloya pa in tal Egipto!
Kwakin in baka' pihpitsawak hyero nesiloya, kinkwaloya in chikome baka' yehwante tohtomawak.
Ma yok, kwah tamik kinkwak, nesiloya han amoten kikwaloya, yok han pihpitsawak katkaloya hyero nesiloya. Kwakin niwal is.
“Nikpi okse tatemikiliste: Niyok pa notatemikiliste nikinmit chikome miyawalme trigo, temtikatkaloya ka trigo kwal nesiloya mo'apawaloya pa se nitankwa.
Wan in miyawalme pihpitsawak kinkwaloya in chikome miyawalme kwal nesiloya. Nikintakichili in tashoshanilme, wan amo'ak kimat ten kinek kitos.”
Kwakin Yosé kinankili para'ó:
―Melawak, in ome nitatemikiliste para'ó onka pa se. Dyos kinawati ten kinek kichiwas.
In chikome baka' kwal nesiloya chikome shiwim. Wan in chikome miyawalme kwal nesiloya niyok chikome shiwim. Inik tatemikiliste in pa se han.
Inik chikome baka' pihpitsawak wan hyero nesiloya, yewal takwitapit waltakisaloya ka yehwante, chikome shiwim wan niyok in chikome miyawalme pihpitsawak wan tachichinolme ka yehyekat totonki kaha takis tonat yok yeske chikome shiwim ka mayanaliste.
Yok nihnankili para'ó, Dyos kineshtili ten para'ó ten kichiwas.
Walaske chikome shiwim kwah moshte tapishkaske miyak pa mochi in tal Egipto,
kwakin walaske chikome shiwim ka mayanaliste, wan ki'ilkawaske mochi in miyak tapishkaliste yewal katka. Kwakin in mayanaliste kishitinis in tal!
Kampa yes miyak mayanaliste, yahmo ki'ilnamikiske in miyak tapishkaliste.
Wan para'ó kipi ohpa tatemikiliste kampa melak Dyos yok kichiwas, amo wehkAwas pa yok motachiwas.
Ma kintal para'ó wetakwitawilme ma yak pa mochital Egipto, ma konanak pa sesen makwil kostal se han ka in tapishkaliste kwah yeske in chikome shiwim ka miyak tapishkaliste.
Monek pa ankinichikoske mochi in trigo wan oksek shinashte pa inik shiwim ka miyak tapishkaliste shihwikak pa nichahpilme para'ó wan shikahkokik pa kishki Wehwepweblo', ka kintamakaske masewalme.
Kampa yewal ta'ahkokil yes ten kikwaske pa mochital pa kwah asiske inik chikome shiwim ka mayanaliste, pa yok in masewalme amo mikiske ka mayanaliste.”
Yok para'ó kwal kikak nitahtol Yosé wan moshte inik tikipanolme wetatakewalme.
Wan para'ó kintahtanili:
―Aso tikitaske okse takat kina yewal, kipi pa'itik ni'Espíritu Dyos?
Yok para'ó kili Yosé:
―Dyos mishmashti mochi in, se takat kimat hani motanishtili amo onka okse yok kina tewal, se takat yewal hanse tonatim kimatitiya ten monek pa kichiwas.
Nimishtalis niwetatakewan nokal wan moshte masewalme mishmawishtilitiyaske, pa mochiten tikintakiptiyas. Tewal tikpiyas chikawaliste, hanwel newal nikpiyas we chikawaliste ipa tewal, kampa newal niwerey.
Yosé wetatakewan ipa mochital Egipto
―Nimishtali niwetatakewan ipa mochital Egipto.
Kwakin para'ó mokishtil ni'aniyo yewal kiwikaya wan okitalil Yosé. Kitakemilti ka takemtel tachiwal ka lino, wan kitalil se koskat tachiwal ka oro.
Wan Yosé kitehkolti pa se yawaltik tatilanal ka kabayo' yewal takwitap kitokatiwalaya yewal wan yok tatake pa tsatsiloskya: “Shimotankwaketsak!” Yok para'ó kitali ipa mochital Egipto.
Wan para'ó kili Yosé:
―Newal nipara'ó, amo'ak pa mochi Egipto ki'olini nimahwa wan niyok nitankwa, ta tewal amo tikinmakawalti.
Para'ó kitokayolti Yosé, Tsapenat-panéha; wan kimak Asenat, nikonSiwat Potipera, totats in On pa yeskya nisiwa Yosé. Wan nehnemtinem Yosé ipa mochital Egipto.
Kipiyaya Yosé 30 shiwim kwah kiwikak ka para'ó, in weRey pa Egipto.
Wan okis Yosé kaha katka para'ó, wan nehnemtinem pa mochital Egipto.
Pa in chikome shiwim ye miyak tapishkaliste,
kinichiko Yosé mochi in tapishkaliste pa in chikome shiwim, kimani tapishkaloya miyak wan ki'ahkokiloya tapishkaliste pa in kwahmilme kitaliyaya pa inik Wehwepweblo' yewal amo katkaloya wEhka kampa katkaloya in kwahmilme.
Pa in tonatim kwah astiwalaloya in shiwim kampa yeskya in mayanaliste, Yosé nisiwa Asenat, okintakatilti ome ininpilwaTakam Asenat ye nikonSiwat Potipera in totats On.
Yosé nikon yewal okitakatilti ta'ishpa kitokayolti Manashé, kampa kito: “Niktokayolti yok kampa Dyos nishilkawilti mochi noyolkokoliste yewal nipan, wan moshte pa nikal notats.”
Okse nikon okitokayolti Eprayím, wan kito: “Kampa Dyos nishneshti kina se kwawit kimat taki pa in tal kampa newal onipan noyolkokoliste.”
Kwakin tamik in chikome shiwim ka miyak tapishkaliste pa in tal Egipto
kwakin asiyaya in chikome shiwim ka mayanaliste, kina kinmili Yosé. Katka mayanaliste pa mochital ma yok pa in tal Egipto katka pan.
Kwah moshte yehwante pa Egipto mayanak, in masewalme kitsatsilik para'ó pa kinmakaskya ten kikwaloskya. Wan para'ó kinmili moshte in egiptiyo': “Shiyak ka Yosé wan shikchiwak kina anmichili.”
Wan kimani o'as in mayanaliste pa mochi in tal, kwakin kintapo Yosé in kalme kaha kinahkokiloya in trigo wan kinnamakilti in egiptiyo' kampa katka miyak mayanaliste pa Egipto.
Wan pa mochi in oksek talme walak pa Egipto pa kikowililoskya trigo Yosé, kampa katka miyak mayanaliste pa mochi kishki tal.
Yosé ninohniwan yal pa Egipto
Kwah Yakob kimat kampa pa Egipto, katka takwal kwakin kinmili ininpilwam: “Ten ankichiptikak kan, pates anmo'itatikat ka anmehwante sek ka oksek?
Kwakin inik matahti ninohniwan Yosé yak pa Egipto kikowak trigo.
Ma yok Yakob amo kititan ka yehwante BenYamín, ninohni Yosé, kampa ma yok tamatiya pek ten kipanoskya pek ten amokwal.
Oyak ininpilwam Isra'El okikowak takwal, niyok yaloya oksek, kampa mayanaliste katka pa tal Kanán.
Wan Yosé reynarowaya pa Egipto, yewal kinnamakiltiya trigo moshte yehwante pa mochi kishki tal. Kwah asik Yosé ninohniwan, motankwaketsak talpa.
Kwah kinmit Yosé ninohniwan, haniman kinishmat; ma yok, omochi kina amo kinishmatiya, wan kintakichili ka kwalaniliste; kintahtanili:
―Wan anmehwante!, kampa anwalal?
Kinankilik:
―Tiwalal pa tal Kanán, pa timishkowiliske takwal.
Ma yok kinishmat Yosé, yehwante amo ki'ishmatik.
Kwakin ki'ilnamik Yosé nitatemikiliste nahyehwante, wan kinmili:
Yehwante kinankilil:
―Amoyok, Tats! In motikipanolme tewal, walal kikowal takwal.
Moshte tehwante ininpilwam se takat kwal, tehwante titakam kwahkwalme. Amo tiwalal tita'ispiyarol!
Yosé kinmili:
―Amo melak! Anwalal antachiyal kaha kwal kalakiske pa total ka anmogwacho' pa mo'onanaske.
Yehwante kinankilik:
―Tehwante, motikipanolme, titakatilme 12 ininpilwam, pa se takat yewal mochanti pa tal Kanán. In tipichi moka ka nitats, wan in okse nikon yahmo yoltik.
Yosé kinmili:
―Yok kina annimichilis. Amehwante anta'ispiyarotikat!
Wan ka in nihmati: Nimishmak notahtoliste ka niyoliliste in para'ó, wan amo kisaske nika kaha kat hanwel kwah walas monohni tipichi.
Kintsakwa Yosé pa yey tonatim.
Pa in yey tonatim kinmili Yosé:
―Ta ankinekil yoliske shikchiwak in kampa newal nimomapti pa i'ishpa Dyos.
Ta ankat takam kwahkwalme, ma moka se anmonohni tsaktiyas wan in oksek ma mokwepak wan ma ankiwikak trigo pa yok antakwaske pa anmo'icha.
Shihwalikak anmonohni tipichi pa nihmatis ta ankitotikat melawak. Wan yok amo anmikiske.
Wan yehwante kitol haha,
mo'ililoya sek ka oksek:
―Tehwante timokatsawaltik ka tonohni. Moyolkokotikatkaya wan tishtahtaniyaya pa tikihnililoskya wan amo tihnekik tihkakik. Kampa ashka tishpanotik in amokwal.
Rubén kinnankili:
―Amo annimichili pa amo kikatsawiltiloskya in takatYankwik, wan amo ankinekik annishkakik. Ashka monek pa titashtawaske kampa tihmiktik!
Yosé panoti oksela ka yehwante wan chokaya, kwakin, walmokwep pa tahtoskya ka yehwante, wan ika ka yehwante kikitski Shime'ón pa i'ishpa moshte yehwante kitsakwak.
Kinmili Yosé ininwetatakewan pa nikal pa kintemiltililoskya inintamamal ka trigo, wan pa kinkwepililoskya mochi sesen inintomi kintalilik pa sesen inintamamal, wan kinmakaloskya takwaliste pa kikwaloskya pa ot. Wan yok kichiwak.
Kwakin yehwante kintamamaltilik ininburro' ka trigo wan mokwepak.
Asik ompa kaha panoloskya in yowal se ka yehwante kitapo nitamamal pa kitamakaskya niburro, wan okit nitomi pa ikamak nitamamal!
Kinmili ninohniwan:
―Nishkwepilik notomi! Shikitak, nika onka, pa nokostal!
Wan hyero moyoyokatikatkaloya, mo'ililoya sek ka oksek:
―Ten yewal Dyos tishchiwilitik?
Asik pa ikal itats Yakob pa in tal Kanán, kitakichilik ten kinpanowaya, wan kilik:
―In takat tahto ka tehwante ka kwalaniliste pa mochital tichiliyaya kampa tikatkaloya kina ta'ishpiyaroliste.
“Tikat 12 tinohniwan, ininpilwam totats. Se amo yoltik, wan tonohni tipichi onka ka totats pa Kanán.”
’Kwakin in takat yewal niwetatakewan in tal tichili: “Ashka nihmati ta anmehwante ankat takam kwahkwalme: Shihkawak se anmonohni, ka newal wan shiyak shihwikak takwaliste pa amo mayanaske pa anmokal.
Shinishwalikilik anmonohni tipichi ka newal. Pa yok nihmati kampa amo ta'ispiyarotikat kampa ta melak kat takam kwahkwalme. Kwakin annimishkwepili anmonohni, wan annimishmakawalti pa antakowaske wan antanamakaske pa mochital.”
Kwah kinokiloya inintamamal, ninohniwan Yosé kitak pa sesen inintamamal katka inintomi yehwante. Kwah yehwante wan nitats kitak inintomi, hyero momaptik.
Kwakin Yakob kinmili:
―Anmehwante annishkistiliske mochi nopilwam! Yosé yahmo onka ka tehwante, niyok Shime'ón, wan ashka ankinekil ankiwikaske BenYamín! Mochi inik tachiwaliste wetsil nopa newal!
Kwakin Rubén kili nitats:
―Tikinmikti in omente nopilwam ta amo nimishwalkwepil BenYamín. Shinishkawil kampa newal nihkwitawis wan nimishwalkwepilis.
Yakob kili:
―Nokon amo yas ka anmehwante! Kampa omik ninohni, wan yewal han moka. Ta ten okipan pa ot yewal kampa yal, kwakin anmehwante ankipiyaske teshpawiliste kampa nimikis pa nimoyolkokos nitemos pa She'ol<sup>a</sup> kaha kat mihmihke.
Katka we mayanaliste pa tal Kanán.
Kwah kitamik in trigo yewal kiwalikak pa Egipto. Yakob kinmili:
―Shimokwepak, wan shiyak shihkowak oksep trigo pa titakwaske.
Wan Yehudá tanankili:
―Wan yewal takat otichil ta amo ankwalikal anmonohni tipichi, amo shiwalak shichitak.
Ta tiktitan tonohni ka tehwante, titemoske timishkowiliske trigo.
Ta amo tihnek tiktakewas amo titemoske. Kampa in takat tichili amo annimichitas ta amo ankwalikal ka anmehwante.
Kwakin kito Isra'El:
―Pates yok okilik kampa ankipiyaloya okse takat anmonohni?
Yehwante tanankilik:
Kwakin Yehudá kili Isra'El:
―Shiktitan takatYankwik ka newal wan ma tiyaptiyak, kampa yok tewal wan topilwam tiyoliske amo timikiske.
Newal nihkwitawis; pa amoten kipanos yewal. Newal tinishtahtanis in tapowaliste ten panos, ta amo nimishwalkwepil nika kaha tikat, newal nikpiyas tateshpawiliste pa hanse.
Ta amo inik timochiptiyaloskya, ashka yatiyaloskya wan tiwalmokwepalosya ohpa!
Kwakin nitats Isra'El, kinmili:
―Ta amo onka kina kwal, kwakin shikchiwak in: Shihwikilik pa anmotamamal temakaliste kwal in takat, yewal tikchiwal wan mo'apawal pa in tal, shihwikilik tipit balsamo, tipit nekti, wan sek yewal fragante, wan mira yewal fragante, wan sek nwese', wan almendra'.
Shihwikilik in tomi yewal anmishwalkwepil kwah anwalmokwepak, yewal ankitak pa nikamak anmotamamal. Wan shihwikilik oksep in tomi wan niyok shihwikak ka tashtawaske, kampa oksela okital.
Shihwikak anmonohni tipichi wan shimokwepak ka in takat.
Yewal in Dyos kipi chikawaliste ma kichi pa in takat pa kipiyas ta'ihnililiste pa anmehwante pa yok kimakawas in okse anmonohni wan BenYamín! Pa kishki newal, hanwel ta monek pa nikinpolos nopilwam, yewal ten nikchiwas! Ma nimoka ka amoten nokon!
Kwakin kiwikak yehwante takam inik temakaliste, wan niyok kiwikak tomi, pa kikwepililoskya wan ka takowaloskya wan niyok kiwikaloya ninohni BenYamín, temok pa Egipto. Wan moneshtik pa i'ishpa Yosé.
In takat kichi kina kili Yosé wan kinwik pa nikal.
Kampa yehwante momaptitikatkaloya in takam kwah kinwikaloya pa nikal Yosé: “Kitoloya ka in tomi yewal tishkwepilik kwah timokwepaloya pa tokal. Ashka kinek tishkitskis, pa tishchiwas inintikipanolme, wan pa tishkishtilis toburro'.”
Kwakin ki'asik in wetatakewan pa nikal Yosé, wan pa in tatapoli pa in kal tahtok inak yewal kilik:
Shitishihnil, tats:
―Melak setonatim tehwante tiwalak timokowilik takwal;
kwah timokwepak, timoketsak kaha timosewiloskya in yowal, kwah tikintapok totamamal ompa katka totomi pa sesen nikamak totamamal mochi totomi. Yok tihwalikak oksep in tomi ka tehwante!
Niyok tihwalikak tomi pa titashtawaske in trigo yewal tihkowaske. Amo tihmatil akyewal kital totomi pa totamamal!
Wan in wetatakewan pa nikal kinnankili:
―Amo shimomaptik. AnmoDyos anmehwante wan niDyos anmotats anmishtalil in tomi pa anmotamamal. Newal nikonan anmotomi yewal nishtashtawilik.
Kwakin kiwalikak Shime'ón ka yehwante,
Yehwante, kichiwak temakaliste, inik yewal kiwalikilik Yosé kwah asiskya takwalispa, kampa takakik ompa takwaloskya.
O'as Yosé pa nikal, ninohniwan kimakak inik yewal kiwalikilik, wan mopachok ni'ishpa pa in tal.
Kintahtanili Yosé kina katkaloya, kwakin kinmili:
―Kina onka anmotats, in tats kolinche yewal annichilik? Yoltik?
Yehwante kinankilik:
―Totats, motikipanol, kwal onka, wan yoltik.
Wan mopachok ni'ishpa yewal pa kichiwililoskya tamawishtiliste.
Kwakin Yosé otachi wan okit BenYamín, ninohni in okse nikon nitats wan ninantsi, wan kito:
―In yewal anmonohni tipichi, in yewal nishtakichilik anmehwante? Ma mishmashti Dyos, nokon!
Kwah kit Yosé ninohni, kinekiya chokaskya, kampa kinekiya kinapaloskya yok yewal mo'isiwilti. Okalak pa nikwarto wan ompa chokaya.
Yosé takwaya oksela, katkaloya ninohniwan pa okse, kaha takwal wan in egiptiyo katkaloya ka Yosé takwaloya pa okse kaha takwal. Katka in egiptiyo' kampa amokwal takwaloskya kaha takwaloya hebreteko', kampa tatatsotal katka pa egiptiyo'.
Motalik Yosé ninohniwan pa annimesa han kina shiwim kinpiyaloya, kina takatiloya yewal we ka Rubén wan tam ka BenYamín kwah tamik motalik, ninohniwan Yosé mokawak mo'itatikat.
Katka in takwaliste kaha takwa Yosé, wan nitikipanol ki'onan in takwaliste wan kinwalikilik sesen wan sesen ninohniwan se shikal temtiyaya ka takwaliste wan kiwikilil BenYamín we takwal kina makwil shikalme pa nishikal, yok we katka nitakwal. Wan takonik ka Yosé, wan kipiyaloya pakiliste ka yewal.
Yosé okital tapalkatonte tachiwali ka plata pa BenYamín
Kwakin Yosé okinots niwetatakewan pa nikal: “Shikintemiltil inintamamal inik takam ka trigo kishki temi, shikintalil inintomi pa mochi sesen pa nikamak inintamamal.
Shiktal niyok notapalkatonte tachiwal ka plata pa itik nitamamal in tipichi yankwik ika nitomi, ka tashta trigo.” Wan niwetatakewan pa nikal kichi kina kili Yosé.
Tahtanesti, ninohniwan Yosé kintakewak pa yaloskya pa mokwepaloskya inak ininburro'.
Ayamo'ok yaloya wEhka pa in wepweblo' wan Yosé okinots niwetatakewan pa nikal: “Shi! Shikinas in takam! Kwah tikinasis, shikinmil: ’Pates annishtashtawilik amokwal wan anmishmak in kwal?
Pates anki'ishtikilik yewal nitapalkatonte tachiwal ka plata wan kaha nowetatakewan takoni wan kaha kit ten panos? In amokwal ten ankichiwak!”
Kwah niwetatakewan pa nikal kinas, kinmili oksep inik tahtolme.
―Pates yok tikito, notats we in? Tehwante motikipanol amo'ik tikchiwal ten yok!
Shikit, timishwalkwepilik tomi yewal tikitak pa'itik nikamak totamamal sesen ka tehwante, tihwalikak kwah tikisak pa Kanán. Kina yok tikishtikililoskya plata, oro pa nikal in tats?
Ta se ka tehwante motikipanol tikit, ma kimiktik wan tehwante, in oksek timochiwaske nitikipanol nikal in notats.
Wan niwetatakewan pa nikal kito:
―Ma ye kina ankitol, akyewal kipiyas tapalkatonte tachiwal ka plata yes notikipanol; wan anmehwante mokawaske tamakawaliste pa in tateshpawiliste.
Kintemowik sesen inintamamal wan kitalik pa tal, wan ka sesen kintapok.
In wetatakewan otatem okipewalti ka ninnohni we wan otam ka ninohni tipichi. Kitak yawiya pa nitamamal BenYamím in tapalkatonte tachiwali ka plata!
Kwakin motsayanilik ininshashalme.<sup>a</sup> Kintamamaltilik ininburro' wan mokwepak pa in Wepweblo.
Kimani Yehudá wan ninohniwan asik pa nikal Yosé, yewal ompa katkaya ayamo yawiya tikipanowaya. Kwakin motankwawetsak pa tal ni'ishpa yewal,
kinmili Yosé:
Kinankili Yehudá:
―Kina timichiliske Tats! Ten tikitoske! Kina timishnishtiliske kampa amo tikpiyal takokoliste? Ka Dyos yewal kineshti totakokoliste tehwante motikipanol. Ashka tehwante tiyeske motikipanol, notats we, tehwante tonohniwan wan in se yewal kipiyaya in tapalkatonte tachiwal ka plata.
Yosé kinmili:
―Amo'ik pek ten nikchiwaskya! In yewal aki kipiyaya tapalkatonte yes notikipanol. Wan in oksek mokwepaske ka anmotats ka mosewiliste, amo'ak anmehwante anmishtsakwili.
Kwakin Yehudá o'as ka yewal wan kili:
―Newal nimishtahtani tewal, Tats, shikit newal nimishtahtani motikipanol nimichili tewal tats sek tahtolme pa monaka. Amo shikwalan ka newal motikipanol, kampa newal, nimichit tewal ti'onka kina para'ó.
Tewal tats titishtahtanil tehwante motikipanol ta ankipiyal anmotats wan okse anmonohni,
wan tehwante titanankilik tikpiyal totats kipi myak shiwim, wan se tonohni tipichi yewal okitakatilti kwah notats kolinche katka ka myak shiwim. Wan niyok tikitok kampa totats hyero miyak kinek wan yewal hanse mokawiliyaya nikon ka in se han nisiwa, kampa nokse ninohni omik.
Kwakin tewal timotikipanolme otishtahtan pa tihwalikaloskya kampa tihnek tikishmatiskya.
Wan timichilik tewal notats kolinche amo kika in piltonte nitats kampa, ta kika, kwakin nitats miki.
Timokwepak kaha motikipanol notats, wan tikilik in tewal tats titichili.
Kwah tichili totats: “Shimokwepak shihkowak tipit takwaliste pa tehwante.”
Wan tehwante titanankilik: “Amokwal tiyaske ta amo ya ka tehwante tonohni tipichi amo tiyaske. Amo tikitaske nishayak in takat ta amo oy ka tehwante tonohni tipichi.”
Totats, in motikipanol, kito: “Ankimatil kina annishtakatilti nosiwa ome nopilwam.
Ka in omente se yahmo onka ka newal. Wan nikito kampa melak se yolikilme kika tahtakito, wan ashka amo'ik nikita pa mochi in shiwim.
Ta annishkishtilik niyok nokon, wan niyok ta okipan pek ten, kwakin kichiwaske kampa in tsontek temos pa She'ol<sup>b</sup> kaha kat mihmihke!”
’Ashka, shikit, kimani nimokwepas newal motikipanol, ta in takatYankwik ta amo ya ka tehwante, in niyoliliste notats pipichotik inak niyoliliste in takatYankwik,
in panos kimani ta amo okit in piltonte, mikis, wan motikipanolme kichiwaske pa moyokoltis kampa notsontek istak yok temos pa She'ol kaha kat mihmihke.
Newal motikipanol nikili notats melak kampa nihkwepiliskya in piltonte. Nikili: “Ta amo nihwalik oksep ka tewal, noTats newal, kwakin newal nikpiyas hanse tateshpawiliste mo'ishpa.”
Ashka, shinishmakawilti pa newal motikipanol nimokawas nika pa niyes motikipanol pa tewal, tats ma nimoka wan in piltonte shihmaka pa mokwepas ka ninohniwan.
Yosé kinmashti ninohniwan
Kwakin Yosé yahmo kwal kina motsakwiliskya ininishpa pa moshte inintikipanolme, yewal tsats: ''Shikisak moshte anmehwante nika!” Yok amo katkaya ni se inintikipanolme Yosé hanwel ninohniwan. Kwah yewal kinnawati akyewal katka,
kwakin walchokaya chikawak wan kimatik inik egiptiyo', wan niyok kimatik yehwante pa nikal para'ó.
Newal niYosé kinmili ninohniwan:
―Yoltik notats?
Wan amokwal kina kinankililoskya ninohniwan kampa momaptiloya i'ishpa yewal.
Kwakin Yosé kinmili:
―Shiwalak ka newal!
Yehwante monichikok ka yewal, wan kinmili:
―Newal annimonohni Yosé, in yewal ankinamakak pa Egipto.
Ashka panok ome shiwim ka mayanaliste pa in tal, wan pa inik oksek makwil shiwim amo yes tatokaliste wan tapishkaliste.
Dyos onishwaltitan ta'ishpa ka anmehwante: pa yok mokawaloskya anmokolinchim pa in mochital wan pa anmishmakas yoliliste ka we tapololtiliste.
Amo anmehwante aki annishtakewak pa nikek han Dyos. Kampa onishtal kina nitats para'ó wan niwetatakewan pa mochi nikal, wan in wetatakewan pa mochi in tal Egipto.
Ashka, shi'isiwik! Shimokwepak kaha notats wan shikilik: “Yok kito yewal mokon Yosé: Dyos nishchi we nireynaroliste pa mochi Egipto. Ma wal ka newal. Amo shiwehkA.
Timochanti pa in tal Goshen, amo wEhka kaha newal niyes, ompa anyeske tewal wan anmopilwam, wan anmokolinchim wan mochi inik tanichikolme borrego', chibo', baka' wan mochi yewal ten tikpi.
Nika annimishmakas takwaliste tewal wan moshte mochantilme pa mokal. Wan moshte yehwante kat ka tewal, pa mochiten kipiyaske, kampa yeske oksek makwil shiwim ka mayanaliste.’”
Anmehwante ankital wan BenYamín kampa melak newal nitahtotik ka anmehwante.
Shikilik notats kina niWe nitatakewan nika Egipto, wan shikilik mochi yewal ankitak. Wan shi'isiwik wan shihwalikak notats!
Kwakin Yosé kinapalo ninohni BenYamín, wan walchokaya BenYamín wan Yosé.
Chokaya niyok, kintenamikik moshte ninohniwan wan walchokaya ka yehwante. Kwakin ninohniwan kiwaltakichilik.
Wan kili para'ó Yosé: “Shikinmil monohniwan ma kintamamaltilik anniyolikilme wan ma mokwepak pa in tal Kanán.
Shinishwalikilik anmotats wan moshte mochantilme pa nikal. Wan newal annimishmakas in kwahkwalme talme pa Egipto, wan anmehwante ankikwaske in kwal yewal pa in mochital.
Niyok shikinmil, shikinwikak sek yawalokilme nika pa in tal Egipto pa ankwalikaske anmosiwam wan anmopilwam, wan shihwalikak anmotats,
amo shikilnamikik amoten yewal pa anmoyashka, kampa mochi yewal onka kwal pa Egipto wan yok anyes anmoyashka.”
Yok kichiwak ininpilwam Isra'El. wan Yosé kinmak yawalokilme kina kili para'ó, wan niyok kinmak takwaliste ten monekiskya pa ot.
Kinmak sesen wan sesen shashalme yahyankwik, wan BenYamín kimak 300 tomiplata wan makwil takemiltiliste shashalme.
Wan nitats kititanil matahti burro' ka tamamaltiliste ka in kwahkwal ten onka pa Egipto, wan matahti burra' tamamtiyaloya trigo, wan ten monekiya pa ot.
Kwakin Yosé kintake ninohniwan pa yaloskya pa in ot kinmili: “Amo shimokwalantik pa ot!”
Yok kisak pa in tal Egipto wan asik kaha nitats in Yakob, pa in tal Kanán.
Kilik: “Yosé yoltik! Yewal reynarotik pa mochi Egipto!” Amo kimat ten kitoskya Yakob amo kinneltokaya,
Kwakin kito: “Melak! Yoltik nokon Yosé! Niyas nikitas ashka kwah ayamo'ok nimiki.”
Yakob wan ininpilwam pa Egipto
Yok panoti Isra'El ka mochiten tapiyaya. Yok o'as pa BérSheba, kitalili tatamakal niDyos nitats Itsak.
Pa se tayo Dyos otahto ka Isra'El tachiyaya kina tatemiktiyaskya kili:
―Yakob! Yakob!
Kinankili:
―Nika ni'onka.
Kili:
―Newal niDyos, niDyos motats. Amo shimomaptiti pa tiyas Egipto, kampa ompa nikchiwas se tanichikol we.
Niyas monak Egipto, wan niyok nikchiwas pa tiwalmokwepas. Wan Yosé yes ka tewal pa kintsakwas moshtololme kwah timiki.
Niyok kinwikak ininyolikilme wan kinwikak mochi ininyashka, yewal Yakob tapiyaya pa Kanán.
Yok Yakob kinwik pa Egipto ininpilwaTakam wan ininpilwaSiwam wan nikolinchimTakam wan nikolinchimSiwam, moshte yehwante oyak inak yewal.
Yok itokaloya ininpilwam Isra'El wan Yakob nikolinchim yehwante oyak pa Egipto:Rubén ye nikon we, Yakob.
Ininpilwam Rubén yek: Henok, Palú, Hesrón wan Karmí.
Ininpilwam Shime'ón yek: YemuEl, Yamín, Óhad, Yakín, Tsohar wan Sha'úl, yewal katka nikonSiwat kananeya.
Ininpilwam Lewí yek: Gershón, Koat wan Merarí.
Ininpilwam Yehudá yek: Er, Onán, Selá, Perets wan Séra. (Er wan Onán mikik pa in tal Kanán.)Ininpilwam Perets yek: Hesrón wan Hamul.
Ininpilwam Isakar yek: Tolá, Puwá, Iyob wan Shimróm.
Ininpilwam Sabulón yek: Séred, Elón wan YahalelEl.
Niyok yek ininpilwaTakam yewal Le'a okitakatilti Yakob pa in tal Padán-aram, wan niyok okitakatilti nikonSiwat Dína. IninpilwaTakam wan ininpilwaSiwam yek 33 masewalme.
Ininpilwam Asher yek: Imná, Yishwá, Yishwí, Berihá wan Séra, ninohniSiwat yehwante.Ininpilwam Berihá yek: Héber wan MalkiEl.
Yehwante okintakatilti Silpa ininpilwam Yakob. Yewal Labán okimak Le'a pa yeskya nitikipanolSiwat. Katkaloya 16 masewalme.
Inik yek ininpilwam Rakel, nisiwa Yakob: Yosé wan BenYamín.
Pa Egipto, okitakatilti Yosé ka nisiwa Asenat, nikonSiwat Potipera, totats On: Manashé wan Eprayím.
Ininpilwam BenYamín yek: Bela, Beker, Ashbel, Gerar, Namán, Ehi, Rosh, Mupim, Hupam wan Ard.
Inik yek ininpilwam Rakel, okintakatilti Yakob katkaloya 14 masewalme.
Nikon Dan ye: Hushim.
Ininpilwam Neptalí yek: YahetsEl, Guní, Yeser wan Shilem.
Inik yek ininpilwam Yakob yewal okinpi inak Bilha. In tikipanolSiwat yewal Labán kimak nikonSiwat Rakel. Yek chikome masewalme.
Moshte inik masewalme yehwante yaloya inak Yakob pa Egipto, moshte katkaloya nikolinchim wan katkaloya 66, amo katkaloya tapowalme ininsiwamom.
Kwakin Yakob kitake Yehudá kampa katka Yosé pa yok kiliskya Yosé pa kinamikiskya pa in tal Goshen.
Kinmili Yosé nitakam pa kipiyaloskya nikareta, pa yok yaskya pa Goshen pa kinamikiskya nitats Isra'El. Haniman kwah okit Yosé pa i'ishpa nitats kinapalo, nitats wan owehkA moka chokati.
Isra'El kili Yosé:
―Ashka kwal pa nimikis! kampa nimichit tewal kampa tiyoltik!
Kwakin kinmili Yosé ninohniwan wan yehwante pa nikal nitats:
―Ma nitakis pa nitahto ka para'ó pa nikili nonohniwan, wan yehwante kat ka nikal notats, yewal mochantiloya pa in tal Kanán, yehwante walak ka newal.
In takam takwitawilme tanichikolme ka yolikilme kinpiyal borrégo', chibo' wan baka', kinwalikak wan mochiten tapiyaloya.
Kwah anmishnotsa wan anmishtahtanili pa ten tikipanoloya,
shikilik pa kishki tiyoltikat wan pa ashka inik tehwante timotikipanolme tewal tikinkwitawil yolikilme, kina inik towichalme yehwante mikik. Yok anmokawaske pa in tal Goshen, kampa inik egiptiyo' kipiyal tatatsotalme pa mochantiske inak yehwante takwitawilme yolikilme borrego.
Yosé oy ka para'ó, wan kili:
Kinonan Yosé makwil ninohniwan wan kinwalik pa ni'ishpa para'ó.
Kinmili para'ó ninohniwan Yosé:
―Ten tikipanoliste ankimatil?
Yehwante kinankilik para'ó:
―Tehwante motikipanol titakwitawilme tanichikolme ka yolikilme yok kina towichalme yehwante mikik tishkawilik.
Niyok kilik para'ó tiwalak pa timochantiske nika kampa onka miyak mayanaliste pa Kanán, amo onka sakat pa niyolikilme motikipanolme. Kampa mayanaliste hyero we! Timishtahtanil kampa titishmakas pa timochantiske pa in tal Goshen.
Para'ó kili Yosé:
―Motats wan monohniwan ashka walak ka tewal.
Wan in tal Egipto pa mo'ishpa onka tewal. Shikinmak motats wan monohniwan pa in tal kwal, ma mochantik pa Goshen. Ta tihmat ta ka yehwante kat sek kimatil takwitawil yolikilme, kwakin shikintal pa yeske notatakewalme pa noyolikilme.
Yosé kiwik niyok Yakob, nitats kaha para'ó, pa ki'ishmatiskya wan Yakob kimashti para'ó.
―Kishki shiwim tikpi?
Yakob kinankili para'ó:
―Newal nikpi 130 shiwim niyaptinem nika nepa amo myak shiwim nikpi pa niyoltik wan inik shiwim amokwal onipan, ayamo'ok nikashilti pa niyolis kina ininyoliliste nowichalme yehwante mikik, pa inik tonatim yaptinemil nika nepa.
Kwakin Yakob kimashti para'ó, wan okis pa ni'ishpa.
Yok Yosé kinmak nitats wan ninohniwan talme pa Egipto, in tal kwal amoyok kina oksek talme kaha ta'itok Ramsés, kichi kina kili para'ó.
Niyok Yosé kinmakaya takwaliste ninohniwan, pa moshte nikal nitats, pa kishki myak ininpilwam katkaloya pa sesen nikal.
Yosé tikipanowaya pa in tonatim pa mayanaliste
Amo katka ten kikwaloskya, pa mochi in tal kampa katka miyak mayanaliste pa Egipto wan pa Kanán. Amo kipiyaloya ten kikwaloskya, miktiyaloya ka mayanaliste.
Yosé kinichiko mochi in tomi pa in tal Egipto wan pa tal Kanán, kampa kinamakaya trigo wan yewal kitashtawililoya in tomi kiwalikaya pa nikal para'ó.
Kwah yahmo katka tomi pa egiptiyo' wan pa Kanán, kwakin walak moshte egiptiyo' kaha Yosé kilik:
Wan kinmili Yosé:
―Shikinwalikak anmoyolikilme, annimishmakas ten ankikwaske kampa antashtawaske ka anmoyolikilme.
Yok kiwalikilik Yosé ininyolikilme, wan kinmak ten kikwaloskya, tashtawak ka ininkabayo', ininborrego', ininchibo', ininbaka' wan ininburro', yok Yosé in egiptiyo' kinnamakiltiyaya ten kikwaloskya yehwante tashtawaloya ka nitanichikolme yolikilme.
Kwah otam in shiwit walak ka Yosé oksep pa okse shiwit kilik:
―Amo tikpiyal ten, kampa otam totomi wan toyolikilme. Amo tikpiyal amoten pa timishmakaske, hanwel tokwerpo tonakayo wan totalme.
Kampa timikiske mo'ishpa ka tewal wan ka totalme niyok? Shitishko tehwante wan totalme. Pa yok tishmakas ten tikwaske. Tehwante wan totalme tiyeske inintikipanolme para'ó. Hanwel shitishmak shinashte, pa yok tiyoliske wan yok in tal amo mo'ihtakos wan mokawas tawak!
Kwakin Yosé kinkowili mochi in talme pa Egipto, wan yok oye kina mokawil mochi in tal para'ó moshte in egiptiyo', kinnamakak inintalme kampa mayanaliste katka chikawak ipa yehwante,
wan yok Yosé kintikipanolti inik egiptiyo' pa itenko in mochital Egipto, han itenko analko.
Amo kiko nitalme in totatsim. Yehwante amo kinnamakak inintalme, kampa totatsim takwaloya ka nitomi para'ó, amo monekya pa kinnamakaloskya inintalme.
Wan in egiptiyo' kinmili Yosé:
Pa sesen makwil kostal se han ka in tapishkaliste kimakaske para'ó. In oksek nawi kostale' ka in tapishkaliste yeske pa anmehwante, pa yok tatokaske in talme wan ka kintamakaske yehwante mochantilme pa anmokal wan pa takwaske anmopilwam.
Yehwante kinankilik:
―Tewal tishwalkwepil toyoliliste! Ma tiyek inintikipanolme in para'ó!
Yok kina Yosé okital tahtoliste pa mochital Egipto pa kimakaloskya para'ó. Pa sesen makwil kostal se han ka in tapishkaliste, wan pa ashka in tahtoliste kipiyal pa yok kichiwaske. Hanwel in talme ka in totatsim amo temakaloya in sesen makwil kostal, kampa amo katkaloya pa para'ó.
Wan yok ye kina moka mochantiti Isra'El pa in tal Egipto, pa in pweblo Goshen. Ompa mokowilik kwahmilme, wan kinpiyaloya ininpilwam wan momiyaptik hyero myak.
Wan mochanti Yakob 17 shiwim pa Egipto, yolti pa 147 shiwim.
Kwah astiwalaya in tonat pa mikiskya Isra'El, okinots Yosé nikon wan kili:
―Ta melak tinishtasot, shiktal momahwa itsinta nopyerna wan shinichil motahtol ka ni'itokaliste Dyos. Kampa tinishchiwilis kwal ka ta'ihniliste wan melak nimishtahtani amo shinishtapach pa Egipto!
Kwah nimosewis ompa kaha nowichalme yehwante mikik, shinishwik pa kiyawak Egipto, shinishtapach kaha yehwante tapachotikat.
Kili Yosé:
Isra'El kito:
―Shinishmak motahtol ka ni'itokaliste Dyos!
Kwakin Yosé kimak se tahtol ka ni'itokaliste Dyos, kwakin Isra'El motankwakets kaha westotikatka.
Manashé wan Eprayím
Panok sek tonatim wan kinawatik Yosé kampa kitakoko motats. Óy Yosé okit wan okinwik in omente ininpilwam, Manashé wan Eprayím.
Kimani kinawatiloya Yakob kampa mokon Yosé owal omichit, kwakin konan Isra'El nichikawaliste, pa motaliskya pa nitapeshte.
Yakob kili Yosé:
―Ones ka newal Dyos ka miyak chikawaliste pa in Wepweblo Luts, pa in tal Kanán, wan nishmashti
wan nichili: “Nimishchiwas pa momiyaptiske mopilwam, nimishchiwas pa tewal kisas se pweblo ka masewalme. Wan takwitap yeske myak tanichikolme ka masewalme wan nikinmakas in tal pa mokawiliske mokolinchim pa hanse.”
Ashka, mopilwam in omente yehwante takatik nika Egipto kwah ayamo'ok ni'asiyaya. Eprayím wan Manashé yeske nopilwam kina yehwante nopilwam Rubén wan Shime'ón.
Kimani niwalaya pa Padán-aram pa nimokwepaskya pa Kanán, kampa omik Rakel pa tal Kanán kwah tikatkaloya pa ot, opoli amo wEhka katka in pweblo Eprata. Ompa niktapach pa Eprata, yewal niyok itok BetLéhem.
Isra'El okinmit ininpilwam Yosé wan kitahtanili:
―Akyehwante inik?
Kili Yosé nitats:
―Yehwante nopilwam onihsmak Dyos nika.
Kwakin Isra'El kili:
―Shiwalak pa nikek yok nimishmashti ika Dyos.
Nishtololwa Isra'El shiyaptikatkaloya kampa kolinche katka amo tachiyaya; kwakin kinwalikil Yosé ininpilwam ka nitats kintenamik wan kinnapalo.
Wan Isra'El kili Yosé:
―Nitamatiya kampa amo nimichitaskya, wan ashka Dyos onishmakawalti pa nikinmitaskya nokolinchim!
Wan kinonan Yosé in omente, kikets Eprayím pa nimahwakwal wan kikets Manashé pa nimahwamapoch wan kinashilti ka nitats. Wan Eprayín moka pa nimahwamapoch Manashé pa nimahwakwal.
Kwakin Isra'El, kimela nimahwam, kipanolti wan okital nimahwakwal ipa itsontek Eprayím, yewal otakat takwitap, kwakin okital nimahwamapoch ipa nitsontek Manashé, yewal otakat ta'ishpa.
Wan kinmashti Yosé ka inik tahtolme:
“In Dyos yewal
nehnemtiyak inak notahwan, AbRaham wan Itsak,
yewal in Dyos hanse tonatim nishkwitawiyaya
wan pa ashka in tonat,
in nitakwitawilanhel pa in takpakIlwikak yewal nishkishti pa mochiten amokwal,
ma kinmashti inik piltontim.
