Yosé kili nitats:
―Amoyok tats! Kampa in okse nitakatiliste ta'ishpa nokon! Shiktal momahwakwal pa nitsontek!
Kampa nitats amo kinek kichi, yok:
―Nihmat nokon, nihmat! Yewal niyok momiyaptiske pa mochiwas se tanichikol we. Ma yok ninohni tipichi yes hyero we amoyok kina Manashé, ninohni tipichi nikolinchim yeske myak tanichikolme pa Wehwepweblo.
