―Newal nimikis pa se tonat; ma yok Dyos yes ka anmehwante wan anmishkwepas oksep pa nital mowichalme yehwante mikik.
Wan tewal, nimishmak ma we amoyok nikinmak monohniwan, nimishmak in tal yewal onikinkishtil in amoreteko' ka noteposte pa momiktiliste ka notawitol.
